n<p>B Su c c Diu Hnh  ng ln  chp hnh chung vi on t thin trc tng Quan m. B c b tr ng gia thy Tm Thin v c Diu Hnh. Ln u tin trong i b cm thy hnh phc, m p tnh ngi nh th!</p>\r\n<p>* * *</p>\r\n<p>Bui chiu hm , ngi ta thy ch Tm xe m ch n tp lu tranh ca b Su mt bao go 50 k. Ri ch cn ch b i tr n xp v s b git hi tra v mua cho thng Cu T mt ci o trng mi tinh  hng m n xng xnh n lp tnh thng ca cha i Bi.</p>\r\n<p>Chic phong b cn st li  lm cho bui chiu trong khu ngha a ny m p hn d ma ng  chm v.</p>\r\n<p><br /><strong>Truyn ngn Phan Ct Tng</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-14 14:42:26.065377	2016-08-20 12:04:44.058147	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
143	hinh-nen-phat-giao-dep-danh-cho-may-tinh-hinh-anh-4.jpg	T  (Phn 1)	<p><strong>T  l gio ngha c bn dng  gii thch mi hin tng nhn sinh v tr c quy np t thp nh nhn duyn, cng l con ng trung o duy nht gii thot sinh t lun hi, l nhng li dy i cng trn i th ca gio ngha nguyn th ca c Pht cho c Tiu tha ln i tha sau ny.</strong></p>\r\n<p>T  l php nguyn th u tin c c Pht chuyn php lun ni vn lc d cho nm v t kheo, sau khi Ngi thnh V thng Chnh ng Chnh gic. L gio ngha c bn dng  gii thch mi hin tng nhn sinh v tr c quy np t thp nh nhn duyn, cng l con ng trung o duy nht gii thot sinh t lun hi, l nhng li dy i cng trn i th ca gio ngha nguyn th ca c Pht cho c Tiu tha ln i tha sau ny. Nhng trn thc t, nh kinh Diu php Lin hoa<strong>[1]</strong> (Puarika)  ni r l c s nhn thc sai bit quan trng v cc Thnh  (ryasatay) cng nh l Duyn khi (Prattyasamutpda) trong vic chng c Nit-bn (Nirvna) gia cc nh Tiu tha v i tha, ngha l mt chng sanh theo cc nh Tiu tha, mun t c Nit-bn th phi vt qua khi sinh t (samsra) mi t c cnh gii Nit-bn ngoi sinh t, hay i t trng thi th gian (laukika) n mt trng thi xut th gian (lokuttara). Cn theo cc nh i tha th gia sinh t v Nit-bn khng c s sai khc no. Th gian c c ch l mt s hin hu tng i, gi tm khng tht c, nh nhn thc v thc hnh nh vy nn chng c Nit-bn chn tht, cn gi l Tathat (nh tht tnh) hay Snyat (khng tnh).</p>\r\n<p>Qua hai quan im v S tht sai khc nh vy, nn phng php thc hnh, v hai nhn quan i tt c mi s vt hon ton khc xa. i vi cc nh Tiu tha T Thnh  v l duyn khi lun cho l tht c, chng thuc v  nht ngha  (paramattha) ch khng phi tc  (savti) hay Bin k s chp (parikalpita), Y tha khi (paratantra) ca cc nh Duy thc. V s sai khc gia hai quan im nh vy nn theo  chng ti xin c trnh by v chng theo hai quan im c ly ra t hai h kinh in Tiu tha v i tha v T .</p>\r\n<p>Nh kinh Phn bit Thnh  trong Trung A hm 7<strong>[2]</strong>, hoc i t-b-sa lun 77<strong>[3]</strong>,  nh ngha v T  th:</p>\r\n<p><strong>1. Kh  (dukha-satya):</strong> Ch cho trng thi kh no bc bch thn tm. Nhn thc ng th gian, khng lun l hu tnh hay v tnh ca tt c mi s vt gia th gian, tt c u l kh; cng mi gi tr phn on do nhng hon cnh chung quanh to ra trong cuc sng ca con ngi thuc v th tc, th bn cht ca chng l kh. Kh  l Chn  ch cho quan h sinh t tht l kh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Tp  (samudaya-satya):</strong> c ngha l nhm hp tch cha. Nhn thc ng tt c nghip hoc phin no, chng c kh nng nhm hp qu kh sinh t ba ci. Tp  l chn  ch cho quan h sinh khi cng cn nguyn ca mi th kh ca chng sanh  trong th gian ny.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Dit  (nirodha-satya):</strong> l tch dit. Nhn thc ng v vic on tr dc i ngun gc ca kh, th kh s dit c, v c th s nhp vo cnh gii Nit-bn. Dit  l chn  ch cho s quan h dit tn kh v tp.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. o  (mrga-satya):</strong> o c ngha l thng sut. Nhn thc ng v o dit kh, qua bt Chnh o (T chnh kin cho n chnh tu). Nu nng ta vo chng m tu hnh, th s thot khi hai  kh-tp, t n cnh gii Nit-bn tch tnh. o  l chn  ch cho s quan h n bt chnh o.</p>\r\n<p>Qua T  kh v tp biu th cho nhn qu m vng ca th gian; tc qu ca hu lu th gian l kh , nhn ca hu lu th gian l tp ; qu ca v lu xut th gian l dit , nhn ca v lu xut th gian l o .  l nhn qu T  gii thot sinh t qua kinh in dnh ring cho cc nh Thinh vn nh trong kinh Php Hoa (Puarika) phm ta  dy.</p>\r\n<p>C rt nhiu thuyt khc nhau ni v t tnh ca t : Theo i t-b-sa lun 77<strong>[4]</strong>, hay cc nh lun s ca A-t-t-ma th ly ng th un lm kh , nhn hu lu lm tp ; ly trch dit lm dit , php hc, v hc lm o . Cn Cu x lun 22<strong>[5]</strong>, i t-b-sa lun 78<strong>[6]</strong>, th theo th t ly T   hin qun: Trc ht qun Kh , tip theo qun Tp , Dit  v o . Ngoi ra v l T  cn phn ra lm ba giai on, mi giai on nh vy th c bn hnh tng gi l tam chuyn thp nh hnh tng:</p>\r\n<p>a. Ln chuyn ban u gi l <strong>Th chuyn</strong>: y l Kh .</p>\r\n<p>b. Ln chuyn th hai gi l <strong>Khuyn chuyn</strong>: y l kh nn bit tt c (vnh vin on tr, chng nhp v tu tp).</p>\r\n<p>c. Ln chuyn th ba gi l <strong>Chng chuyn</strong>: y l Kh  bit tt c, cho n  tu tp.) V c nh vy Tp, Dit, o  c ba ln chuyn nh vy. Cho nn gi l mi hai hnh tng.</p>\r\n<p>Theo kinh A hm 15<strong>[7]</strong>, Cu x lun 24<strong>[8]</strong>, th trong ba ln chuyn T  ny mi  c bn hnh tng nhn, tr, minh, gic; v nh vy th trong mi  c c mi hai hnh tng. Nhng theo li gii thch ny chng khng thng dng m ch thng dng mi  c ba ln chuyn thnh mi hai hnh tng, ch khng c bn hnh tng ca nhn, tr, minh, gic trong mi .</p>\r\n<p>Nhng theo cc nh Nht thit hu b<strong>[9]</strong> trong tu chng lun gio hc th dng t thin cn  thnh lp cch qun T , mi mt  nh vy th c bn loi hnh tng, cng li thnh mi su hnh tng, nn gi l mi su hnh tng T : Tc l qun Kh  c bn hnh tng phi thng, kh, khng, phi ng, ngha l tt c vn php khng c tnh thng tn, chng l Kh, chng ch tn ti trong tng gi tm, khng c th tnh tht s; qun Tp  c bn hnh tng nhn, tp, sinh, duyn, ngha l chp i l nhn ca kh, Tp ny tch t kh, m cng lm tr duyn cho kh sanh khi; qun Dit  c bn hnh tng dit, tnh, diu, ly, ngha l cnh gii l tng ca dit kh l dit mi si giy tri buc, phin no khng cn na, cnh gii th thng vi diu, xa la mi tai hon; qun o  cng c bn hnh tng o, nh, hnh, xut, ngha l t n Thnh o dit kh, v thnh l con ng chnh ca thc hnh hp vi chnh l, hng n cnh gii l tng, m vt qua khi cuc sng tn ti m vng. Theo th t bn thin cn ny nhp vo kin o, dng tr v lu chn tht hin qun T . Kin o ny tc l d lu hng, n ni d lu qu, v t  tr v sau thuc v tu o, nu  thng c mi su tm hin qun T  ca d lu hng, v d lu qu ri th gi l hin qun Thnh .</p>\r\n<p>Hn na, theo cc nh Hu b ln lt qun T  vi bn nhn, bn tr ly Dc gii lm i tng, khi chp nhn kh l s tht th qun Kh  gi l Kh php tr nhn hay cn gi l Kh php nhn, l hin qun Kh  dc gii, on tr phin no m ca Kh , dng Kh php tr hin qun Kh  ca dc gii  chng nhp l ca Kh . Cn nu dng sc gii, v sc gii lm i tng qun T , l nh phng php loi suy, khi nhn thc c c khi qun Kh  gi l Kh loi tr nhn hay cn gi l Kh loi nhn, l hin qun Kh  ca hai ci trn, m on tr phin no, nh Kh loi tr hin qun Kh  hai ci trn m chng l, tc dng bn tm hin qun Kh  ny. i vi Tp , Dit , o  cng hin qun nh vy. Tt c l mi su tm gi l tm tr, tm nhn. Ngoi ra, cng theo th t qun v thanh tnh v lu ca T , c th sinh ra Kh tr, Tp tr, Dit tr, o tr, bn tr ny cng vi Th tc tr, Php tr, Loi tr, Tha tm tr, Tn tr, V sanh tr, cng gi l Thp tr bao gm tt c Hu lu tr, v V lu tr.</p>\r\n<p> l nhng quan im v T  t lc s chuyn php lun ti vn nai cho n hin ti ca cc nh Tiu tha ni chung v ca b phi Hu b ni ring, h cn c vo nhng th c c c t nhng li dy u tin v T  v nhng trin khai sau ny ca h, theo nh lut nhn qu, tu theo hin qun T  v nhng hin thc kh au tn ti ca nhn sinh m h mun vt qua khi s kh au sinh t ny bng cch vt ra khi ba ci  t n mt th gii Nit-bn chn tht ngoi ba ci ny.</p>\r\n<p>i vi cc nh Tiu tha T  v l Duyn khi l tht c hin hu, nhng ngc li cc nh i tha nht l cc nh Trung qun, cho rng cc php khng nh tht c, k c php T  hay Thp nh nhn duyn. Tuy nhin cc nh i tha s d khng ph nhn chng l v theo cc Ngi sinh t khng ngoi Nit-bn, v Nit-bn khng ngoi sinh t cho nn khng gt chng ra ngoi, m chp nhn rng chng sanh v v minh che lp, ban u mun hiu c Pudgala nyat (nhn khng) th phi nh hai php ny. Do  cc nh i tha coi T  nh l mt php phng tin nh mun nghn php phng tin khc,  t  chuyn chng thnh cu cnh trong nhng nhn thc thc hnh ca h. Cc nh i tha xem c Pht c hai hnh thc v nhng li dy ca Ngi, mt l Tc , hai l Chn . Nhng g Ngi dy v T  chng thuc v Tc  (Samvti), ch c Tathat v nyat mi thuc v Chn  (Paramrthsatya). V v vy T  cng tu theo s nhn thc ca cc nh i tha bi nhng th c ca h c c v T  v hnh thc cng nh ni dung.</p>\r\n<p>Theo Hin dng Thnh gio lun 7<strong>[10]</strong>, ca i tha Pht gio th y c vo ni dung ca T  m trin khai ra nhiu hnh thc: Hnh Kh , Hoi Kh , Kh Kh , Lu chuyn  (Ly Kh  trin khai), Tp nhim  (tng ng vi hai  Kh, Tp), Lu tc  (tng ng vi Dit ), Thanh tnh  (tng ng vi hai  Dit, o), Chnh phng tin  (tng ng vi o ) thnh bt .</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin ngoi thuyt gii thot sinh t ny trong Tiu tha gio, kinh in i tha cng c ni v T  ny, nh kinh Thng man, kinh i bt Nit-bn 7<strong>[11]</strong>, bc bn, pht huy v gii thch rt nhiu v thm ngha ca T  ny. Theo Thng Man bo kht ca Ct Tng quyn h<strong>[12]</strong>, cho l cch qun ca Tiu tha v T  khng c trit , khng t cu cnh, sau  phi tu tc tr li, nn gi l hu tc T ; cn T  ca i tha l hon ton trit , t cu cnh, sau  khng cn tu tc na nn gi l v tc T . Hai quan im ny hp li cng gi l bt . Theo Thng Man Ging Lun ca TT. Tu S, chng VII Thnh  v Nit-bn tr. 130-124 th: Bn Thnh  l ni dung ca gio php khng ch ring bit ca Thanh vn hay Duyn gic tha m chung cho c ba tha. Tu theo trnh  nhn thc m  ngha ca bn Thnh  c ni dung khc nhau. Nh s khng nh kinh i Bt-nh v t tnh ca bn Thnh . Tu-b- hi Pht:</p>\r\n<p><em>"Th no l bn Thnh  bnh ng?"</em></p>\r\n<p>Pht ni:</p>\r\n<p><em>"Nu khng tn ti s kh, khng tn ti nhn thc v kh; khng tn ti nguyn nhn tp khi ca kh cng khng tn ti nhn thc v nguyn nhn tp khi ca kh; khng tn ti s dit kh cng khng tn ti nhn thc v s dit kh; khng tn ti con ng dn n dit kh, cng khng tn ti nhn thc v con ng dn n dit kh.  gi l bn Thnh  bnh ng.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Li na, Tu-b-, bn Thnh  y l nh nh, l khng d bit, l php tng, l php tnh, l php tr, l php v, l tht t. V rng, c Pht hay khng c Pht, php tng l thng tr, khng h di, khng bin thi."</em></p>\r\n<p>V bn Thnh  theo s nhn thc ca Thng Man Phu nhn khi tha trnh c Pht:</p>\r\n<p>Bch Th tn, trong bn Thnh  ny, ba l v thng, mt l thng. V sao? V ba  thuc vo tng hu vi. Nhng g thuc vo tng hu vi, l v thng; nhng g l v thng, la php h vng. Nhng g l php h vng, khng phi l , khng phi l thng, khng phi l ch quy y. Do , Kh , Tp , o  khng phi l  nht ngha , khng phi l thng, khng phi l ch quy y.</p>\r\n<p><em>Mt kh dit  la tng hu vi. La tng hu vi, nn l thng. Thng nn khng phi l php h vng. Khng phi l php h vng nn l , nn l thng, l ch quy y. Nn dit  l  nht ngha .</em><strong>[13]</strong></p>\r\n<p>Theo Thng Man phu nhn, mc d c s khc bit trong nhn thc v phng php, trn mt hin tng gii chng b l thuc vo thi gian ca ba , nn ci nhn b hn ch vo c bit.  y, nhng ni kh ca sinh t ch c chim nghim v kinh qua bi c th, v c vng hng n  gii thot kh cng tu thuc vo c th  trong phn on sinh t, nhng v t tnh ca bn Thnh  gia Tiu tha ln i tha vn bnh ng, nn Phu nhn ni: <em>"V php khng hn km m chng c Nit-bn. V tr tu bnh ng m chng c Nit-bn. V gii thot bnh ng m chng c Nit-bn. V thanh tnh bnh ng m chng c Nit-bn. Cho nn Nit-bn ch c mt v, v bnh ng, gi l v gii thot."</em><strong>[14]</strong> .  l nhng sai bit trong cch nhn thc, trong phng php v trong ci nhn v bn th ca bn Thnh  gia cc nh Tiu tha v i tha trong cch l gii v chng.</p>\r\n<p>Theo i s Tr Khi ca tng Thin Thai y c vo kinh Nit-bn 5, phm c vng<strong>[15]</strong>, cng  ngha trong bn cu k: Nhn duyn s sinh php<strong>[16]</strong>  m thnh lp ring bn loi T  t cn n su khng ng, phi hp cng bn gio tng ca Tng, Thng, Bit, Vin li thnh:</p>\r\n<p><strong>a. Sinh dit T :</strong> l ch trng ca Tng gio, dng s sinh dit ca php hu vi, m qun nhn qu T  l tht c sinh, dit.</p>\r\n<p><strong>b. V sinh T  (hay l V sinh dit T ):</strong> l ch trng ca Thng gio, dng cc php nhn duyn tc khng, v sinh m qun nhn qu m ng T  u l khng-v m khng sinh dit.</p>\r\n<p><strong>c. V lng T :</strong> l ch trng ca Bit gio, ly s sai bit v lng hng sa ca ni gii v ngoi gii, m qun tt c mi hin tng u do nhn duyn sinh ra c y  v lng s sai bit, nhn  m T  cng c v lng tng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>d. V tc T :</strong> l ch trng ca Vin gio, ly ng th ca m ng tc tht tng, m qun s i lp mu thun ca m cng ng tc chng phi mu thun, m chnh chng l tht tng.</p>\r\n<p> sai bit v bn loi T  ca Tng Thin thai qua y c kinh Nit-bn 51, phm c Vng, ca Tr Khi i s c thnh lp cn c vo gio tng ca Tng gio, Thng gio, Bit gio, v Vin gio  t  cho chng ta thy c t im c bn  y l tu thuc vo cn c nhn thc qua thc t ni kh ca cuc i c biu hin qua mi ci nhn c bit v thc ti kh ca mi hnh gi c th hin qua mi gio tng ca gio mn, t cn n su, t tiu n i qua T : T dng c; n dng khng; t dng va c, va khng; n dng chng phi c, chng phi khng.</p>\r\n<p>Cn theo cc nh Duy Thc th trong: <em>"Cc tc phm Duy Thc nh Thnh Duy thc (Siddhi), v Nhp Lng Gi (Lakvatra) khng ch ni ring v T  m ni n gio l Tiu tha  so snh v nu r s khc bit. V d cc tp y ni n cc nh Tiu tha nh nhng v ch nm gi hin gio ca c Pht ch khng phi mt gio; t bng lng xc nhn s sinh khi ca s vt m thi, ch khng tm hi tnh bt sanh cn bn. Chng b kh cc di vng tng (parikalpan), xem ba gii l tht c, c nh s sai bit gia ch th v i tng, t chp nhn s hin hu ca un, x, gii, tm (citta), nhn duyn (hetupratyaya), hot ng (kriyyoga), sanh (utpda), tr (sthiti), dit (bhaga) v..v..."</em><strong>[17]</strong> Trong khi cc nh Duy thc li ch trng: Xem mi s vt l khng thit c, bt sinh bt dit, chn  khng th tuyn b, ng nht vi Nh tht tnh v khng thay i, y  tng anyha (bt th), v niryha (bt x), v vt ngoi mi kh nng tng tng (Lak. Tr. 196). Theo cc nh Duy Thc th T  cng nh bt c gio l no  c c Pht ni ra, chng c coi nh l nhng php khng tht hu ngoi tr Tathat (nh tht tnh) hay Snyat (khng tnh) mi thuc v  nht ngha  hay Chn , cn tt c chng thuc v Tc , thuc v bin k s chp, y tha khi i vi cc nh Duy Thc.</p>\r\n<p>Cng vy, Ngi Ngrjuna (Long Th) cng ng trn quan im coi mi vt khng tht hin hu, nhng nu c hin hu i chng na, th s hin hu T  ny cng ch l hin hu gi tm, chng nh mt gic chim bao, nh mt gic m, cn c nhn thc nh vy. V theo Ngi mi vt u khng (Sarvam Snyam) qua nhng li dy ca c Pht v ba php n,  cho chng ta mt ci nhn chnh xc hn v cc php c c Pht ni ra trong  c T . Nhng cc nh Tiu tha  khng nhn ra c, nn gia cc nh Tiu tha v i tha c s tranh lun si ni gay gt v vn  ny v ngy cng thm quyt lit hn trong cung cch chp nhn v gii thch theo quan im ca mi b phi. Cc nh Tiu tha ch chp nhn v bng lng vi li gii thch gin d l: <em>"V th gii khng c t ng v nhng s hu ca ng nn c gi l Snya"</em> (yasm ca sunnam attena va atteniyena va tasm sunno loko ti vuccati). T quan im y, cc nh Tiu tha ch chp nhn dnh Snya cho cc php hu vi v c bit l Nhn khng (Pudgala snyat) m thi . Trong khi , cc nh i tha, c bit l cc nh Madhyamiks (Trung qun), khng dng li ni y, ngc li cn tin xa trit  hn trong cch gii thch ca mnh v Sarvam snyam. Theo cc nh ny, th Snyat khng nhng ch dnh ring p dng cho cc php hu vi, m ngay n cc php v vi cng c p dng mt cch trit  nh quan nim v Nit-bn (Nirvana), Nh Lai (Tathgata) hay bt c mt khi nim no khc .</p>\r\n<p>Chnh nhng quan nim trit  ny  lm lung lay tn nn tng tri thc ca cc nh Tiu tha v nhng quan nim m h  th c c t nhng li dy ca c Pht v T  (ryasatyas), l Duyn khi (Prattyasamutpda) cng tt c nhng gio l khc. T nhng ht hng ny, cc nh Tiu tha  phn bc li bng nhng nn vn sc bn. M theo , nhng nn vn ny, chng va cng c cho lp trng hu l ca h, va nh  nhng phi l ca cc nh i tha v Trung qun  phm phi, theo quan im v lp trng ca h.  y, chng ti s trnh by nhng nn vn ny, cng nhng quan im ca B tt Long Th (Ngrjuna) v T <strong>[18]</strong> :</p>\r\n<p>Theo quan im v lp trng ca cc nh Tiu tha th: Nu tt c th gian u khng, khng c s hu th s khng c hin tng sanh dit . Khi  khng c hin tng sanh dit hin hu, th tt c mi hin tng theo  khng hin hu v ngay n c nhn qu T : <em>"Thy kh, on tp, chng dit v tu o"</em> cng khng lun. Do  php bo cng khng c. T khng ny dn n Bn qu Sa mn, Bn hng, Bn c cng khng. T  Bt hin thnh cng khng hin hu. Khi Bt hin thnh  khng hin hu th khng c Tng bo. Tm li, nu Php bo  khng, Tng bo  khng th lm g c Pht bo? Do  ngi  ph hoi Tam bo. Khng nhng ch ph hoi Tam bo thi m cn ph hoi lun c nhn qu ti phc cng tt c cc php ang hin hu trn th gian ny. T nhng phn tch trn cho thy cc ngi  qu sai lm trong nhn thc v cc php.  y, cc php ch thc hu ch khng phi khng thc hu nh cc ngi  quan nim.</p>\r\n<p> tr li nhng nn vn ny, ngi Long Th thy rng: i phng  khng nm c  ngha Khng (Snyat), tng Khng cng nhn duyn Khng, nn c nhng tng tng sai lm v chng. Do , trc ht, ngi mun vch ra nhng sai lm ca i phng v Snyat:</p>\r\n<p>- Snyat khng phi l Nsstitva (on dit) cng khng phi l Abhva (khim din mt ci g) nh h tng, m Snyat cn phi nhn thy qua cc c tng trong vic gii thch n .</p>\r\n<p>- Snyat l Aparapratyaya (khng th dy cho ngi khc) ch c t mnh chng ng ni tm, khng th nghe ngi khc ging dy m hiu c .</p>\r\n<p>- Snyat l Snta (an tnh), khng b sinh dit chi phi .</p>\r\n<p>- Snyat l Prapancairaprapancitam (khng th ngh bn).</p>\r\n<p>- Snyat l Nivirkalpa (khng th gii ng), vt ngoi vng tng.</p>\r\n<p>- Snyat l Annrtha (khng c nhiu ngha khc nhau). Ngi tip tc gii thch Snyat l Prttyasamutpada (duyn khi)<strong>[19]</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>S khng c bt c gi tr tng i no thc hu tn ti v mt th gii m  , mi vt c coi nh l tht hin hu, m chng ch l mt gi nh v mt hin tng khi duyn hp ,  ni ln ci hiu qu bt ton cho ci duyn bin  theo sau chng.  chnh l ci Tnh Khng (snyat) ca cc php c soi sng bi ci nhn su, thm hiu qua mi s kin, m qua , chng khng c mt s kin sai khc no gia sanh t v Nit bn. Th gii ch hin hu tng i gi tm, nhng chng s tr thnh hnh nh tht c i vi mt tm hn m m. Do , cn phi p tan mi quan nim sai lm v mt th gian chn tht  bn ngoi th gian ny, theo quan im ca cc nh Tiu tha. Theo , h s loi b Tc  (sanh t)  chng Chn  ( nht ngha hay Nit-bn). Ngha l cc v y i t trng thi th gian (laukika) n trng thi xut th gian (lokuttara).</p>\r\n<p>V tt c nhng quan nim sai lm nh trn, nn  dn cc nh Tiu tha n mt th cc oan khng th chp nhn c, trong vic c bin gio l T  v l Duyn khi thnh mt th chn l thc hu thuc v  nht ngha  (Paramattha) ch khng phi Tc  (Samvti), v c m cht vo , cho l mt th cu cnh thc hu cn phi t n. Cho nn h  hiu mt cch sai lc v quan im Sarvam snyam chnh c Pht ni ra. T , h  ra nhng nn vn m chnh h s t hi h trong cuc i thoi ny.</p>\r\n<p>Tip n, ngi Long Th mun lm sng t lp trng ca mnh v Dharmasnyat qua nn vn ny. Trc ht, ngi khng ph nhn Nh  mc d ngi  lit n vo hng Tc  trn phng din m. Song khng th khng chp nhn gio l ny trn ci nhn ca bc Thnh, v gia sanh t v Nit bn khng c s sai khc. V khi m N l tc, khi ng N l chn; ch khc nhau  ch m n v ng n, nh bi k ngi vit :</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Nu chng y Tc </em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Chng c  nht ngha</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Khng c  nht ngha</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Thi khng t Nit bn</em><strong>[20]</strong><em> .</em></p>\r\n<p> y, c s sai bit nhau trn bnh din m, nn c Tc  - nht ngha  -Nit bn. Nhng khi ng th chnh ba ci sai bit  khng khc nhau. V nhng l do  cho nn ngi Long Th khng ph nhn gio l Nh  trong quan im ca mnh, v ch coi n nh l mt phng tin cn cho giai on chuyn m khai ng. Theo ngi, nu khng nh nhng ngn thuyt ca Tc  thi  nht ngha khng ni c, v nu khng t c  nht ngha th lm sao chng ta c th t c Nit bn? V vy, n c coi nh l mt phng tin chuyn ch cho s thnh cng ca mt cu cnh. Nhng khi cu cnh  t c, v n nhn li chnh n, th chnh n l phng tin ch khng g khc. T nhng lp lun ny cho chng ta thy rng: quan im Snyat ca ngi Long Th khng ph nhn gio l Nh .</p>\r\n<p>Cng ng trn lp trng ny, ngi cnh co cc nh Tiu tha rng: Nu hiu Snyat sai lm nh nhng nn vn trn th chnh mnh t hi mnh. Bi v ci ngha Khng ny, n quyt nh s thnh tu ca cc php th gian v xut th gian. Ngc li, nu khng c n, th cc php th gian bt thnh. Theo php Thc-Hu ca cc nh Tiu tha th chng i lp vi ci Khng Thc Hu ca cc php. Nhng Snyat khng phi l ci Khng Thc Hu nh cc nh Tiu tha quan nim. Do , Snyat ny, n vt ra khi quan nim c-khng ca Tiu tha v nh vy m n quyt nh c s thnh bi ca cc php. Ngc li, chnh cc php Hu, theo quan nim ca cc nh Tiu tha, l php sai lm, ri vo thng kin. N s tr thnh k ph hoi Tam bo qua s soi sng ca Snyat.  y, chng ta s thy mt cch r rng hn, nhng phn bc m ngi Long Th  dng phng php Gy ng p lng ng, do chnh cc nh Tiu tha p li chnh h, sau khi ngi  ch r nhng hiu bit sai lm v Snyat m cho l ci on dit, ci khng thc hu, trong khi Snyat khng can h g ti chng c .</p>\r\n<p>Ngi Long Th bo: nu cc nh Tiu tha bo rng tt c cc php trong  k c T thnh , t chng  c thc hu nh tnh ca n, th cc php ny khng nhn, khng duyn. Ch v tnh kin tr ca n cho nn chng s khng sanh dit. Nh vy, r rng s thnh tu ca cc php u cn n nhn duyn? Nhng trong thc t, cc php t duyn sanh v chng dit i cng t duyn dit. Vy, nu bo cc php  c sn nh tnh ni t tnh ca chng th iu ny hon ton khng ng. V nu  c tnh quyt nh ni t tnh ca chng ri, th theo  nhn qu cng s b ph lun, v khng nhn th lm g c qu theo sau   th hin ci tng v thng ca cc php. ng ny, cc php nh ngi Long Th ni:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cc nhn duyn sanh php</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Ta ni tc l khng</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em> cng l gi danh</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cng l ngha Trung o</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cha tng c mt php</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Chng t nhn duyn sanh</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cho nn tt c php</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Khng phi chng l khng</em><strong>[21]</strong><em> .</em></p>\r\n<p> y, chng ta thy mi s hin hu ca mi s vt lun lun ty thuc vo cc duyn. Do , chng khng c t tnh, ch v mun hng dn chng sanh nn phi dng gi danh  ni. Khng  y xa la, khng l thuc vo c-khng nh cc nh Tiu tha  t hiu, nn chng c gi l Trung o. V php ny khng c tnh nn khng c bo l c, cng khng c khng, nn khng c bo l khng. Nu php t n  c tnh tng th dt khot khng cn l thuc vo cc duyn m hin hu. Nhng  y, nu mun c php m khng nh cc duyn th iu  s khng xy ra. Do , c-khng ca cc v khng phi l php Khng (Dharmasnyat) ca c Pht .</p>\r\n<p>Ngi Long Th lp lun tip: Nh trn, cc v bo rng quan im v Dharmasnyat ca chng ti c nhng li nh vy. Nhng r rng, ci li sai lm , chnh cc v vp phi ch khng phi chng ti. V sao? V nu bo rng tt c cc php vn t chng  c tnh, chng phi khng tnh th s ri vo khng sanh dit. Nhng nu m khng sanh dit th s khng c T thnh . Ti sao vy? V Dukkha (kh) khng t duyn sanh nn s khng c kh. Nhng theo kinh th "V thng l kh". Vy kh  c nh tnh ca ring n ri th lm g c v thng, v chng khng b t tnh ring ca chng.</p>\r\n<p>Li na, nu Dukkha  c nh tnh ri th khng cn phi sanh tr li, v trc   c Dukkha ri cn g phi t Tp sanh ra. Do  khng c Samudaya (Tp ). Mc khc, nu Dukkha  c nh tnh ca n ri th cng chng cn Nirodha (Dit), v tnh Dukkha  nh ri nn khng th mt c.</p>\r\n<p>Li na, php nu  nh c th s khng c tu o (magga), v nu l tht php th phi l thng hng. Nhng  thng hng ri th khng tng khng gim,  khng tng khng gim th cn g phi tu o? o, nu  tu c th khng c nh tnh. Do , khi trc , cc php  quyt nh c tnh ca chng ri th khng th c Kh  -Tp  -Dit . Vy th con ng dit kh hin ti nn i n ch no  dit kh?</p>\r\n<p>Li na, nu Dukkha  l nh tnh, m trc khi cha lm phm phu cha thy chng, th trong hin ti vn khng th thy c, v trong c tng lai na. Vn  on Tp, chng Dit v tu o cng nh vy. Nu t trc n nay chng on, chng chng, chng tu th trong hin ti cng chng on, chng chng, chng tu; v t trc ti nay cha tng on, cha tng chng, cha tng tu. Cho nn bn hnh trong T Thnh , tt c u khng hin hu. Khi bn hnh  khng hin hu th bn o qu cng khng lun, v nh tnh ca cc php cho nn t trc n nay cha t c, v trong hin ti cng th. Ngc li, iu ny c th xy ra, vi iu kin tnh ca chng khng nh th kh d t c. Nhng iu ny s khng xy ra vi quan im ca cc nh Tiu tha i vi cc php. Do , ci hu qu tt yu s xy ra theo  i vi vn  t Hng, Bt hin thnh, Tng bo, Php bo cho n Pht bo. Tt c u b ph, u b y li vo trong on dit, khng hin hu nh chnh quan im ca cc nh Tiu tha  hiu v Dharmasnyam, m cc v   gn cho cc nh i tha v Trung qun ch trng,  i nghch li ci Hu ca h.</p>\r\n<p> y, d l hu hay l v m hiu theo cc nh Tiu tha cng ri vo hai bn, chp th thin kin. Nu hiu theo cch m quan im cc nh Tiu tha v hu v v nh vy, th cho d chng ta c n lc sing nng tu hnh  t c qu v Pht, s khng th no thc hin c. Bi v mun t c qu v Pht phi thc hnh T thnh . Nhng nu thc hnh theo ng li ca cc nh Tiu tha, nh nhng phn tch trn ca ngi Long Th th lm sao t c?  l nhng quan im m ngi Long Th a ra  phn bc li nhng lp lun ri vo t kin ca cc nh Tiu tha. Chnh li dng "Gy ng p lng ng" ny  a cc nh Tiu tha vo tuyt l.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1472547349.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p>V sau y l nhng vn nn cui cng v T  ca cc nh Tiu tha a ra, sau khi h  c nghe gii thch v Dharmasnyat sai lm theo quan im chnh h:</p>\r\n<p>Ngi tuy  ph cc php, nhng cu cnh ca con ng i n A-nu a-la tam-miu tam-b-<strong>[22]</strong> (Anuttarasamyuak-Sambodhi) buc phi c. Nhn vo con ng ny  gi l Pht?</p>\r\n<p>Ngi Long Th cng ng trn lp trng Php-Hu ca chnh h  tr li cu hi ny. Ngi bo: Theo nh cc v, th cc php  c nh tnh ri, cn g phi nhn ni B   c Pht; hay ngc li, nhn ni Pht o  c B , v hai nh tnh ny l hai nh tnh ca ring chnh n. Cho d chng ta c n lc tinh cn tu hnh n mun kip i na, m trc kia chng ta khng c tnh Pht, th lm sao hin ti c th thnh Pht c? Cng nh thic khng c tnh vng, d dng  mi cch  rn da nung c, cui cng cng khng thnh vng.</p>\r\n<p>Li na, nu cc php  c nh tnh m khng phi khng, th rt cng cng khng c ngi to ra ti phc, v tnh ti phc  quyt nh trc ri, k c hnh ng to tc v ngi to tc cng khng. Do , d chng ta c  trong nhn duyn ti phc m vn khng c qu bo, v qu bo c th c c khi la xa nhn duyn ti phc i na, th qu bo vn khng cn i c nhn mi xut hin.</p>\r\n<p>Li na, la ti phc c th khng c qu bo thin c, nhng t ti phc th c qu bo thin c?</p>\r\n<p> tr li nn vn ny, ngi Long Th bo d c la ti phc hay khng la ti phc, c qu bo hay khng c qu bo, th tt c u ri vo li c-khng nh  ni  trc .</p>\r\n<p>Li na, nu cc nh Tiu tha v khng nm bt c ngha Khng v nhn duyn ca n nn c nhng quan im sai lm nh vy, th  v tnh ph  nht ngha Khng.  nht ngha Khng m b ph, tc l ph tt c php th tc.</p>\r\n<p>Hn na, nu chng ta quan nim tt c cc php-hu u c nh tnh ca chng, th theo , cc hin tng c c trn th gian ny u khng th sanh ra v khng th dit mt, m chng phi lun lun thng tr, vnh vin khng bin mt. V chng  c tht tnh ca chng ri, nn khng th bin khc c. Nhng mun vt gia th gian ny, hin by ra trc mt chng ta, lun lun  trong chiu hng sanh dit, bin dch trong tng st-na mt, trong tng hi th. Nhng hin tng ny lun ty thuc vo cc duyn hp-bin m hin khi. V vy, chng khng c nh tnh. Nu chng  c nh tnh th nh chng ta  bit: mt l thng, hai l on dit. Do vy, nu khng c ci KHNG (nyat) th nhng vic ny c th xy ra i vi chng ta: cha c khng cn c - phin no cng khng on - vic kh cng khng ht .</p>\r\n<p> kt lun phm T  ny, ngi Long Th  dn li dy ca c Pht trong kinh :</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cho nn trong kinh ni</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Nu thy php nhn duyn</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Thi c th thy Pht</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Thy Kh -Tp - Dit - o</em><strong>[23]</strong><em> .</em></p>\r\n<p> y, nu ngi no thy tt c php t cc duyn sanh ra, th ngi ny c th thy c php thn ca c Pht, tng trng tr tu t mi li ch, v c th thy c Kh-Tp-Dit-o ca T thnh . V thy c T thnh  cho nn t c T qu, dit tr tt c mi phin no. Bi vy, chng ta cn phi thu t ngha KHNG ny, nu khng s i vo con ng v minh t kin nh cc nh Tiu tha vp phi. Ai ph ngha KHNG tc l ph php nhn duyn, ph php nhn duyn tc l ph Tam bo. Nu ph Tam bo tc l chnh mnh t ph mnh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>(Cn tip)</strong></p>\r\n<p>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\r\n<p>[1] . i tha v s lin h vi Tiu tha, HT. Thch Minh Chu dch, tr. 327.</p>\r\n<p>[2] . .1, Trung A hm 7, tr. 0462a-0462b.</p>\r\n<p>[3] . i t-b-sa lun 77[3], tr . 0397a-0397b-0397c .</p>\r\n<p>[4] . i t-b-sa lun 77[4], tr . 0397a-0397b-0397c</p>\r\n<p>[5] . Cu x lun 22[5], .29, tr. 0113c-0114a.</p>\r\n<p>[6] . i t-b-sa lun 78, . 27, tr . 0401c.</p>\r\n<p>[7] . kinh A hm 15[7], . 01, tr.</p>\r\n<p>[8] . Cu x lun 24, . 29, tr. 0128c.</p>\r\n<p>[9] . Cu x lun, i 29, tr. 119b.</p>\r\n<p>[10] . Hin dng Thnh gio lun 7, Pht quang i t in. 2, Tr. 1842a.</p>\r\n<p>[11] . i bt Nit-bn 7, . 12 Tr. 0647a-0647c.</p>\r\n<p>[12] . Thng Man bo kht ca Ct Tng quyn h, Pht quang i t in. 2, Tr. 1842a.</p>\r\n<p>[13] . Thng Man ging lun, TT. Tu S, tr.283-284-285.</p>\r\n<p>[14] . Thng Man ging lun, TT. Tu S, tr. 134.</p>\r\n<p>[15] . kinh Nit-bn 5. phm c vng, . 12, tr.</p>\r\n<p>[16] . Nhn duyn s sinh php . 30, Trung lun, phm T , tr. 33)</p>\r\n<p>[17] . i tha v s lin h Tiu tha, HT. Thch Minh Chu dch, tr. 363.</p>\r\n<p>[18] . . 30, Trung lun, q 4, phm qun T  24, rya-satya-park, tr. 32.</p>\r\n<p>[19] . i tha v s lin h Tiu tha, HT. Thch Minh Chu dch, tr. 340-341.</p>\r\n<p>[20] . . 30, Trung lun, q 4, phm qun T  24, rya-satya-park, tr. 33.</p>\r\n<p>[21] . . 30, Trung lun, q 4, phm qun T  24, rya-satya-park, tr. 33.</p>\r\n<p>[22] . A-nu a-la tam-miu tam-b- l phin m t Anuttarasamyuak-Sambodhi ting Sanskrit, l ch tr tu gic ng vin mn bnh ng ca c Pht; cn gi l v thng chnh bin t