65	kho_bau.jpg	Kho Bu Trong Tim	<p>M ca tri tim l mt vic khng c g kh nhng cng khng phi l d. Khng kh bi n khng cn ti nng hay vn ling g. Nhng khng d bi cnh ca ny lun c th sp vo bt k lc no.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471271782.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p>Khi   n tri tim mnh ti thy n c th m ca <br />vi ngi ny nhng li ng vi ngi khc - nh minh ha</p>\r\n<p>Alibaba ch cn c cu thn ch Vng i, m ca ra th l cnh ca vo kho bu cha bao nhiu vng bc, ca ci m ra.</p>\r\n<p>Ti cng bit mt cu thn ch c th m ra mt kho bu v tn.</p>\r\n<p>Tim i, m ca ra!</p>\r\n<p>Nhng  khng phi l tri tim ca ai khc m chnh l tri tim mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Trong nhiu nm ti  c ht sc  tm c cu thn ch m ca tri tim ngi khc, khng ch trong tnh yu nam n m cn l trong n lc tm kim s n nhn, yu thng, coi trng, tn trng ca mi ngi, ca x hi.</p>\r\n<p>Ti khng h ngh rng kho bu c th li nm ngay trong tim mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Ti  khng thy rng bt c khi no tri tim ti m ra th bc bi, gin d, kh chu, ghen ght, hn th, tham lam, s hi, lo lng, c n, bun phin v cc dng thc au kh khc cng theo  m i ra.</p>\r\n<p>Ti  khng nhn ra rng bt k khi no ti thy trong lng mnh c yu thng, c mong mun cho tt c u c hnh phc th khi  ti cng thy trong lng mnh khng c au kh.</p>\r\n<p>Ti  khng thy rng m ca tri tim mnh l con ng  thot khi au kh.</p>\r\n<p>Bc bi, gin d, kh chu, ghen ght, hn th, tham lam, s hi, lo lng, c n, bun phin ging nh nhng bng ma ch c th tn ti trong bng ti ca mt tri tim ng ca. Nhng bng ma ny s tan bin khi ca c m ra cho nh sng ca tnh thng trn vo.</p>\r\n<p>Nu ti t cho mnh mc tiu l tm cch m ca tri tim ngi khc hay t cho c ci ny, ci kia nh kin thc, cng vic, xe c, nh ca, danh vng cng nhng gi tr tinh thn khc th cng tc l t ti phn chia th gii thnh hai cc bn v th, thnh nhng ngi c th gip cho mnh t c mc ch v nhng ngi cn tr, gy kh khn.</p>\r\n<p>Nh vy chng phi, chnh ti ch khng phi ai khc,  t to ra k th cho mnh? T ti a mnh vo th i u, ua tranh, ginh git vi ngi khc? Ti thy bc bi khi gp kh khn, tht vng khi mc ch khng t c, ghen ght khi ngi khc thnh cng, lo lng khi cha c vic, c n khi khng ai gip </p>\r\n<p>Cn nu nh ti t mc tiu cho mnh l m ca tri tim, l nui dng yu thng, nui dng ci mong mun cho tt c u c hnh phc th mi chuyn s hon ton khc. Khi  k th s khng th cn tn ti, khng cn ngi cn ng, tranh ginh vi ti. Ngi ta ch c th nui dng yu thng, chng c th no li tranh ginh, so b yu thng. Ngay ci thi khc tranh ginh, so b th trong lng  chng c yu thng ri.</p>\r\n<p>Khi mc tiu l nui dng ci mong mun cho tt c u c hnh phc, cho tt c ch khng phi l ch cho ngi ny hay nhm ny, th th con ng tht thnh thang, bng phng,  u, ai cng l iu kin, l c hi cho mnh lm ci vic .</p>\r\n<p>Ti chng cn phi i u, tranh ua, hn thua vi ai.</p>\r\n<p>Ti chng cn cn phi gii hn ai, tt hn ai, hnh phc hn ai.</p>\r\n<p>M ca tri tim l mt vic khng c g kh nhng cng khng phi l d. Khng kh bi n khng cn ti nng hay vn ling g. Nhng khng d bi cnh ca ny lun c th sp vo bt k lc no.</p>\r\n<p>Khi   n tri tim mnh ti thy n c th m ca vi ngi ny nhng li ng vi ngi khc, hoc ngay c vi cng mt ngi n cng lc ng, lc m. C khi mi pht trc cn thy yu thng, pht sau  thy kh chu, bc bi.</p>\r\n<p>Cnh ca ny rt d b ng li bi v t nh ti gi ti  gieo khng bit bao nhiu ht ging, to khng bit bao nhiu iu kin cho bc bi, gin d, kh chu, ghen ght, hn th, tham lam, s hi, lo lng, c n, bun phin v cc dng thc au kh khc sinh si ny n. Rt nhiu hnh vi  tr thnh thi quen, thnh nghin. Chng nh nhng bng ma gi cht cnh ca tri tim  bng ti - mi trng sinh sng ca chng - lun ng tr.</p>\r\n<p>V vy nu ti thc s mun tri tim mnh lc no cng m th ti phi canh chng tng pht tng giy.</p>\r\n<p>Kho bu ca Alibaba th phi canh chng v s b ngi khc ly trm.</p>\r\n<p>Cn kho bu trong tim th phi canh chng cho ca ng ng li.</p>\r\n<p>Cng m ra th n cng y thm.</p>\r\n<p>Tim i, m ca ra!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>L c Tn</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:36:29.174751	2016-08-20 12:24:51.082538	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
66	4.jpg	Pht Gio Khu Vc Trong Bc Chuyn Mnh	<p><strong>Chu  c xem nh l ci ni ca Pht gio vi nhiu gi tr tt p vn cn c lu gi qua bao bin thin ca lch s. V trong nhng nm gn y, trc s tc ng ca vng xoy kinh t, Pht gio khu vc ny dn dn c nhng iu chnh ph hp  tn ti v song hnh vi i sng ca s ng.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272055.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Pht t l Pht trong dp n vi hi ch Pht gio ti Singapore</em></p>\r\n<p>Vi gc nhn thong qua di y phn no cho thy iu .</p>\r\n<p><strong>C-ph Starbucks trong cha</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trong khu vc, i Loan c xem nh l mt hn o phn thnh vi i sng pht trin. Nh vy m sinh hot Pht gio  y t nhiu c nhng canh tn. Ch cn i dc vng t ny, chng ta c th d dng nhn ra nhng ngi i t c xy dng nguy nga, trng l trn nhng khu t rng hng chc hecta. Cc ngi cha nh Pht Quang Sn  thnh ph Cao Hng, Trung i Thin T hay Linh Nham Sn T  i Trung, Php C Sn  i Bc l nhng biu tng ca Pht gio i Loan, th hin tinh thn nhp th cao  v vn tm ra khi mt c s tn gio thun ty.</p>\r\n<p>Khi n Pht Quang Sn (Cao Hng), c l ch Tng Ni cng nh nhiu khch hnh hng t phng xa s v cng ng ngng, chong ngp trc v hin i ca ngi cha ni ting ny. Khng nhng th, trong qun th c gi l Trung tm Tng nim c Pht c s hin din ca nhng nh hng sang trng, khch sn cao cp, cc ca hng thc phm vi thng hiu ni ting v c ca hng c-ph hng u th gii Starbucks...</p>\r\n<p>B qua nhng kha cnh v thng mi v li nhun, hnh nh ca nhn hiu c-ph c gii tr c u ln  a chung ngy nay hin din trong cha to nn s ti mi v gn gi ca khng gian ny. Hin nhin ca hng c-ph s phi chn la cc thc ung v thc phm cung ng chay tnh, ph hp vi v tr c bit so vi nhng a im bnh thng khc  nhng chn ng c. Nh th m ch mt thi gian ngn c mt, ca hng c-ph ny  thu ht kh ng thc khch khi n tham quan v ving cnh cha, nht l gii tr.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272020.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>C-ph Starbucks trong Pht Quang Sn</em></p>\r\n<p>Ti Pht Quang Sn, khng ch c c-ph Starbucks m cn c c rp chiu phim Pht gio 4D, c vin bo tng hin i m ting Anh, Hoa lun c s dng song hnh, trong  cc v hng dn tham quan thng l s c hoc Pht t thm tn.</p>\r\n<p>Khi c hi v v nhng s cch tn mi m v hin i ny, S c Php Tnh, mt v hng dn on ti Pht Quang Sn cho bit, chng c kin to  thu ht gii tr n vi Pht gio. HT.Tinh Vn, v Thy ca chng ti, lun quan tm n vic truyn b Chnh php n cc th h tr nn ngi lun thao thc lm sao  ngi tr ngy ti cha ng o trong tm trng thoi mi v nhiu thch ng. V th, cc c s Pht Quang Sn  i Loan v khp ni trn th gii lun c u t xy dng theo phong cch hin i v tin ch nht, S c Php Tnh gii thch thm.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mt kiu Pht gio lin kt</strong></p>\r\n<p>C th thy, xu hng lin kt cc t chc Pht gio trong khu vc ang l mt xu hng tt yu v cn thit, bi l Pht gio dn dn cn c hnh ng nh mt tp th v s ng.</p>\r\n<p>V bi cnh lch s, vn ha v  thc h nn Pht gio  nhiu nc v vng lnh th trong khu vc nh Malaysia, Indonesia, Singapore, i Loan, c, Hn Quc, Nht Bn khng c t chc Pht gio mang tnh i din cho mt quc gia m ch l cc Gio hi, cc hi on c lp. Hoc nu c th vai tr tp hp v cng chung hnh ng khng c th hin r nt. Do vy, cc quyt sch c a ra khng to hiu ng chung v thc y c h thng Pht gio tin bc.</p>\r\n<p>Singapore l mt v d in hnh. o quc ny cng c Lin on Pht gio (Singapore Buddhist Federation) l ni tp hp cc hi on, cc t chc Pht gio c nc, vn hnh theo c ch nhim k 2 nm. Tuy nhin, Lin on ch hin hu mang tnh hnh thc m khng c to dng nh mt t chc Pht gio mnh m, i din cho c quc gia. Trong khi , t thn cc hi on Pht gio thnh vin tn ti c lp, phi t lc hnh thnh, hot ng v pht trin m khng c mt s tr gip gi tr no t Lin on.</p>\r\n<p> l l do m nhu cu lin kt Pht gio ti cc quc gia ny tr nn thit yu. Lin kt  chia s cc gi tr trong li dy ca c Pht,  trao i kinh nghim hong truyn gio l,  cng nhau tr vng trc s bin i khng ngng ca i sng kinh t v  gim i cc chi ph khng cn thit gia mt x hi m mi th u phi quy ra bng tin.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471271996.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Mt hi ch Pht gio c t chc ti ni cng cng ti Singapore</em></p>\r\n<p>Nh lin kt nn d khng c mt Gio hi quc gia, nhng ti cc nc nh Singapore, Malaysia, Indonesia v.v phong tro tu hc, s giao lu v chia s kinh nghim hong php lun si ni v ch ng. Kh nng t iu hnh v qun xuyn cc cng tc Pht s ti mi c s c tng cng. Nh vy hng ngy, c nhiu kha tu hc din ra, cc bui thuyt ging c s tham gia ca nhiu ging s ni ting khp th gii lin tc c t chc thu ht ng o thnh chng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Pht t tr dn thn</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sinh hot ca Pht t tr l mi lu tm hng u ca Pht gio  nhiu quc gia trong khu vc. Ch trng n ngi tr, y c xem nh bc i ng n v cn c u t  to s vng bn ca Pht gio  tng lai.</p>\r\n<p>Ngy nay, t tng ngi tr kh ci m. H i n cha i khi khng phi  cu nguyn m  tm cht bnh an v tnh thc gia s x b ca cuc sng. Nhn thc c vn , nhiu t chc Pht gio dnh cho ngi tr c thnh lp v lin tc a ra cc hot ng mang tnh mi m v thn thin bng cc bui giao lu, hun luyn, thin tp, thuyt ging, chia s gi tr sng, hot ng x hi, d ngoi v lin kt quc t.</p>\r\n<p>Ti Singapore, mt o quc kh nh vi khong 6 triu dn nhng  c gn 40 hi on Pht gio dnh cho ngi tr hin din ti cc ngi cha ln, cc trung tm nghin cu Pht hc v cc trng i hc danh ting nh NUS, Nanyang. Sinh hot ca nhng t chc ny kh phong ph, a dng v c t chc theo hnh thc m  bt c bn tr no c dp tip cn cng c th tham gia. Nhng ngy l ln nh Pht n, Vu lan l dp m cc t chc ny hot ng si ni v rn rng. H t chc nhng hi ch Pht gio ni cng cng, thnh lp cc ban nhc ng ph biu din cc ca khc Pht gio, tin hnh cc cng tc gy qu  pht trin v lm cng tc x hi.</p>\r\n<p>C mt im c bit l cc t chc Pht gio tr ny do chnh ngi tr iu hnh theo nhim k. H ng c v nu c chn s t hoch nh chng trnh, iu hnh hot ng t chc ca mnh trong thi gian c tn nhim. Song song  l s h tr v ti chnh v k nng t cc gio s i hc, cc chuyn gia thm tn Pht gio trn nhiu lnh vc. Ngay c vic lin kt quc t v t chc nhng hot ng giao lu vi s tham d ca cc Pht t tr t cc nc lng ging cng do ngi tr m trch.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471271966.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Mt ban nhc ng ph ca nhm Pht t tr cha Vimalakirti - Singapore</em></p>\r\n<p>Ni v quan im Pht gio hng n ngi tr, Chin Wy, mt chuyn gia x hi hc v cng l mt Pht t thun thnh trn o quc vi s mng lin kt cc nhm Pht t tr cho rng tp trung vo ngi tr mang tnh sng cn ca Pht gio,   Pht gio khng nn cu n hnh thc, khng nn ph din cc l nghi rm r m phi ch ra cc li ch s mang li cho ngi tr. Mang tm nim , c v nhiu cng s  hot ng khng mt mi trong sut nhiu nm lin v n nay, h  kt ni kh vng chc nhiu hi on Pht t tr khng ch  Singapore m cn lan ra c Malaysia, Indonesia v Thi Lan.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Bo Thin</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Ngun: giacngo.vn</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:41:02.851731	2016-08-20 12:25:55.403461	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
67	1.jpg	Ma C in n  - Mt Ngn Trn X S Sng Hng	<p><strong>Nu c lng du trn qu x sng Hng th vic khm ph th gii ngh thut qua nhng iu ma c in qu thc khng him, n nh nhng dng chy bt tn ti tm xanh ti theo tng th iu ma qua sn khu, phim nh, ca nhc, hoc trong cc sinh hot l hi dn gian  khp mi ni trn x s sng Hng.</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272212.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Cc ngh s ma n </em></p>\r\n<p>Cc loi hnh ngh thut trn t nc n  va giu c, va li huyn nhim nh cc v thn lung linh sut lch s thm thm nhng nm ngn nm qua, m dng nh nh cao ca mi nh cao y l ngh thut ma c in.</p>\r\n<p>Ngy nay, cc th loi ngh thut ma c in y,  tr thnh nhng s gi,  n  a bn tay thn thin ca mnh bt tay vi ton nhn loi. M c th,  c ln trn thnh ph sng Hn, ti  c dp thng thc cc ngh s Odissi n  din dch bng mt th ngn ng ma y b nhim,  t  ti hiu ra, v sao th gii ngh thut y c tng xng nh truyn thuyt v mt tnh yu khng hi kt thc.</p>\r\n<p>Bn c th ngi sut bui m say thng thc ch mt iu Kathak khng thi m khng h c cm gic chn nn mt cht no. Bi thng thc ma c in n , khng ch b cun ht theo ci nhn quan m ui m ly ca s thng hoa hoan lc, m ta cn nghe ra th, hiu ra nhc t din dch ca ngn ng ma huyn o. Cng c th bn s ngn ng nh b ht hn bi nhng ting gi cm ca hnh th, gi m ra nhng s thi, nhng truyn thuyt, nhng cu chuyn tnh yu qua cc iu thc phc hp uyn chuyn n huyn hoc. V c th cn xa hn na, y l c mt th gii mnh mang v iu c in Bharatanatyam, Kathakali, hay l Manipuri, Kuchipudi</p>\r\n<p>Nhng ngi bn n  ni vi ti rng: C nht trong cc iu ma c m ngi n  ngi ca,  l iu ma Odissi, n  xut hin t th k th hai trc Cng nguyn. V iu ny c ngun gc t bang Orissa  min ng n , c lu du khc ha trong cc cng trnh kin trc c  cc n i Hindu Brahmeswara v n Konark  Puri. Tr tnh, uyn chuyn, lng mn thanh thot theo tng bc nhy, gi cm trong tng nh mt, nhp iu biu cm theo tng ng cong c th. Ma Odissi l bit lm cho ci p nh thc mi nim cm xc tri dy.</p>\r\n<p>Vng, ti khng r lm c phi v th m nh th Tagore  tng ngi ca Mt t, di gt chn em, vang ln nh mt th cm. Ch c iu, nhng gt chn nh nhng lt i nh huyn thoi y, dt du theo nhng thanh m th cm Hindustani, Carnatic cng vi bao loi nhc c khc,  c ln hi ng cng ti, khng ch trn t nc n  xa xi, m ngay trn c qu nh ca mnh. Ci ch  ma m bn sng Hn y, nhng ngh s Odissi n  gi tn l: Khm ph nhng nhp iu Tagore, chng nh  khm khc vo ti mt th tnh yu min man nh c ni vng tay ln. n ni v sau ny, c ln du lm lang thang gia mnh mng ph x New Delhi, hay Kolkata, cho n c cao nguyn Dharamsala di chn Hy M Lp Sn , ti c cm gic nh i u cng c bn tay mu nhim Odissi vi Nhp iu Tagore dn ng!</p>\r\n<p>Rabindranath Tagore l mt thi s, mt trit gia - ngi con v i ca t nc n . ng l nh th chu  u tin ot gii Nobel Vn hc (1913). Ngi ta bit n Tagore trong trit hc, th vn, hi ha, m nhc, vit kch, nhng c l, chnh ngi n  hiu v thin ti ca mnh r hn bt c mt dn tc no. on ngh thut truyn thng Odissi n , bng ngh thut ma c in ca qu hng mnh gn nh  minh ha cho ta hiu v nhng  ngha y.</p>\r\n<p>Cng c th chnh Tagore v trit l khm ph ra nhng nhp iu, nh l linh hn dn dt cho mi tm kim sng to ngh thut trong loi hnh ma c in y. Khng h si ng v rc r n chi ngi bi m thanh nh sng, khng hnh thc phc trang lp lnh hay gi cm quyn r nh ma hin i, m l su lng, nh nhng theo nhp phch phc hp mang m hng ca s chuyn ng tr tng tng, gi cho ngi xem cch gii m nhng mt ng nn th m nhp iu ma to ra.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng no phi ch Khm ph nhng nhp iu Tagore khng u, on ngh thut Odissi n  cn k cho tt c nghe mt m hng khc,  l trnh din tit mc Thakurbarir Shajposhk. Mt tit mc ma minh ha gii thiu v trang phc truyn thng ca gia nh Rabindranath Tagore, ti hin hnh nh cnh gia nh Tagore v bn b vi trang phc t thit k. Di nh sng thm thm ca sc mu v huyn o ca m thanh, hnh nh cc v cng dn dt con ngi ta ngc dng thi gian tr v th k XIX qua cch phc trang v trnh din y biu cm.</p>\r\n<p>Ti nh Nh ht tung Nguyn Hin Dnh m y trn ngp ting v tay khi nhng nhp iu Tagore m ra mt th gii nh l s chuyn ng t khp v tr. Chng nh tng nh mt, tng chuyn ng ca cc v cng to ra nhng nhp iu bit nh thc mi cm xc ngi xem qua thanh m li th v ca khc ha quyn ngn nga lm say m tri tim con ngi.</p>\r\n<p>Vng, chnh mi tri tim s l s sng, sc sng thu t ci l vnh hng s tri chy ca thi gian. Nhp iu ha theo m nhc v v khc, mi phn on nh l s bc tch tng lp, tng mng cu trc nhp nhng. C lng xung tng phn nh th, t pha khn gi, ting v tay tri dy ri li trm xung nh du dt khoan thai theo tng ln sng cm xc khi th a v lc li mnh mang su lng.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272191.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>n  - t nc ca nhng iu ma</em></p>\r\n<p>Th tht, thng thc ma c in n , t by lu, ti nh a tr ham chi lc ng trong cnh rng hoa thm thm. Ni cnh rng hoa l cn ni gii hn, phi l i ngn hoa ni tip i ngn hoa. Ti hiu nh th ny khng r c ng khng, hnh nh c t nc mnh mng n , hu ht tt c ph n t tr n gi u bit ma. Ni ng hn, h  bit ma t u thu cn trong thai m,  n khi sinh n ra, va chp chng bc i l  bit Odissi ri. C v g y kh tng ng vi cc dn tc vng cao  cc min Ty Bc, ng Bc t nc ta. Con gi khp cc thn bn t ni cao n lng thp, ni no cng bit ma. Sinh ra, ln cn ln nng l  bit ma ri, ch cn trng lp ngh thut cao siu no ht. M nu c trng lp chng i na, th y l nhng bc ni tip mang dng dp hin i, n rc r mu sc hn thc y, nhng dng nh ci thn ci hn b vi i, thm ch cn c th mt i.</p>\r\n<p> t nc n  th Bc n, Trung n, Nam n bc vo bt c ni no trong cc l hi hu nh ngi ta cng u gp ma v ma. Liu hiu ra nh th ny ti cung tn hay cng iu lm khng, hnh nh trn x s sng Hng, ma l mt trit l din dch cho con ngi hiu ra mt th mt ng, rng s im lng (hay l ting gi cm) l tt nh ca mi m thanh. y cng l loi hnh ngh thut sng to nn mt th mt ngn truyn i ny qua i khc trong v thc c cng ng dn tc. Th mi hiu sc sng ca ngh thut, ca ci p, m li l ngh thut ma c in t qu hng Tagore, nh li thi s  tng gieo rc vo tri tim nhn loi: m nhc v cc v iu l ngn ng chung ca loi ngi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><br /><strong>Nguyn Nh Tin</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:43:45.086681	2016-08-20 12:26:17.917193	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
