110	1.jpg	Hi Tri "Tui Tr Pht Gio ng Nai" Ln 2 - 2013	<p><strong>Hn 1600 tri sinh v tnh nguyn vin t cc huyn, th, thnh trong tnh ng Nai  hi t v ngi nh lam Linh Ph, huyn Tn Ph lm nn mt hi tri tng bng v n tng.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Hi tri din ra trong 3 ngy, t ngy 9 n 11/8/2013. Tuy hi tri bt u t 15 gi ngy 9/8, nhng t sng sm, tng chic xe  a tri sinh v n vi khung cnh thin nhin hng v ca ni rng Tn Ph. Trc mt tri sinh l mu xanh bt ngn ca ca cy, lm ni bt sc y vng ca Thng ta Thch Php Cn v ch tng cha Linh Ph. Ting nc chy rc rch ca sui ha vi li cho ca chim mung. Tng ln gi nh a ci mt lnh t vch ni xua tan mt nhc, lo ngh ca i thng nhng ch cho s thanh tnh trong tm hn mi ngi.</p>\r\n<p>Dng lu, n nh v tr. Hot ng u tin ca tri bng cuc th ng Nai Idol  chn ra nhng tit mc xut sc cho m la tri hm sau. Ting ma t tch bn mi lu vo m ru tri sinh vo gic ng m m.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663045.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663050.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>L khai mc bt u vo 8 gi sng ngy 10/8 di s chng mnh ca HT Thch Hu Tm - Trng BHD Pht t ng Nai, Trng BTC Hi tri, TT Thch Bu Chnh, Ph BTS PG ng Nai, TT Thch Php Cn  Trng BTS PG Huyn Tn Ph. i din Ban tn gio ng Nai, i din chnh quyn a phng Huyn Tn Ph, huyn Ph Sn cng tham d. BTC  nhn c nhiu lng hoa chc mng ca cc ban ngnh a phng v ban ngnh Pht gio. Ha thng Thch Hu Tm pht biu khai mc cho bit Hi tri ln ny l bc tip theo trong nh hng hot ng cc cu lc b Thanh thiu nhi Pht t, tin ti thnh lp Phn ban Thanh thiu nhi Pht t cp tnh v cp Huyn nhm to sn chi v mt mi trng tu dng o c cho lp tr.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663071.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663074.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663080.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663084.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663088.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663091.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663093.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663096.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>Thng ta Thch Bu Chnh ban o t nhc nh tri sinh sng vui, sng khe v c ch cho x hi. Ban t chc Hi tri  n thm v chp hnh lu nim tng khu vc tri. Cc cng trnh th cng ca tri c u t kh cng phu v mang nhiu tnh sng to.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng hot ng tip theo ca tri c din ra kh nhp nhng v  li nhiu n tng kh phai trong lng mi tri sinh. Di cn ma ln vo chiu, tri sinh c ta m vi ch : Ti yu bin o Vit Nam do Ban Tn gio tnh ph trch. Cc tr chi dn gian: ko co, bnh xe lun hi,  thu ht tri sinh tham gia nhit tnh si ni. Nhng nh nn lung linh huyn o ca m hoa ng nh n sanh thnh nhn ma Vu Lan bao hiu  lm xc ng c ngn tri sinh. Bui vn ngh la tri vi nhng tit mc c tp luyn khc cng phu ca cc n v v giao lu vi cc ca s n t TP H Ch Minh si ni n gia khuya. Ha thng Thch Hu Tm cng ch tng trong BTC  cng tri sinh ta m Pht Php, gii p nhng thc mc hn nhin ca tri sinh nh: Pht t sao phi n chay, tu s Pht gio sao phi co u v nhng vn  lin quan n tam quy, ng gii.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663133.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663136.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663139.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663142.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663145.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663148.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663150.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663154.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663157.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663160.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663162.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663165.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663169.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663172.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663175.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663177.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663180.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663183.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663186.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663189.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663191.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663194.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663197.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663199.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663202.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663205.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663207.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663211.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663213.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663217.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663220.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663223.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">14 gi ngy 11/8, hi tri b mc. Theo Ban T chc, hi tri thnh cng tt p l nh s quan tm ca BTS PS tnh, Ban Tn Gio tnh, Ban Hng dn pht t tnh, s n lc c gng ca Ban t chc, ban iu phi, s cng tc tch cc ca i ng Huynh trng thuc BHD GPT v s tham gia nhit tnh ca hn 1600 tri sinh trong tnh. Nhiu qu tng c trao n tng n v. Tri sinh tham d u c cp giy chng nhn. Ha thng Thch Hu Tm ban o t v tuyn b b mc Hi tri, hn ti ng ti Hi tri ln 3 vo nm sau.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663268.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663271.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663274.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471663277.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>c bit kinh ph t chc tri do Ban tr s Pht gio tnh v cc huyn h tr, ngoi ra cn c s h tr ca Ban tn gio Tnh v ng gp ca cc v mnh thng qun.  chun b cho hi tri ny, Cha Linh Ph  lm mt hi trng ngay trc sn cha vi vt liu bng tre ph bt, t c trn 1000 gh ngi, xy thm trn 20 phng tm v nh v sinh v tu sa nhiu cng trnh khc. Tri sinh khng ng bt c mt khon tri ph no, c cp ng phc v n ung trong sut thi gian din ra hi tri.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Tin, nh: Thin Ng</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-20 03:22:02.699019	2016-08-20 12:48:47.791298	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2013-08-12 00:00:00
68	xuan.jpg	Ma Xun & Tui Xun	<p><strong>t tri c ma xun, con ngi c tui xun. Ma xun ca t tri y hoa thm sc thm, tui xun ca con ngi y sc sng tnh yu. Ma xun i cn tr li, tui xun i ri l qua mi mi... Ta n xun mi nm vi nhng cm xc mi, xun mi ln tr li cng mi tinh khi.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272375.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>t tri c vn ma xun, con ngi vn lun ca ngi v ch n ma xun</em></p>\r\n<p>Ma xun m u cho mt nm. Tui xun m u cho mt i ngi. Tt c u l biu tng ca ci p, ca khi u thng hoa. Ma xun mang n cho con ngi nim vui v hnh phc. Tui xun a con ngi vo bc trng thnh ca tnh yu v s nghip.</p>\r\n<p>S khi u no cng rt quan trng v ngi ta tin  l nn tng ca tng lai. Khi ng trc ca ng tng lai y, ngi ta hn nhin nh hoa nh bm, m mng nh gi nh my; ngi ta ngh di chn mnh l ni  uy nghi, trong hn mnh l sui ngun bin c, trc mt mnh l mt tri rc r. Ri thi gian i ti, con ngi cng i ti theo vng quay nhn th. Ma xun ln i trong t tri  ri mt nm sau tr li vi chic o chong hoa sc s v m p.</p>\r\n<p>Tui xun cng ln i trong i ngi nhng khng bao gi tr li. Mc cho luyn lu tic nui, tui xun lnh lng i qua mang theo s tn ph ca thi gian, con ngi ch bit tm li tui xun trong k c v hoi nim.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng ai sng trong tui xun hy sng ht mnh vi ci p ca n, v t ci p  ta gi mi ci p cho i mnh,  khi n tui gi ta vn cn c cht hn xun,  l hnh phc vin mn ca i ngi. i gia ma xun, ta tn hng tt c hng hoa nng m,  l tinh ty ca mt nm. Bng tnh yu trn vn v lng rung cm dt do, ta nguyn gi mi v p ca ma xun sut mt nm di  d xun c i qua, tm hn xun vn sng trong lp lnh gia ci trn gian dim tuyt.</p>\r\n<p>t tri c vn ma xun, con ngi vn lun ca ngi v ch n ma xun. i ngi ch c mt ln xun, hy lm cho thi gian bt lc trc ci p tm hn vnh cu v v gi ca con ngi</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Trnh Bu Hoi</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:46:22.133575	2016-08-20 12:26:36.467919	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
70	nang_niu_1.jpg	Thc Hnh Lng Bit n  Sng Hnh Phc Hn	<p><strong>Gio s Tm l hc Robert Emmons, tc gi quyn Cng nng ca lng bit n (Gratitude Works) nh ngha s thc hnh lng bit n l nhn thc v s tng tr ca ngi khc dnh cho chng ta v l s mong mun c hi p li nhng iu tt p ta  nhn c t ngi khc.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cc nh nghin cu  chng minh nhng li ch to ln m vic thc hnh lng bit n mang li cho sc khe th cht ln tinh thn nh: gip khe mnh hn, ci thin gic ng v thm ch cn gip tng cng sc  khng cho c th.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272638.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Nhng ngi bit n thng c mt ngn phong c bit (a particular linguistic style) </em><br /><em>v thng ni v cc ni dung nh: qu tng, s cho i, nhng iu an lnh</em></p>\r\n<p>Ni mt cch thi v hn, nh chia s ca Emmons vi t Huffington Post, lng bit n gip cuc sng t do hn, nh nhng hn v d chu hn v chnh lng bit n gip chng ta c sc mnh  kim sot i sng cm xc ca chnh bn thn mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Theo , 4 cch gip thc hnh lng bit n m mi ngi c th lm mt cch d dng mi ngy:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vit th</strong></p>\r\n<p>PGS.Steven Toepfer, chuyn khoa Gia nh v S pht trin Con ngi, i hc Kent (Hoa K) thng qua nghin cu  khng nh mi lin h gn gi gia lng bit n v s khe mnh (th cht v tinh thn) ca c th.</p>\r\n<p>Mt nghin cu nm 2011 trn 200 sinh vin i hc c cuc sng hnh phc cho thy rng, nhng ai vit mt l th  ngha v lng bit n mi tun trong kha hc sut 3 tun (dnh khong 15-20 pht cho mi ln vit th) th c c s gia tng ng k v s hi lng v cuc sng, nim vui v gim c cc triu chng phin mun, suy nhc.</p>\r\n<p>Tc gi chia s: Bn khng nht thit phi gi l th i. Hy xem y nh l s phn hi mt cch c  thc v nhng iu bn cm thy bit n.</p>\r\n<p>Nhiu gi  cho rng nn rt ngn thi gian mi ln vit th li v nhiu ngi cm thy nhng ln vit sau tr nn kh khn hn l ln vit l th u tin. Tuy nhin, Toepfer khng nh rng d ch dnh mt t pht  hng lng bit n ca mnh v mt ai  mt ln mi tun cng c th mang li thay i ln no .</p>\r\n<p><strong>Vit nht k</strong></p>\r\n<p>Nghin cu tm ra rng nam gii v ph n vit vi dng nht k mi tun v nhng s vic  xy ra gip tng trng lng bit n  h v h c xu hng cm thy lc quan hn, thy cuc sng tt p hn. Nu bn khng a giy bt th hy vit trn bt c phn mm ng dng no bn thch.</p>\r\n<p>Tp ch Forbes cng ng ti cc nghin cu chng minh rng th hin lng bit n qua nht k cn gip ci thin cc vn  v gic ng.</p>\r\n<p>Toepfer ni thm: Tt c chng ta ai cng c  thc v lng bit n nhng nu chng ta  lng bit n ca mnh ng im lm th chng ta s b qua nhiu li ch quan trng. Cm ng v quy np lng bit n l cch gip chng ta ha chy vo ngun sng tt p m t thn mi ngi u s hu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cn trng nhng g mnh ni</strong></p>\r\n<p>Lng bit n khng ch thin v khng ni nh nhng g bn lm, theo Emmons. T NBC khng nh rng: phn nn v vn  ca ai  c th gy ra lo lng v suy nhc. Tuy vy, nghin cu cng a ra li ch ca vic ni ra (chia s) nhng cn nht vn l c s cn bng.</p>\r\n<p>Theo chia s ca Emmons, nhng ngi bit n thng c mt ngn phong c bit (a particular linguistic style) v thng ni v cc ni dung nh: qu tng, s cho i, nhng iu an lnh, Tri li, ngi km lng bit n thng c xu hng ni v s tc ot, s xng ng, iu hi tic, thiu thn, nhu cu, s hi v mt mt ng khuyn rng nn cn trng vi nhng iu mnh ni, nu khng dn d chng ta s tr thnh ngi km bit n.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hy ha mnh vo lng bit n</strong></p>\r\n<p>Nu bn vn cn mt tr lc  c th thc hnh lng bit n trong cuc sng, hy c nhng quyn sch c ni dung v lng bit n  gi cm hng cho bn thn. Rt nhiu tc gi ln u vit v lng bit n. Hy c v suy ngh, phn hi v tm quan trng ca s thc hnh ny. T t, bn s thc hnh tt trong cuc sng.</p>\r\n<p>Nu mun thc hnh thnh tho lng bit n, tht s cn thi gian. Vi nhng s thc hnh nh, li ch c th thy sau dm ba tun nhng  lng bit n tr thnh mt thi quen th cn nhiu thi gian hn. S thun thc no cng c tnh qu trnh c. Thay i l di lu v mi chng ta cn tp tnh v iu chnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Trn Trng Hiu </strong><br /><strong>(theo The Huffington Post)</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:51:19.045942	2016-08-20 12:27:13.220873	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
71	2.jpg	Nng Chn Tr Thin	<p><strong>T ngy xa xa cho n nay, ngi dn Vit Nam  gn b vi cy ch xanh (gi l tr), cng thn thuc hn vi vic ung tr, tr thnh mt loi thc dng chung hng ngy ca ng b chng ta, cho n ngy nay vn cn c lu truyn.</strong><br />Nhiu nc khc trn th gii  s dng v a vic ung tr tr thnh mt nt vn ha thun ty nh Nht Bn, Trung Quc, Hn Quc  mi quc gia u c mt phong cch khc nhau cho vic dng tr. Ring Nht Bn, tr c nng n mt nh cao,  chnh l Tr o. Theo , vic ung tr  c cc nh khoa hc rt quan tm, nghin cu k lng v khng nh rng: tr c tc dng tt cho sc khe ngi dng nh phng nga bnh ung th, bnh tim mch, tiu lng m tha trong c th</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272820.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Ung tr cng l mt cch tu tp. Vi ci tnh , ngi xut gia thng ly tr lm bn</em></p>\r\n<p>Ngy xa, ngi Vit Nam chng ta vi vn ha n tru  c t rt lu i, dng tru  i khch, dng ming tru  bt u cho mt cu chuyn. Mi tru l cch m u giao tip rt lch s, cch cho gn gi ca ng b hi xa. Ming tru l u cu chuyn, hay Tin y n mt ming tru. Hi rng qu qun  u chng l? - th hin mt s cho hi rt n tnh.</p>\r\n<p>Ngy nay, tru hu nh khng cn c s dng nh vy,  tip ni cho vic m u mt cu chuyn, th hin s hiu khch, nhit thnh, ngi ta thng bt u bng vic mi tr, mt kiu vn minh mi m khi giao tip. Ung tr nghim nhin tr nn thng dng hn, dng tr  i khch, i bn,  bn chuyn lm n, chuyn i, chuyn o Dn d, tr li thnh nn mt loi hnh ngh thut c o, mt vn ha rt c trng c mi ngi yu chung, nghin cu, nht l  gii tr v nhng nm gn y. T , cng  hnh thnh nhiu  ngha, nhiu quan nim khc nhau cho vic ung tr.</p>\r\n<p>Bch Lc Mai l mt nh vn n tn tui ti Giang Nam (Trung Quc) vi vn phong thanh m, nh nhng v tinh t, trong tc phm Nhn sinh l mt bnh thin tr, b vit:</p>\r\n<p>Sau ny mi bit, trong lng chng sinh, tr c mi v khc nhau. Th tr mi dng nc tinh khit un si trong bnh , qun quanh gia rng v mi ca tr khch, ung xong, c ngi cm thy ng nh sinh mnh, cng c ngi thy nht nh gi mt.</p>\r\n<p>Tr c m nht, c nng lnh, cng c bun vui. Dng mt tri tim trn tc  thng tr, kh trnh khi ch chm chm vo sc, hng, v, m thiu i mt phn thanh m v cht phc. Tr c ngn vn v, thm ch ha ln vi th s v tnh cm. Dng mt tri tim siu thot  thng tr, th c th ung dung tn hng s tnh lng tuyt m ca my bay ngang tri, nc bic khng gn sng.</p>\r\n<p>Qua , tc gi cng  lm nt hn hnh nh bc xut trn thng s  chn thin mn yn tnh, tay nng chn tr, phong thi an nhin, nh nhng, thanh thot, mc cho tri nng hay ma, b mc bao nhiu c-mt ngoi th s. B mc,  y khng phi ngha nh chng ta t b ht tt c vic ca ngi, m l b nhng g nn b v ch lm nhng g ng lm, v hnh phc ca mnh, ca ngi ng theo tinh thn trong nh Pht. Trong tinh thn ca nhng ngi hc Pht, ung tr cng l mt cch  tu hc, mt cch  chng ta thc tp, c th gi chung l Thin tr. Tr c v m c nht, cng nh ngi trong i, vic trong i, c thng-ght, bun-vui, c tt-xu, c sanh-dit</p>\r\n<p>Nhn nhn nh th  ta c th vt qua bc tng ca nh kin v mi th l phi nh th ny, khng c nh th kia, vt qua c nhng u lo mun phin ng tr trong chng ta trc v thng i thay. Thi gian nh nc tri, tt c mi tng duyn trong i ny cng s n ci hi kt. Mi th biu hin trong cuc i cng ch l nh vy, nh vy n din ra theo nhiu hnh thc, a chiu, a dng, mc  phc tp cng khc nhau.</p>\r\n<p>Tr, t tnh thng dng trong dn gian l dng  tip i khch, nhiu ngi coi tr nh mt ngi bn tri m, tri k  nhng khi bun vui, khi mang trong mnh ni nim trc n ca cuc sng, h li ngi bn chn tr mt cch cn trng, sn sng s chia, gii by v thnh tht vi chnh mnh hn. Khi ung tr, ngi ta cm nhn v tr thm thu t ni tm can ca h, gip cun tri i nhng mun phin. Ung tr l mt cch  sng chm. Cng c ngi li ngh, ung tr s tr nn bn rn. Nhng gi tr nm  gia nhng bn rn  nhn nhn, tm ra con ngi chn tht ca chnh mnh.  cn l mt cch  t hon thin mnh.</p>\r\n<p>S d tr ngon, hp dn l  ci v, ng sau v ng cht th hi ngt cn vng li ni c hng. Thng tr,  ta bit mnh c kh nng  n nhn c tt c v ng-thanh-m-nht, y  hng v ca cuc sng. Ging nh trong cuc i, kh au v hnh phc tng tc vi nhau, nng ta nhau, nh nhn nhn c kh au th con ngi mi thy c gi tr ca hnh phc. Khng c bn th khng c sen - s tng tc  biu hin khp ni, khp chn trong mi mi  nim, li ni, tng hnh ng. Ngi con Pht c phc duyn hc c  ngi Cha, ngi Thy ca mnh vi sui ngun T bi, Tr tu, H x, hc c cch t mnh nng ta mnh, ch tc hnh phc. T nhng bi hc qu gi , ngi ta bit ghi li trong t tng  khi nhn vo o, vo i, vo mt c th, hay vo tt c vi i mt bit thng yu, vi tm nhn cao rng. Vic ung tr l cch chng ta gi gn, thc tp phng php phng h khi su cn (mt, tai, mi, li, thn, ) ca mnh, khi tip xc vi su trn (sc, thinh, hng, v, xc, php) bn ngoi...</p>\r\n<p>Huynh  ng tu  trong cha thi thong cng hi nhau ng ng, sau mt bui thin tr: Hm nay ung tr, anh / ch / em c thy hnh phc khng?. Ch vi mt cu thm hi vy, chng ta s c c hi nhn li mnh, v khng  vng  ci ch l tr khng thm, khng ngon, mu khng p - mt cch ung tr bng mi, bng mt.  thc c iu , mi chng ta nn thc tp chnh nim trong vic ung tr. Vi con ng chnh nim, d cho bn l ai,  u, lm g, ang i, ng hay nm, ngi, nht rau, mc nc nng lng chnh nim bnh an trong thc ti, khin bn lun cm thy an lc, hnh phc. Cho n khi bn ngi mt mnh (c m) hay ngi quy qun bn nhau trong cc bui thin tr, bn u cm thy d chu hn.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471272803.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p>Ngi vui cnh s vui, ngi an thy cnh cng an, tt c do nng lng trong tm ca chng ta biu hin nn. Ngi mt mnh, ta hc cch nhn li mnh, phn quan t k. Ngi ng ngi, ta hc c cch lng nghe, chia s chuyn tu tp, xy dng tnh huynh ,  thc c s c mt cng nh tnh thng ca nhng ngi xung quanh chng ta. Ung tr, ta hc cch ngi an nhin, vng chi nh ni, th vo th ra tnh lng, hc cch mm ci tht nhiu trong mi pht giy, nhn cuc sng theo hng tch cc hn, ti p hn. Duy nht  ci tm:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Tm nh ha s kho</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>V th gii mun mu.</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>(Kinh Hoa nghim)</em></p>\r\n<p>Mi tr - ung tr, vi nt p phong tc truyn thng c xa , chng ta nn pht trin vn ha tr trong x hi rng ln bng cch ngi li cng nhau trong yn lng, tnh thc, mt cch  bc vo con ng hnh phc. Hng tr y s bay i khp ni, khp chn dn gian ha quyn vi ci hng ci v ca t ti v gii thot.</p>\r\n<p>Bnh minh nng ln, hong hn nng tt. Ti khng mun phin. Bnh yn sng v chiu, nu chng qu mong cu ta chng phi kh au. n cho mt ngy sang, vi mt chn tr trong hai tay, trong tnh lng, trong s an tr. Cuc sng vn khng phi l bn rn m ch ti v chng ta cha chu b, cha chu dng li m li c mang vc thm nhng lao xao. Ung tr, l mt nt p rt dung d, rt t ti, m cht th, cht thin, cht ngh thut, m  cht liu sng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Tr thm bay khi th khng ch</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Th ch tr ln tn nh my.</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>(Thin s Thch Nht Hnh)</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Hay l ca mt tc gi khc:</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Ni l ni, sng l sng</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Thin l mt tch tr nng trn tay.</em></p>\r\n<p>Nh vy, Thin v Tr  c duyn c gn kt vi nhau t rt lu i. Ung tr cng l mt cch tu tp. Vi ci tnh , ngi xut gia thng ly tr lm bn. Cho bn cng chnh l cho ti. Xin hy trn qu tng giy pht ny!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><br /><strong>Thch n Tnh Tm</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:53:44.899605	2016-08-20 12:27:30.859783	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
72	DSC00296_65939.jpg	Ti Sao Trng Chui Li Dng 108 Ht?	<p><strong>Nh vy, trong ba i ta  to thnh 108 th phin no  lm hnh trang trong on ng sanh t khng cng tn. Cho nn, by gi chng ta ln trng ht 108 ln trong khi nim Pht, l quyt tm on tr 108 mn phin no m mnh  to trong ba i. on tr 108 mn phin no cng c ngha l lm cho su cn thanh tnh.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pht gio nhn vo v tr nhn sinh, khng phi l duy vt, khng phi duy tm, cng khng phi l duy thn. M Pht gio nhn vo s hnh thnh ca con ngi  ba trng thi kt hp nhau l tm, sinh v vt l. Hay ni bng danh t Pht hc l s duyn hp ca ng un, t i; hoc cn, trn v thc. Cn l ni v sinh l, trn l vt l, v thc l tm l. Cn, trn v thc t hi nhau  tn ti. Nu la mt ch cn hai th th gii s khng tn ti. Vy cn, trn, thc l g?</p>\r\n<p>Cn l: mt, tai, mi, li, thn v . Trn l: sc, thanh, hng, v, xc v php. Thc l: nhn thc, nh thc, t thc, thit thc, thn thc v  thc. T ni su cn tip xc su trn sanh ra su thc. Thc to tc vng ng, to nghip hoc thin hoc c  tri ln trong su no lun hi. D nh mt nhn thy sc p ca mt ngi (nam hoc n), lin khi tm say m, t ni m m sc p m to nn hnh nghip. Cho n tai nghe m thanh, mi ngi mi thm, thn chm xc nhng ch trn lng mm mi,  suy ngh ght, thng, hn, thLc cn l cng c sai khin ca lc thc  to tc hnh nghip thin hoc c. T ni hnh nghip tch t cha nhm mang i trong su no lun hi, t qu kh n hin ti, v, s tip din trong tng lai;  chu kh trong vng lun hi.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1471273007.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="835" height="626" /></p>\r\n<p>Qu kh do su cn khng thanh tnh, chy theo trn cnh khi ln m trc to nghip: tham, sn, si, mn, nghi, c kin. V trong i v lai ta li cng theo con ng c to nghip sanh t tham, sn,  ny m i.</p>\r\n<p>T ni mt thy sc to nn su mn cn bn phin no: tham, sn, si, mn, nghi, c kin; cho n mt, tai, mi, li, thn v , mi cn u to nn su phin no cn bn ging nhau: tham, sn, si, mn, nghi, c kin. Mi cn chng ta c su th cn bn phin no, v; nh vy, su gic quan  to nn 36 th phin no trong i sng thng ngy.</p>\r\n<p>Do , nh trn  ni cuc i ca chng ta lin tc ni tip trong ba i t qu kh n hin ti v tng lai. Nh vy, trong ba i ta  to thnh 108 th phin no  lm hnh trang trong on ng sanh t khng cng tn. Cho nn, by gi chng ta ln trng ht 108 ln trong khi nim Pht, l quyt tm on tr 108 mn phin no m mnh  to trong ba i. on tr 108 mn phin no cng c ngha l lm cho su cn thanh tnh.</p>\r\n<p>Su cn t trc n nay chy theo su trn, khi ln su mn phin no cn bn: tham, sn, si, . by gi ta ln trng ht nim Pht, l ngn cn khng cho su cn vng ng chy theo cnh trn, v, gip cho su cn quay v vi t tnh. Su cn cm nhn su trn sanh ra su thc, thc vng ng to nghip lun lu trong vng sng cht. Ln trng nim Pht l khng cho cn nhim vi trn; cn khng nhim trn tc cn thanh tnh, cn  tnh th nghip khng cn, nghip  dt sanh t on dit. y gi l gii thot, hoc vng sanh v th gii Cc Lc ca Pht A Di .</p>\r\n<p>Thu trit c l o nh vy th khng cn vng nim phn bit php tu ny hn php tu khc. Hoc cho rng c Thch Ca xa kia do Thin Ta m thnh Pht ch khng phi nim Pht m thnh chnh qu. Hoc cn t v vng nim hn khi tuyn b rng: thy T  khuyn bo ta trong thi mt php ly php mn nim Pht cu vng sanh l trn trnh, khng thch ng vi li Pht dy.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Thch Phc Nhn</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:57:13.326057	2016-08-20 12:28:08.082004	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-18 00:00:00
73	hinh-nen-hoa-sen-dep-full-hd-1.jpg	V Sao Ngi Lng Thin C i Gp Ni Bun V Trc Tr?	<p>Ti  tm mt ngi thy thng thi v o hnh xin ch bo: -V sao nhng ngi lng thin nh con li thng xuyn cm thy kh, m nhng ngi c li vn sng tt vy? <br /> <br />Thy hin ha nhn ti tr li:</p>\r\n<p><br />- Nu mt ngi trong lng cm thy kh, iu  ni ln rng trong tm ngi ny c tn ti mt iu c tng ng. Nu mt ngi trong ni tm khng c iu c no, nh vy, ngi ny s khng c cm gic thng kh. V th, cn c theo o l ny, con thng cm thy kh, ngha l ni tm ca con c tn ti iu c, con khng phi l mt ngi lng thin tht s. M nhng ngi con cho rng l ngi c, li cha hn l ngi tht s c. Mt ngi c th vui v m sng, t nht ni r ngi ny khng phi l ngi c tht s.</p>\r\n<p><br />C cm gic nh b xc phm, ti khng phc, lin ni:</p>\r\n<p><br />-Con sao c th l ngi c c? Gn y, tm con rt lng thin m!</p>\r\n<p><br />Thy tr li:</p>\r\n<p><br />-Ni tm khng c th khng cm thy kh, con  cm thy kh, ngha l trong tm con ang tn ti iu c. Con hy ni v ni kh ca con, ta s ni cho con bit, iu c no ang tn ti trong con.</p>\r\n<p><br />Ti ni:</p>\r\n<p><br />-Ni kh ca con th rt nhiu! C khi cm thy tin lng thu nhp rt thp, nh  cng khng  rng, thng xuyn c cm gic thua thit bi vy trong tm con thng cm thy khng thoi mi, cng hy vng mau chng c th ci bin tnh trng ny; trong x hi, khng t ngi cn bn khng c vn ha g, li c th lng qun bc triu, con khng phc; mt tr thc vn ha nh con, mi thng li ch c mt cht thu nhp, tht s l khng cng bng; ngi thn nhiu lc khng nghe li khuyn ca con, con cm thy khng thoi mi</p>\r\n<p><br />C nh vy, ln lt ti k ht vi thy nhng ni thng kh ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p><br />Thy gt u, mm ci, mt n ci rt nhn t n hu, ngi t tn ni vi ti:</p>\r\n<p><br />- Thu nhp hin ti ca con   nui sng chnh con v gia nh. Con cn c c phng c  , cn bn l  khng phi lu lc ni u ng x ch, ch l din tch hi nh mt cht, con hon ton c th khng phi chu nhng kh tm y.</p>\r\n<p><br />-Nhng, bi v ni tm con c lng tham i vi tin ti v ca ci, cho nn mi cm thy kh. Loi lng tham ny l c tm, nu con c th vt b c tm y, con s khng v nhng iu  m cm thy kh na.</p>\r\n<p>- Trong x hi c nhiu ngi thiu vn ha nhng li pht ti, ri con li cm thy khng phc, y chnh l tm  k. Tm  k cng l mt loi c tm. Con t cho mnh l c vn ha, nn cn phi c thu nhp cao, y chnh l tm ngo mn. Tm ngo mn cng l c tm. Cho rng c vn ha th phi c thu nhp cao, y chnh l tm ngu si; bi v vn ha khng phi l cn nguyn ca s giu c, kip trc lm vic thin mi l nguyn nhn cho s giu c ca kip ny. Tm ngu si cng l c tm!</p>\r\n<p><br />- Ngi thn khng nghe li khuyn ca con, con cm thy khng thoi mi, y l khng rng lng. Du l ngi thn ca con, nhng h vn c t tng v quan im ca ring mnh, ti sao li cng cu t tng v quan im ca h bt phi ging nh con? Khng rng lng s dn n hp hi. Tm hp hi cng l c tm.</p>\r\n<p><br />S ph tip tc mm ci:</p>\r\n<p><br />- Lng tham, tm  k, ngo mn, ngu si, hp hi, u l nhng c tm. Bi v ni tm ca con cha ng nhng c tm y, nn nhng thng kh mi tn ti trong con. Nu con c th loi tr nhng c tm , nhng thng kh kia s tan thnh my khi.</p>\r\n<p><br />- Con em nim vui v tha mn ca mnh t ln tin thu nhp v ca ci, con hy ngh li xem, cn bn con s khng cht i v cht cng; nhng ngi giu c kia, tht ra cng ch l khng cht i v cht cng. Con  nhn ra cha, con c hnh phc hay khng, khng da trn s giu c bn ngoi, m da trn thi  sng ca con mi l quyt nh. Nm chc tng giy pht ca cuc i, sng vi thi  lc quan, ha i, cn c  thay th lng tham, tnh  k v ch k; ni tm ca con s dn chuyn ha, dn thay i  thanh thn v bnh an hn.</p>\r\n<p><br />-Trong x hi, nhiu ngi khng c vn ha nhng li giu c, con hy nn v h m vui v, nn cu chc h cng giu c hn, cng c nhiu nim vui hn mi ng. Ngi khc t c, phi vui nh ngi  chnh l con; ngi khc mt i, ng ci trn ni au ca h. Ngi nh vy mi c coi l ngi lng thin! Cn con, gi thy ngi khc giu con li thiu vui, y chnh l tm  k. Tm  k chnh l mt loi tm rt khng tt, phi kin quyt tiu tr!</p>\r\n<p><br />- Con cho rng, con c ch hn ngi, t cho l gii. y chnh l tm ngo mn. C cu ni rng: Ngo mn cao sn, bt sinh c thy (ngha l: ngn ni cao m ngo mn, s khng to nn loi nc tt) ngi khi  sinh lng ngo mn, th i vi thiu st ca bn thn s nh c mt m khng trng, v vy, khng th nhn thy bn thn c bao nhiu c tm, sao c th thay i  tt hn. Cho nn, ngi ngo mn s t mnh ng ca chn ng s tin b ca mnh. Ngoi ra, ngi ngo mn s thng cm thy mt mt, dn dn s chuyn thnh t ti. Mt ngi ch c th nui dng lng khim tn, lun bo tr tm thi ha i t bi, ni tm mi c th cm thy trn y v an vui.</p>\r\n<p><br />-Kip trc lm vic thin mi chnh l nguyn nhn cho s giu c  kip ny, (trng da c da, trng u c u). M ngi thng khng hiu c nhn qu, trng da li mun c u, trng u li mun c da, y l th hin ca s ngu mui. Ch c ngi chm hc Pht Php, mi c c tr hu chn chnh, mi tht s hiu c nhn qu, quy lut tun hon ca vn vt trong v tr, ni tm mi c th minh t thu trit.  t , bit lm th no la chn t tng, hnh vi v li ni ca mnh cho ph hp. Ngi nh vy, mi c th theo nh sng hng n nh sng, t yn vui hng n yn vui.</p>\r\n<p><br />-Bu tri c th bao dung ht thy, nn rng ln v bin, ung dung t ti; mt t c th chu ng ht thy, nn trn y s sng, vn vt m chi! Mt ngi sng trong Th gii ny, khng nn ty tin xem thng hnh vi v li ni ca ngi khc. Du l ngi thn, cng khng nn mang tm cng cu, cn phi ty duyn t ti! Vnh vin dng tm lng thin gip  ngi khc, nhng khng nn cng cu iu g.<br />-Nu tm mt ngi c th rng ln nh bu tri m bao dung vn vt, ngi  sao c th kh y?</p>\r\n<p><br />V thy kh knh ni xong nhng iu ny, tip tc nhn ti vi nh mt y nhn t v bao dung  lng.</p>\r\n<p><br />Ngi im lng hi luxa nay ti vn cho mnh l mt ngi rt lng thin, mi n lc ny, phi! ch n lc ny, ti mi bit c trong ti cn c mt con ngi rt xu xa, rt c c! Bi v ni tm ca ti cha nhng iu c, nn ti mi cm thy nhiu au kh n th. Nu ni tm ca ti khng c, sao ti c th kh ch?</p>\r\n<p><br />Xin cm t thy, nu khng c ngi khai th dy bo, con vnh vin s khng bit c mt ngi xu xa nh vy ang tn ti trong con!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Tm L Minh </strong><br /> <br /><strong>(Theo phatgiaovietnam.vn)</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-15 14:59:10.126371	2016-08-20 12:28:25.90354	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-27 00:00:00
