120	5_perks_of_online_meditation.jpg	Nhng Li ch Ca Thin nh	<p><strong>Nu l ngi lo u, thin nh c th lm cho bn bnh tnh v tm n tm an bnh.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ngy nay, nhiu ngi khp ni trn th gii, bt lun l theo tn gio no, h u  thc c li ch ca thin nh. Mc ch gn ca thin l  rn luyn tm v dng tm mt cch c hiu qu cao trong i sng thng nht. Mc ch ti hu ca thin l  gii thot ra khi sinh t lun hi. Mc d thin nh c xem l mt vic lm kh nht, nhng nhng li ch tch cc th c th t c ngay trong gi pht hin ti nu chng ta chuyn tm thc hnh. Nhng li ch ca thin nh c th c tm tt nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>- Nu l ngi bn rn, thin nh c th gip bn bung b cng thng v tm n s th th.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu l ngi lo u, thin nh c th lm cho bn bnh tnh v tm n tm an bnh.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l ngi c nhiu vn , thin nh c th gip bn pht trin lng can m v ngh lc  i u v vt qua.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn thiu t tin, thin nh c th gip bn c c t tin (t tin l b quyt thnh cng trong cuc sng).</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn c tm lo s, thin nh c th gip bn thu hiu thc cht ca nhng vn  khin bn hong lon, lc  bn c th khc phc tm lo s.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn lun bt mn v khng c g trong i sng lm bn tha mn, thin nh c th gip bn to c hi  pht trin v duy tr s hi lng vi chnh mnh.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn hoi nghi v khng quan tm n cch sng tn gio, thin nh c th gip bn vt qua thi  hoi nghi v thy c nhng gi tr thc tin trong o php.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn tht bi v kh s do thiu hiu bit v tnh trng bp bnh ca i sng v th gii, thin nh c th hng dn v gip bn hiu bit tnh ph du ca cc php th gian.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l ngi giu c, thin nh c th gip bn nhn chn bn cht sang trng, cao c ca bn v cch s dng n khng nhng v chnh hnh phc ca bn m cn v hnh phc tha nhn.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l ngi ngho kh, thin nh c th gip bn pht trin s tri tc v khng cha chp lng ganh t trong lng vi nhng ai giu c hn bn.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l mt thanh nin ang  "ng ba ng" khng bit r v u, thin nh c th gip bn tm thy chnh o  i n mc ch m bn  chn.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l mt ngi ng tui, chn ngn cuc sng, thin nh c th mang li cho bn s hiu bit cuc sng su sc hn; s hiu bit ny ln lt s lm vi i nhng ni au ca bn v gia tng nim vui sng.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn nng tnh, bn c th pht trin sc mnh  khc phc nhc im ca tnh nng ny, th hn  tr thnh ngi im m v tnh to hn.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn ganh t, bn c th hiu rng nhng thi  tinh thn tiu cc khng bao gi ng gp bt c iu g cho li ch ca bn.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn khng th gim thiu tham i i vi cc dc lc, bn c th hc cch tr thnh ngi lm ch nhng dc lc ca bn.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn nghin ru hoc ma ty, bn c th vt qua thi quen nguy him <br />tng lm cho bn n l.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l ngi hp hi, bn c th pht trin tr sng sut  mang li li ch cho chnh mnh, bn b v gia nh; v trnh s hiu lm.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn kh s t nhng hn lon nh nhng chng suy nhc thn kinh v xo trn tinh thn, thin nh c th lm khi dy nhng nng lc tch cc trong thn tm bn  phc hi sc khe, c bit nu chng thuc nhng vn  thn kinh.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l ngi nhu nhc hoc c tnh mc cm t ti, thin nh c th gip bn pht trin lng can m v khc phc nhc im.</p>\r\n<p>- Nu bn l ngi sng sut, thin nh s hng dn bn n tr tu cao siu. Lc  bn s thy chn tng ca cc php, v khng cn chp theo hnh tng bn ngoi na...</p>\r\n<p>y l mt s iu li ch thit thc pht xut t vic thc hnh thin nh. Nhng li ch ny khng th rao bn trong cc ca hiu hay ca hng bch ha m bn mun c th phi thc tp thin v rn luyn tm mi ngy. Tm l cha kha m cnh ca hnh phc v cng l cha kha m cnh ca kh au. Hiu c tm v kho dng tm l cng vic hn hn i sng thanh bnh v tha mn.</p>\r\n<p>Mt s ngi cho rng thc tp thin rt kh v khi hnh thin h gp phi lon ng ri cho rng khng ai c th on tr lon ng y. Thc ra, trong th gii chng ta ang sng khng c ni no m khng c lon ng. Nhng vi s kho lo v hiu r s vt mt cch hp l th chng ta s bit cch bo v tm ca mnh, chng li bt k hnh thc xo trn no. c Pht dy: "Khi bn thy bt k s vt g, bn cng ng chp cht vo s vt  m phi dng tm  pht trin s cm nhn su sc vo bn cht tht ca s vt hin tng".</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1472482903.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p>Hy quan st mi vt vi s r bit. Tt hn bn khng nn m say vo n nu bn tht s mun gi tm yn tnh. Hy  cho tm t do khng dnh mc vo mt th no. Khi nghe m thanh d vui hay bun, ch nghe vi s r bit. Bn phi c chnh nim  trnh s tc ng ca m thanh, lc  tm ca bn mi khng b vng mc vo nhng g mnh ang c. Bn phi rn luyn tm  duy tr s bnh yn ni ti.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi cnh v s hng phn thng lm cho tm b xo trn nn  nim tham lam, ganh t, sn si, vng tng s pht sinh; chng lm cho tm  nhim. Thin l phng tin gip ta bo v tm. Ngi kho dng cng, khi tp trung vo bt k s vt hin tng no d vui hay bun m vn khng c lng tham m hay th hn pht khi.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ta thng dnh nhiu thi gian  chm lo cho thn th nh tm ra, git o qun, n ung, trang im, th gin... nhng th hi chng ta  dnh bao nhiu thi gian  quan tm n tm?</p>\r\n<p>Nhiu cn bnh v chng ri lon c th trnh c nu chng ta bit dnh thi gian thc tp thin, rn luyn tm  gi tm yn tnh. Nhiu ngi khng tin hoc do li bing khng hnh thin, khng am tng v thin nn cho rng thin ch l lng ph thi gian.</p>\r\n<p>Thin c th gip con ngi vt qua thn bnh v duy tr sc khe thng qua s pht trin ca tm. Khi tm thoi mi, chng ta d dng tip thu kin thc hoc nhy bn hn. Khi tm cha  tng xu, nhng tp nhim ny c th gy tn thng thn th. Y hc ngy nay cng chp nhn rng tm l ngun gc ca cc loi bnh v tng t tm cng c th c dng  iu tr bnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Thch Qung t dch theo Meditation the only way</strong><br /><strong>Ngun: giacngo.vn</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-29 15:01:59.851158	2016-08-30 16:14:01.062312	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
90	1.JPG	Cha Linh Quang Khai i Hng Chung	<p>Sng 26-1-2013, khong 700 Pht t  v d l khai i hng chung v tng kt Pht s nm 2012 ti cha Linh Quang (x Ph Ha, H.nh Qun, ng Nai).</p>\r\n<p>i hng chung c trng lng 1 tn c c ti cha hi thng 11-2012, do cc ngh nhn n t thnh ph Hu thc hin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471451998.JPG" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>i c Thch Hu Tr khai i hng chung</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><img src="/uploads/editor/1471451988.JPG" /></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Pht t nhip tm tham d bui l</em></p>\r\n<p>Sau nghi thc si tnh, tr ch, nhng ting chung u tin c ngn ln trong khng gian thanh bnh, tnh lng thc tnh mi ngi tinh tn tu hnh  mau vt ra ngoi vng ti li, ti tm, kh au trong vng lun hi, thc tnh tm m mui ca chng sinh.</p>\r\n<p>Trong bui tng kt Pht s, nm qua nh cha  lm nhiu cng tc ni bt nh: c i hng chung c trng lng 1 tn, dng mt nh mt sau cha c din tch 100m2, lm 300m ng giao thng nng thn, tng qu t thin 5 t vi hn 500 phn qu tr gi hn 80 triu ng, h tr gn 20 sut hc bng cho hc sinh ngho vi tr gi 20 triu ng.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Gia nh Pht t c duy tr vi 60 on sinh, trong nm, cha  t chc l quy y hng trm Pht t, t chc cc ngy l ln, cc ngy va trang nghim. Hng thng u c cc kha tu cho Pht t gn xa.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471451975.JPG" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Tng qu Tt Qu T ti ngi ngho</em></p>\r\n<p>c bit, cha cng  thnh lp i Thanh nin Thin nguyn vi 18 thnh vin c tinh thn t nguyn tham gia cng tc t thin, gip  nhng gia nh kh khn.</p>\r\n<p>Nhn dp xun v, Ban T thin cha Linh Quang  trao 70 phn qu cho cc gia nh neo n, mi phn qu tr gi 120.000 gm go, m gi, nc tng, gia v</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Tin, nh: Thin Ng</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-17 16:40:26.614399	2016-08-20 12:57:07.580877	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	t	2013-01-26 00:00:00
94	40.jpg	Cha Linh Quang: Cng Tc Chun B Mng i L Pht n - PL 2558	<p><strong>Ha trong khng kh hn hoan ca c nc n i l Vesak LHQ 2014 ang din ra ln th hai ti Vit Nam, nhng ngy va qua, Ch tn c Tng v Pht t cha Linh Quang ang tch cc trong cng tc chun b cho i l Pht n sp ti.</strong></p>\r\n<p>T u thng T m lch, cc hot ng cho n i l Pht n  c tin hnh. C phn, bng rn, biu ng c trang tr rc r trn cc con ng dn vo cha. Ni bt nht v cng phu nht l qu trnh lm l i v xe hoa. Tnh n thi im ny, nhng khu cui cng ca cng tc chun b cho i l  gn nh hon tt.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sau y l mt s hnh nh cng tc chun b mng i l Pht n ti cha Linh Quang:</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453460.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453463.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453465.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453467.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453469.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453472.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453474.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453477.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453478.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453480.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453482.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453484.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1471453486.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/14714