130	hinh-nen-phat-giao-dep-danh-cho-may-tinh-hinh-anh-4.jpg	Tp Thoi	<p><strong>Trong qu trnh tu tp, ai cng bit vic gi chnh nim  tnh ha khu nghip l iu rt kh. Tp thoi (ni linh tinh) l cn bnh kh cha m li d ly lan. Nn d b ngi tu ch ng ngn chn v gip tt nhng nu c c hi tp thoi lin bng pht, k c trong nhng hi chng T-kheo  t ca Th Tn.</strong><br />Chnh ng hay ni nng nh Chnh php l mt php tu cn bn thuc Bt chnh o. Ch cn mt chnh nim th mi lun bn, ni nng u theo nghip m biu hin, ri vo tp thoi. Ni t th sai t, nn trc khi ni cn un li by ln hay mun bn lun nn bn lun v mi vic cng c mi khng ri vo tp thoi. Hy nghe Th Tn dy v s v ch, khng dn n php lnh ca vic hay ni linh tinh:</p>\r\n<p>Mt thi Pht  nc X-v, rng K-, vn Cp C c.</p>\r\n<p>By gi, phn ng cc T-kheo, sau khi th trai xong u t tp ti ging ng Ph Hi, cng nhau bn lun v ngha ny: Bn lun v chuyn y phc, trang sc, n ung; bn lun v nhng chuyn chin tranh, gic cp ca nc ln bang; bn lun v ru ch, dm dc, ng dc; bn lun v ca v, k nhc. Nhng chuyn v ch nh th nhiu khng th tnh k.</p>\r\n<p>By gi, Th Tn dng thin nh nghe cc T-kheo bn lun nhng chuyn y, lin i n ging ng Ph Hi, hi cc T-kheo:</p>\r\n<p>- Cc Thy nhm hp  y bn lun chuyn g?</p>\r\n<p>Khi y, cc T-kheo bch Pht:</p>\r\n<p>- Chng con nhm hp  y cng bn lun nhng vic v ch nh th.</p>\r\n<p>c Pht bo cc T-kheo:</p>\r\n<p>- Thi, thi! Cc T-kheo, ch bn lun vic y. V sao? Nhng iu lun bn y khng c  ngha v cng khng dn n php lnh. Khng do nhng iu lun bn ny m c tu Phm hnh; khng n c ch tch dit, Nit-bn; khng c o Sa-mn bnh ng.  l nhng iu lun bn ca th tc, khng phi lun ca ng chnh. Cc Thy  la th tc, xut gia hc o, khng nn suy ngh v nhng lun bi hoi.</p>\r\n<p>Nu cc Thy mun bn lun, nn bn lun v mi vic cng c. Th no l mi? L sing nng tinh tn; t mun bit ; c tm dng mnh; a vn, c th thuyt php cho ngi; khng s st kinh khng; y  gii lut; thnh tu chnh nh; thnh tu tr tu; thnh tu gii thot; thnh tu gii thot tri kin. Nu cc Thy mun bn lun th nn bn lun v mi iu ny.</p>\r\n<p>V sao? V chng thm nhun tt c, ch li nhiu, c tu Phm hnh, c n ch tch dit, Nit-bn. Hm nay cc Thy l con nh ho tc,  xut gia hc o, nn suy ngh v mi iu ny. Lun ny l lun ca Chnh php, xa la ng c. Nh th, ny cc T-kheo, hy hc iu ny!</p>\r\n<p>By gi, cc T-kheo nghe Pht dy xong, vui v vng lm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>(Kinh Tng nht A-hm, tp III, phm Thin c, </strong><br /><strong>VNCPHVN n hnh, 1998, tr.311)</strong></p>\r\n<p>V sao ngi tu phi trnh nhng iu lun bn ca th tc? Thc ra lun bn  trau di v nng cao tri thc th gian cng rt tt, cn thit cho cuc sng nhng n khng dn ngi tu n cc php lnh, khng i n Phm hnh, khng n c ch tch dit. y l ch ngi tu hng n gii thot, Nit-bn cn ht sc lu tm.</p>\r\n<p>Ngi tu th nn ni chuyn tu, khng ni chuyn i m ch bn lun v mi vic cng c, chnh l li cn dn ca Th Tn. Bi li ni, suy ngh v hnh ng lun gn b mt thit vi nhau nn bn lun nhiu v th s vi v vn bin ng s khin tm t  nhim, nng n thm.</p>\r\n<p>Thc tp chnh ng, ni nng c chnh nim, trnh i nhng cu chuyn phim khng c ch cho tu hc l iu m ngi tu cn phi thnh tu  tng bc hng n thnh thi, an nh v gii thot.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Qung Tnh</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-29 15:46:08.169725	2016-08-30 16:30:57.067092	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-07 00:00:00
