135	B10_2_.jpg	Kinh Hoa Nghim Vi Php Mn Tnh 	<p><strong>Khi ni n Php mn Tnh  ngi ta u ngh n cc kinh Di , kinh V Lng Th, Kinh Qun V Lng Th, v Lun Vng Sanh Tnh  ca B Tt Th Thn hoc kinh Nim Pht Ba La Mt l cc b kinh tng yu ni v Php mn Tnh . t ngi bit rng kinh Hoa Nghim l b kinh ni v php nht tha vin gio cng ni n Tnh , dy tu Tnh , khuyn nguyn sanh v th gii Cc Lc.</strong></p>\r\n<p>iu ny cho thy nguyn sanh Tnh  khng ch l bn nguyn ca thng nhn m cng chnh l bn nguyn ca bc thng cn i tr. Nhng Hoa Nghim ni n Tnh  nh th no ? Ngi tu Tnh  theo Hoa Nghim c ging nh ngi tu Tnh  thng thng hay khng ? C chng tri hay tng ng cng mt bn nguyn?</p>\r\n<p>Trc ht, kinh Hoa Nghim cho ta bit tt c quc  u ty nghip lc sanh hay do cng c nguyn lc ca ch Pht thnh tu. Hoa Nghim ng trn Php Gii Nht Chn nhn thy Tht tng tt c Php l Chn Khng Diu Hu, tm v cnh tng quan nh nht. Tm thanh tnh th cnh thanh tnh, tm nhim  th d cnh trang nghim cng bin thnh u trc xu xa.</p>\r\n<p>c bit Hoa Nghim nhn mnh n tm quan trng ca ch Pht v B Tt. Cc Ngi n ci no, ni  bin thnh thanh tnh. Khi cc Ngi nhp dit hay ra i th ci  ht trang nghim. Nh vy, kinh Hoa Nghim ch r s hnh thnh cc th gii nhim tnh cho ta thy. c bit v ci nc Tnh  th th gii Hoa tng gm c v lng th gii cng hnh thnh.</p>\r\n<p>Ta B hay Cc Lc cng ch l mt trong v s ci nc trong Hoa Tng th gii. Trong th gii , c v lng cnh Pht trang nghim thanh tnh, ch khng phi ch c mt th gii Cc Lc.</p>\r\n<p>Th nhng, chng sanh ci Ta B phn ng ch kh hp vi Cc Lc nn Pht ni r v cnh Cc Lc cho chng sanh tin tu.</p>\r\n<p>Kinh Di  ch tn thn ci Tnh  trang nghim  cho ngi pht khi nim tin, pht nguyn tu hnh, cu sanh Tnh  qua hnh nht tm nim Pht. Kinh V Lng Th ch r tin thn Pht A Di  pht ra 48 li nguyn kin to Cc Lc rc ngi vng sanh, v cnh gii Cc Lc trang nghim thanh tnh, phn nh r chn phm vng sanh cho ngi hc Pht.</p>\r\n<p>Kinh Qun V Lng Th ch 16 php qun cho Vi  Hy cng 500 th n r rng tng tn  qun st nguyn v Cc Lc.</p>\r\n<p>Kinh Nim Pht Ba La Mt ch cn k php tu cho ngi c Chnh nh nim Pht, thnh tu tht tng nim Pht.</p>\r\n<p>Kinh Hoa Nghim cng dy ngi tu tin chc vo Pht, Php, Tng nhng i su hn khi dy ta tu nim Pht, tin Pht vi B  tm, khuyn pht tm hnh i tha cng dng ch Pht nht tm nim Pht bt ng  thy v lng ch Pht, thu sut Php thn bt ng ca Nh Lai, nguyn hnh hnh Pht cu chng Pht o. Cu v Tnh  l  thn cn cng dng thnh chuyn Php lun, hc theo hnh Pht,  vin thnh Pht qu, ch khng phi i nghip vng sanh.</p>\r\n<p>Nim Pht cng l php thit yu u tin m hnh gi mun nhp Php gii phi tu. Thin Ti ng T sau khi c Vn Th B Tt khai th bn tm, ch r Chn tm khuyn hnh B Tt o, tu B Tt hnh i tham hc vi 53 v Thin tri thc. V thy u tin Ngi n cu hc l c Vn T Kheo  dy Ngi Thin Ti Php mn c nim nht thit cnh gii ch Pht tr hu quang minh ph kin, tc dng tm thanh tnh nh ngh tt c cnh gii Pht nh k ni k.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>"Cnh gii Nh Lai nu mun tm,</em><br /><em>Nn tnh  mnh nh h khng,</em><br /><em>Xa la vng tng v chp trc,</em><br /><em>Hng tm n ch chng ngi ngn"</em></p>\r\n<p>Khi tm thanh tnh nht nh th 10 phng ci Pht hin tin, r bit tm Pht khng hai, ngoi tm khng c Pht, y chnh l ch kinh Qun V Lng Th ni : Tm ny l Pht, tm ny lm Pht. Khi r sut l ny th t c tht tng nim Pht bit mnh v Pht ng mt th. Th nhng, Thin Ti ng T nh nim Pht c Php nh khng vi nguyn sanh v Cc Lc m li pht tm cu hnh Pht php, hnh B Tt o, lm li ch chng sanh.</p>\r\n<p>Mi n v Thin tri thc th nm mi ba l Ph Hin mi dy Thin Ti ng T mi hnh nguyn ca mnh, phi thng thn cn ch Pht cng dng, nghe php, thnh chuyn Php lun. Khi Pht sp Nit Bn mi tr th lm an lc chng sanh. Khi Pht sp Nit Bn n hu h phng s.</p>\r\n<p>Hnh tr hu v hnh c   o Ph Hin. Lc mng sp lm chung nguyn sanh Cc Lc th gii ca Pht Di , sen n thy Pht lin c th k o B , y  tr hu, phng tin nguyn lc, lm li ch khp chng sanh gii.</p>\r\n<p>Nh vy, Kinh Hoa Nghim cng hng ngi tu hnh B Tt sanh v Cc Lc nhng khc bit vi cc Kinh khc. Ngi tu Tnh  ch cn tn su vo Pht, tin chc nguyn Pht, pht tm nim Pht, cu sanh Ty Phng l nh nguyn. Do khng c cng c tr hu nguyn lc su dy nn c khi mang nghip vng sanh, sanh v Ty Phng mi chng qu v sanh. Tri v lng kip mi thnh Pht o. C th ni ngi bnh thng tu nim Pht, sanh vo Phm Thnh ng C  chng qu v sanh, pht tm B  tin tu Pht o.</p>\r\n<p>Hnh gi tu theo kinh Hoa Nghim r sut ngun tm cu hnh i tha c pht nguyn lin c vng sanh. Qu tu hnh chc chn vo Thng phm, trc mt Pht lin c th k o B , cnh gii an tr l Tht Bo Trang Nghim . Ngi tu Tnh  chn cnh Ta B u trc nguyn sanh Tnh  an lnh, nng Pht lc tin tu, trc chng v sanh, sau pht B  tm, tu B Tt hnh. Tu theo Hoa Nghim trc cu Diu Php, tri thn hnh o, nguyn sanh Tnh  thn cn cng dng   vin thnh B Tt o, thn hnh t ti, nhp u   trang nghim cu t chng sanh v Tnh  thn cn cng dng hu cn Pht chng vin thnh hnh qu.</p>\r\n<p>Nhn theo mt kha cnh khc, tu theo Hoa Nghim l con ng ca B Tt, hnh theo Tnh  l vic ca Thanh Vn hi hng b  v thng. Tuy lc nhn nh th nhng nu hnh c Tht tng nim Pht, ng c tht l i tha hnh tr no c sai bit. Kinh Php Hoa ni : Php php bnh ng khng c sai bit, tu tt c thin php th vin thnh Pht o. S d c sai khc l do tm hnh nguyn lc chng ng nhau.</p>\r\n<p>Do  khng th ni tu theo Hoa Nghim cao, tu theo Tnh  thp. Nh th, chc chn l Hoa Nghim l con ng vin n  thn chng Pht tha. Hnh gi tu theo Hoa Nghim phi y  tr hu, hnh c,  hnh Ph Hin  khi n ni no th quc   trang nghim thanh tnh.</p>\r\n<p>Ngi tu nim Pht tam mui vin thnh nh B Tt i Th Ch n ni no th ci nc cng trang nghim, su iu vang ng, ri hoa bu ln. Nh vy, nu thu l mu, Hoa Nghim, Tnh  no khc bit. Do cn c chng tnh hnh sai bit khc nhau nn c ngn sai mun khc, cao thp chng ng.</p>\r\n<p>Tm li! kinh Hoa Nghim cng ni v Tnh  nhng ch r cho ta thy nguyn nhn c u tnh v ci ngun hnh thnh th gii. Nu Tnh  l php ph thng cho qun chng th Hoa Nghim dnh cho bc thng cn thng tr. Ngi tu Hoa Nghim phi tu tr hu hnh c, ly nc t bi nui ln tm B , hnh B Tt o  vin thnh Pht o. Ngi tu Tnh  r Pht tc tm nim Pht, nh Pht c gp ch Pht, thn cn nghe php cng dng th cng ln ln thnh Pht khng sai. Phng tin tuy khc, nhng l tnh th ng ng.</p>\r\n<p>c bit ta thy khi vin mn hnh Ph Hin vn cu sanh Tnh , gp Di . ng trn l Di  l th tnh, hnh dng  mn nhng Php thn phi bin nhp mi ph t chng sanh, vin thnh Pht o. Nim Pht cng tr v t tnh. Bao cng c thnh hnh u vin thnh, t c Php thn nh ch Pht khng sai khc. ng hnh c thin sai vn bit, nhng tt c u nhm vin thnh Pht o. Kinh Hoa Nghim  lm cho Diu php Tnh  c r rng sng l. Tng cnh dung thng, u khng la Php gii nht chn. Nguyn tt c ngi tu Pht r sut Hoa Nghim v Tnh  dung thng khng chng tri  cng chng nhp Nht tha Pht o.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Thch Nguyn Bnh</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-29 16:07:54.895908	2016-08-30 16:33:07.490125	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
113	49.jpg	 Gio Hi Trc Thi Duyn	<p><strong>Trong nhng nm gn y, th gii  c nhiu s thay i su sc. Cuc cch mng cng ngh thng tin  tc ng lm thay i nhiu lnh vc.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Th gii khng cn khi nim b chia ct bi nhng tr ngi a l nh trc y; ranh gii gia s ring t v cng cng dng nh b xa nha trong th gii thng tin vi s pht trin ca cc ng dng thng tin c nhn trong mng li ton cu.</p>\r\n<p>Song song , khng hong o c, mi trng sinh thi, nn ha bnh b e da, s bt n trong i sng vn  c li b y n mc  gay gt hn vi nhng cuc khng b nhn danh tn ngng, chin tranh, tai nn thm khc lin tc xy ra   y trn th gii.</p>\r\n<p>Vi Vit Nam chng ta, nh hng ca tnh hnh chung, nn kinh t gp nhiu kh khn, chng ta cn phi i din vi hin tng suy thoi o c li sng, vn ha t pht, t nn x hi gia tng lm nhiu ngi lo lng, bt an. Ton b h thng chnh tr hin nay  nhn thc vn  v ang ra sc iu chnh chnh sch nhm ci thin, xy dng nim tin v to dng s n nh, pht trin.</p>\r\n<p>Vi Gio hi Pht gio VN, 3 nm k t i hi VII (2012) din ra ti H Ni, b my nhn s ca Gio hi cng  c nhiu s thay i.</p>\r\n<p>So vi nhn s c suy tn v suy c ti i hi VII, i ng nhn s Ban Thng trc  c s b sung v thay i nhiu chc danh quan trng. Theo , nhn s cng  c tr ha, c trnh  th hc cao hn, nng lng sc khe di do hn.</p>\r\n<p>Nh t nhng nhim k trc, mt s v gio phm lnh o c tm nhn  ch trng tr ha i ng lnh o Gio hi nhng gp phi mt s tr ngi. iu , hm nay c th ni Gio hi  thc hin c mt phn no.</p>\r\n<p>Tui tr ng ngha vi s nhit tnh v sng to. Vi s b sung v tr ha nhn s nhiu v tr ch cht trong Ban Thng trc Hi ng Tr s v cc ban, ngnh, vin Trung ng Gio hi, hy vng rng Gio hi s c nhng bc chuyn mnh bt kp nhp pht trin chung ca th gii cng nh ca t nc, tnh thc v c gii php tt trc tnh hnh vn di phc tp nhm thc y cc Pht s ca Gio hi vt qua, vn ln mt tm cao mi, xng ng l th h tip ni trong ngi nh Pht gio VN.</p>\r\n<p>Trong ci nhn duyn sinh ca o Pht: <em>Ci ny c th ci kia c, ci ny sinh th ci kia sinh; Ci ny khng c th ci kia khng c, ci ny dit th ci kia dit</em>, bn cnh nhiu thnh tu ng ghi nhn ca th gii, ca t nc cng nh ca Gio hi, lun c nhng khoang lng y thch thc va phc tp cn phi i din v gii quyt.</p>\r\n<p>Trong th gii duyn sinh, thi i no, xa hi no m giai cp lanh o gii quyt c nhng iu nan gii v con ngi v lng tham ca con ngi th nht nh thi i , x hi ... s t c mc tiu l tng v thnh cng. Trong tn gio o c cng vy, bt k thi duyn no, gii lnh o tinh thn vt ln chnh mnh, soi sng tnh t ng, v ng  phng s li lc nhn sinh th nht nh tn gio  c tng trng, xng minh.<br />Trn nhng iu kin thay i  ni, chng ta mong rng Gio hi s c nhng bc tin mi thc y cc lnh vc ca Pht gio pht trin, gp phn vo vic xy dng t nc, xng ng vi truyn thng h quc an dn ca Pht gio VN gn b vi dn tc m Gio hi chng ta t ho l t chc i din v k tha ca lch s.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>HT.Thch Gic Ton</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-20 04:21:32.088018	2016-08-20 12:50:40.414536	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
112	xay_dung_2.jpg	Xy Dng Nim Tin	<p><strong>Chng ta khng th mi ngi nguyn ra bng ti m phi thp ln mt que dim, t  nhn nh sng  n lan rng ra.</strong></p>\r\n<p><br />Theo nh Pht, trong ni tm ti nht vn c nh sng, ni au kh nht vn c tnh yu,  l  ngha tng sinh qua hnh nh quen thuc l sen v bn, hay phin no v b- (tnh thc, gic ng).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471666797.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Nim tin cn mt cht ny ?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chng ta ang sng trong mt th gii nhiu bt an. Ni lo s v chin tranh, i ngho, bt cng hin din  mi ni, t Ukraine n Iraq, t Nga sang M, t Bin ng n a Trung Hi</p>\r\n<p>V mt x hi, nn kinh t vn cn kh khn, li thm cc t nn khc nh cp git, trm cp khng suy gim bao nhiu. Ngi dn c php phng khi ra khi nh vo ban m, cng vi  l tnh trng bo lc gia tng  trong nh cng nh ngoi ng ph. Nhng v trng n ang gia tng gn y nhan nhn trn cc trang mng v xung t trong gia nh, tranh chp trong tha k ti sn, thm ch nhng n mng xut pht t nguyn nhn rt v duyn  lm khng t ngi t vn : phi chng o c x hi b suy thoi, xung cp trm trng? Phi chng nim tin, li sng ang b khng hong?</p>\r\n<p>Vn  ny  c cc nh lnh o nhn nh: Tnh trng suy thoi v chnh tr, t tng, o c, li sng trong mt b phn khng nh cn b, ng vin v tnh trng tham nhng, lng ph, quan liu, nhng tiu cc v t nn x hi cha c ngn chn, y li m cn tip tc din bin phc tp (trch Bo co chnh tr ca Ban Chp hnh Trung ng kha X ti i hi i biu ton quc ln th XI ca ng Cng sn Vit Nam, theo TTXVN).  mt cch nhn khc, nh bo Kim Dung/K Duyn  tng ni: Ci chn thng tm l ln nht trong x hi hin nay l g? Chnh l suy gim nim tin. Ngay vi mt a tr, mt nim tin  l mt chn thng ln lm khi tr mi bc vo i. Thm ch l ni m nh, v c khi n i theo sut trong cuc i. Cho nn c mt cu ni mt nim tin l mt tt c.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xy dng li c s cho nim tin</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chng ta khng th mi ngi nguyn ra bng ti m phi thp ln mt que dim, t  nhn nh sng  n lan rng ra. Theo nh Pht, trong ni tm ti nht vn c nh sng, ni au kh nht vn c tnh yu,  l  ngha tng sinh qua hnh nh quen thuc l sen v bn, hay phin no v b- (tnh thc, gic ng).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>"D tn hu o c</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Chnh  hng v nghi</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Dc thot tam c o</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Th vi ti ct tng</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>(C nim tin, c mt i sng tm linh</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Tm  ngay thng, khng b hoi nghi che lp</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>C quyt tm lnh xa ba no v xu c</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em> l im lnh ln nht)."</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>(Kinh Phc c, bi k 11 )</strong></p>\r\n<p>Nim tin (tn) l mt nng lng. Khi ta c nng lng nim tin nh trn, ta c sc mnh v hnh phc. Trong o Pht, c nm ngun nng lng: tn, tn, nim, nh v tu. Tam c o l ba no xu c, cc ngun nng lng khc. Hu o c i hi ta phi c mt i sng tm linh. Khng c i sng tm linh th khng c nng lng  i din, tho g kh khn trong ni tm ca chng ta. Chnh  hng v nghi l tm  ngay thng, hng v s thc tp chnh kin. Chnh kin tc tu, khng cn ng vc, hoi nghi</p>\r\n<p>Mi tranh chp trong cuc sng ny u c ng c t dc, tham lam, sn hn v si m. Hn hai ngn nm trm nm trc, c Pht tng dy rng: Ny cc T-kheo, do dc lm nhn, do dc lm duyn, do dc lm nguyn nhn, do chnh dc lm nhn, vua tranh ot vi vua. St--l tranh ot vi St- -l; B-la-mn tranh ot vi B-la-mn; gia ch tranh ot vi gia ch; m tranh ot vi con; con tranh ot vi m; cha tranh ot vi con; con tranh ot vi cha; anh em tranh ot vi anh em; bn b tranh ot vi bn b. Khi h  dn mnh vo tranh chp, tranh lun, tranh ot, h cng ph nhau bng tay, h cng ph nhau bng , bng gy, bng kim.  y h i n t vong, i n s au kh gn nh t vong. Ny cc T-kheo, nh vy l s nguy him cc dc l nguyn nhn ca dc.</p>\r\n<p>Li na, ny cc T-kheo, do dc lm nhn do chnh dc lm nhn, h cm mu v thun, h eo cung v tn, h dn trn hai mt, v tn c nhm bn nhau, ao c qung nm nhau, kim c vung chm nhau. H bn m nhau bng tn, h qung m nhau bng ao, h cht u nhau bng kim;  dy h i n t vong, i n s au kh gn nh t vong. Ny cc T-kheo, nh vy l s nguy him ca cc dc l nguyn nhn ca dc Ny cc T-kheo, nh vy s au kh cc dc a n au kh tng lai, l kh un, do dc lm nhn, do dc lm duyn, do dc lm nhn duyn, do chnh dc lm nhn. (Phm Tiu kinh Kh un, Kinh Trung b, HT.Thch Minh Chu dch)</p>\r\n<p>c Pht  ch ra nguyn nhn ca mi nguyn nhn gy nn ti c:  chnh l Dc. Cng nn lu  rng dc c ni ti trong on kinh nu trn l c dc. Gio php ca c Pht ch ra cho con ngi cn phi dit tr nhng mong mun tha mn lc th ch gy nn ti li m phi nhm n nhng khao kht hng thin  gii thot khi nhng ni kh tri buc con ngi. Nhng c Pht cng ch ra rng nu hnh gi khng on tn nm tm hoang vu th khng th no hng ti nhng khao kht hng thng.</p>\r\n<p>Cho nn, trc ht, x hi phi ngn nga tnh trang sa mc ha tm hn bng cch xy dng nim tin ng, tnh thng ng, v quan trng nht, theo nguyn l nhn qu. Thit ngh, y l vic ht sc h trng, bi l khng g nguy him trong x hi bng mt k lm c lnh lng khng cht my may ng tm v hu qu tang thng gy ra cho ngi khc!</p>\r\n<p>Nhng ni dung  phi c dy, phi hun tp nguyn l y cho con em ngay t tm b trong chng trnh gio dc - qua cc bi hc, cc cu chuyn, cc tranh, phim nh sinh ng. Gio dc nim tin nhn qu ch khng phi dy tr th kiu Tm - Cm trong truyn c cng tn.</p>\r\n<p>Chng ta cng phi bt u t gio dc gia nh. Tr em cn phi thy s gng mu ca ngi ln,  thc s cng bng, nghim minh ca php lut... Chng no thiu nhng tm gng y th nim tin cn b khng hong, x hi cn tao lon, lng ngi vn nhiu nhng v ci c kh on tr!</p>\r\n<p>Trong kinh Chuyn lun Php vng, c Pht dy bc v phm cht ca lnh o l phi sng trong gio php, trnh lm iu c: Nu ngi lnh o sng chn chnh, nhiu ngi s noi theo, v x hi s an lc. Bc vua cha hy i x thn dn nh con v trnh xa bn iu tai hi khi cai tr: tham lam, sn hn, lo s, o tng. c Pht  ra bn cch thc hnh x l b th, i ng, tit kim v bnh ng. Lnh o khng c xem bn thn l ti thng v khinh r dn chng, thc thi cng bng hay  chnh l kt qu ca tinh thn dn ch.</p>\r\n<p>Nim tin rt cn khi phc trc khi chng ta c th thc thi nhng chnh sch ln lao, chin lc xy dng con ngi. Phi bt u t nim tin, lch s cho thy rng cc triu i huy hong trong lch s cng u nhn c s tin tng tuyt i ca nhn dn.</p>\r\n<p>Hy m ca ma xun cho nng mai trn vo soi nhng gc khut ca tm hn ni chng ta thng che y cm xc, khng dm bc bch nhng suy ngh chn thc ca mnh v tm cha y s hoi nghi!</p>\r\n<p>o Pht l mt con ng thnh thang cho chng ta bc i. Chng ta cn tnh thc, xy dng li nim tin v bt u t tui tr. M cnh ca n ma xun trong tm thi bnh an.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>"Li chim gieo sng dt vn sa</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Trn bc ng xun tr li nh</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>M sch chp rng: - Vui mt sng</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Nghn nm cn mi tm lng ta."</em></p>\r\n<p><br /> (Huy Cn )<br />Nguyn Cn</p>	\N	\N	2016-08-20 04:20:03.253065	2016-08-20 12:51:12.272782	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
114	btn_0022.jpg	Gio Hi Gia Nhng Thay i Ca X Hi	<p><strong>Hot ng Pht s ca Gio hi  i qua nhng nm bn l v dn dn bc vo na cui nhim k VII (2012 - 2017). D cn kh sm  nhn li mt cch tng tn v cc hot ng Pht s nhng vi nhng g c th hin ca nm 2014, vi nhng thay i trong quan nim sng ca nhiu ngi, trong chiu hng pht trin ca x hi cng  li cho nhng ngi lu tm nhiu suy ngh.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>X l khng hong truyn thng</strong></p>\r\n<p>C th ni, cha bao gi truyn thng li c nhng hin tng dy sng d lun nh nm 2014 khi c kh nhiu khong trng trong qun l t cc c quan chc nng cng nh chiu hng nhiu lon phng thc tip cn ca c gi. Nu nh mt vi nm trc, ngi c thng c cm gic e ngi trc nhng knh c xem l bo l ci v tin tc khng ng tin cy, th thi gian gn y, cc kiu thng tin nh th lan sang c bo ch chnh thng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1471666957.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p>Mi ngy, m nhng trang bo mng v c bo giy, p vo mt trc ht khng phi l nhng chia s gi tr cuc sng, cc nhn t in hnh cn c pht huy hay thng tin y trin vng m  l nhng bn tin git gn, cu khch, thin v tnh gii tr tm thng hn l khi gi s suy gm mt li sng hng thng. V th, nm 2014 cng l nm c nhiu c quan bo ch b nhc nh, x pht.</p>\r\n<p>Trong chiu hng y, Gio hi - mt thc th vn ng gia x hi vi b my t chc, con ngi v cc yu t lin h khc cng bt u b sm soi. iu ny l l tt yu bi nhng thay i ca mt t nc ang trn con ng hi nhp, cc c th c dp tip cn nhiu li sng khc nhau thiu nh hng v chn lc. Khng nhng th, vi th gii phng ngy nay, mi s vic v hnh ng u c th b phi by di cch ny hay cch khc m ch nhn ca n kh c th bng bt hay giu nhm.</p>\r\n<p>T thc trng y m nm qua, cc thng tin lin quan n Pht gio, n Tng Ni v Pht t c du hiu trn lan trc cn bo truyn thng. D rng c c tiu cc ln tch cc nhng chung quy li chiu hng xu tr nn ph bin bi nhng cu t to tt, theo kiu pht st, l lng, dy sng, c dn mng sc, s h mang, v.v</p>\r\n<p>Chng vui khi phi nhc n nhng r rng Tng Ni, Pht t c nc  nhiu phen phi chnh lng v cc thng tin lin quan n chuyn nui tr m ci  cha B  (H Ni), v vic ca mt vi tu s tr nh T.M.N (Cn Th) hay mi y nht l T.C.M (Khnh Ha). Ngay c s vic khng c tht nhng cng c cc t bo dng chuyn vi ni dung nhiu xt xa, thng cm v mt v tu ti gia mang php danh Thin Nhn (Bnh Chnh, TP.HCM). Ri n mt t bo chnh thng li cho ng nhng bi vit c xem l xc phm n c mt trong nhng v gio phm cao cp ca Gio hi.</p>\r\n<p>Trc nhng s vic ny, Gio hi  nhiu cp  khc nhau  c nhng pht ngn chnh thc, nhng phn ng nhng iu d nhn thy l vn khng xoa du c d lun nht l  xut hin kh nhiu bnh lun c  trn cc trang mng x hi.</p>\r\n<p> , phn ln ngi tham gia bnh lun  dng nhiu li l chua cay khi m ch v i sng tu hnh ca Tng Ni v sinh hot cha chin, t vin. V c v nh Gio hi cha c s chun b v vn cn lng tng tm cch ng x vi nhng hin tng x hi v truyn thng ny. iu ny cng d hiu v chng ta cha quen vi cc hot ng phn bin nhng t nhng v vic ny, thut ng x l khng hong truyn thng cn c lu tm v tip cn mt cch nghim tc trong cc cp t chc Gio hi. ng  mi chuyn xy ra ri mi tm cch x l v c v th m  sng. Trong trng hp ny, nhng du tch ca thng tin nht l trn cc trang mng x hi kh m xa b.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Chnh lng v s lng tn </strong></p>\r\n<p>Tn  c xem nh mt b phn nng ct v l ht nhn trong nh hng pht trin ca mi tn gio. Khc vi cc tn gio phng Ty vi n np t chc v qun l tn  theo khu vc v n v c th, Pht gio dng nh cha ch trng n vic thng k v tip cn cc thng tin tn  t cc con s.</p>\r\n<p>T ngy thnh lp Gio hi n nay, mi dp hi ngh thng nin u c cc s liu v lng tn  n tu hc ti cc o trng, lp gio l nhng c l thng tin ny cha ng tin cy v i lc c s trng lp. V  ch mi l nhng cp nht mang tnh phng on v tng hp t cc n v cp di gi ln ch cha thng qua mt kho st khoa hc tng th v ng b.</p>\r\n<p>Cch y vi nm, Tng Ni, Pht t c nc git mnh trc con s thng k ca Ban Ch o Tng iu tra dn s nm 2010 khi cng b s lng tn  Pht gio Vit Nam ch  mc 6,8 triu ngi, chim 7,92% dn s. Thng tin ny va c a ra  gp phi nhng phn bin v bnh lun gay gt v tnh ton din ca n. D vy, y vn c xem l thng k duy nht mang tnh chnh thng v s lng tn  i vi Pht gio cho n nay. Ngc li, cc bi pht biu hay nhng bui trao i mang tnh x giao, ch tn tc lnh o Gio hi thng nu con s tn  chim 40%, 60% v thm ch 80% dn s c nc.</p>\r\n<p>Vy u l con s chnh xc? S lng tn  tng th hin nay bao nhiu v ang theo chiu hng tng hay gim trong nm 2014? y thc s l mt du hi ln v cn s quan tm ng mc. Trong mt ti liu ni b khng chnh thc ca mt tn gio phng Ty cng b bng ting nc ngoi vo gia thng 12-2014 m ngi vit c dp tip cn cho thy s lng tn  ca tn gio y ang tng ln mt cch nhanh chng ti khu vc chu . Trong khi  tn  truyn thng ca khu vc ny l Pht gio c du hiu gim i ngay c  nhng t nc o Pht l quc gio, l tn gio lu i, Vit Nam cng khng ngoi l.<br /> l gc nhn ca mt tn gio c th cha c s kim chng nhng chc chn cng l iu ng  suy ngh. Bi l khi a ra thng tin nh th, h cng  cn nhc v c cch thng k ca ring mnh. V pha Gio hi, sau mt nm hot ng vi nhiu chng trnh c thc hin, nhiu k hoch c trin khai, nhiu Pht s c hon thnh m mc tiu vn hng n s nghip truyn b Chnh php, xin dng li dy ca c Pht, trong  khch th l tn .</p>\r\n<p>Vy liu c th oan chc rng mnh  nm r thng tin tn  v quan trng hn, s lng tn  ca chng ta ang tng ln? C l cu hi ny rt cn ch tn tc c trch nhim iu nghin v tm li gii p.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Gia Trc</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-20 04:23:03.822269	2016-08-20 12:51:45.552013	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
136	9.jpg	Bn  Ca Tnh  Tng	<p><strong>Ngi nim Pht tuy  pht khi tn tm dng mnh v cng phu khng gin on, nhng nu ti sinh ci Ta b th vn b lun chuyn v nh hu cn non km, qu c cha hon mn.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cn phi vng sinh Cc Lc th gii, cn k Pht v Thnh chng, thnh tu v lng Ba la mt, thm nhp Tam mui Tng tr mn, pht hong th nguyn i khp mi phng gio ha v s chng sinh. Khng lu sau ly c ri ni B  o trng, hng phc ma qun, thnh ng Chnh Gic, chuyn Php lun V thng. Nn bit rng c vng sinh Cc Lc th khng bao gi tr li a v phm phu vi thn xc ng un na.</p>\r\n<p>Tnh  tng ch trng nim Pht, qun tng c Pht A Di  v s th thng, trang nghim ca ci Cc Lc Tnh , bng t lc vi Tn, Hnh, Nguyn tng ng bn nguyn ca c Pht A Di , hnh gi nng nh Pht lc  vng sinh v Cc Lc trong trng thi nht tm bt lon (Chnh nh). V phn Hnh (trong Tn, Hnh, Nguyn), khng ch c chuyn tr nim Pht, qun tng m cn th tr Tam quy, Ng gii, hnh Thp thin, tu to cc cng c phc lnh, hn th na l pht B  tm, nguyn thnh Pht o, ha  chng sinh. Kinh Qun V Lng Th c ni r: Hnh gi mun vng sinh Tnh  phi hi  ba iu kin: Mt l hiu dng cha m, phng th s trng, nui dng lng t khng st hi, tu tp mi nghip lnh (Thp thin nghip). Hai l th tr Tam quy (quy y Pht, quy y Php, quy y Tng), y  cc gii, khng phm oai nghi. Ba l pht B  tm, tin su l nhn qu, c tng kinh in i tha, khuyn ngi khc cng tu.</p>\r\n<p>T  cho thy Tnh  tng khng phi l mt tng phi ch c tn ngng Tnh  Cc Lc v c Pht A Di , tng phi ch c nim tin, m  l tng phi ch trng con ng tu tp Gii, nh, Tu, mc d c v nh thin v Gii v nh. Nh cng phu tinh tn nim Pht m thnh tu nh (nht tm bt lon, Nim Pht tam mui), nh th tr Tam quy, Ng gii, Thp thin v tu to cc cng c phc lnh (trong  c h tr Tam bo, hong dng Chnh php, t thin-b th, phng sinh v.v..) m thnh tu c Gii (gm c Nhip lut nghi gii, Nhip thin php gii v Nhiu ch hu tnh gii).</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1472487050.jpg" width="723" height="542" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ba b kinh, mt b lun trng yu ca tng Tnh  (Pht thuyt A Di  kinh, V Lng Th kinh, Qun V Lng Th kinh v Vng sinh Tnh  lun), c l kinh Nim Pht Ba la mt (Php s Cu Ma La Thp dch t Phn sang Hn vo i Diu Tn 384-417) l b kinh ni r bn , ch ch ca tng Tnh , l gii mt cch r rng, thu o v mc ch v ng li tu tp php mn nim Pht cu vng sinh. Trong phm th hai Mi tm th thng(Bn dch t Hn sang Vit ca Ha thng Thch Thin Tm, n bn nm 1997-PL.2541) c ni:</p>\r\n<p>Php mn nim Pht chnh l chuyn bin ci tm th ca chng sinh, bng cch khng  cho tm th y duyn vi vng nim, vi lc trn l sc, thinh, hng, v, xc, php, vi huyn cnh, vi kin chp, vi mong cu, vi thc phn bit v.v.. M ch em tm th y duyn mi vi danh hiu Nam m A Di  Pht. Khng bao lu ngi nim Pht t nhin i vo ch vng lng, sng sut, an lc, cm ng vi nguyn lc ca c A Di , thy mnh sinh vo ci nc Cc Lc, thn mnh ngi trn ta sen bu, nghe Pht v B tt ni php, hoc thy Pht ly tay xoa nh(trang 21, dng 14-24). iu ny cng tng t nh li c Pht dy trong kinh Qun V Lng Th: Ch Pht Nh Lai l thn php gii, vo trong tm tng chng sinh, cho nn tm cc ngi tng Pht th tm y l ba mi hai tng tt, tm mi v p, tm y lm Pht, tm y l Pht. Bin Chnh Bin Tri ca Pht t ni tm tng m sinh, v th cc ngi phi nh ngh v qun tng k thn ca c Pht kia.</p>\r\n<p> ch l s an tr tm trong tnh cnh, nhng tr tu v nh lc cha  sc ph tr cn bn v minh, phin no lu hoc vi t. V th cn phi thng  trong tnh cnh do nim Pht nht tm, thnh tu tam mui, cng vi s nhip ha h tr ca c Pht A Di , Thnh chng v hon cnh thanh tnh ca cnh gii Cc Lc  chuyn ha hon ton, thnh tu gii thot. Sau khi c th t ti ra vo sinh t ha  chng sinh, vn tri qua qu trnh hnh B tt o, v cui cng l thnh Pht, chuyn Php lun nh con ng ch Pht qu kh  tri qua. Tip tc kho st kinh Nim Pht Ba la mt, chng ta s thy r iu . Kinh vit: Tuy cng phu nim Pht trong hin kip  t nn tng vng vng cho s nghip gii thot, nhng sau  phi vng sinh Tnh , lnh th s gio ha ca Pht v Thnh chng cho ti khi thnh tu V sanh Php nhn. Sau  mi  nng lc hin thn khp mi phng hnh B tt o, ra vo sinh t m khng tri buc, tr li chn c trc m chng nhim , cu  chng sinh khng c hn lng (Sd, trang 22, dng 16-24).</p>\r\n<p>Ngi nim Pht tuy  pht khi tn tm dng mnh v cng phu khng gin on, nhng nu ti sinh ci Ta b th vn b lun chuyn v nh hu cn non km, qu c cha hon mn. Cn phi vng sinh Cc Lc th gii, cn k Pht v Thnh chng, thnh tu v lng Ba la mt, thm nhp Tam mui Tng tr mn, pht hong th nguyn i khp mi phng gio ha v s chng sinh. Khng lu sau ly c ri ni B  o trng, hng phc ma qun, thnh ng Chnh Gic, chuyn Php lun V thng. Nn bit rng c vng sinh Cc Lc th khng bao gi tr li a v phm phu vi thn xc ng un na. Do  mi gi l Bt thi chuyn. T  v sau, dn dn thnh tu mi th tr lc, mi tm php bt cng, ng nhn, lc thng, v lng  la ni, v s tam mui, thn thng du h, bin ti v ngi v.v.. y  cng c v lu ca bc i B tt, cho n khi c qu Pht. Bi vy m ta, Thch Ca Mu Ni Th Tn hm nay trn trng xc quyt rng: Vng sinh ng  ngha vi thnh Pht (Sd, t dng 5 trang 23 n dng 2 trang 24).</p>\r\n<p>Ch khi tm an tr hon ton vo trng thi thanh tnh vi diu (tnh , cc lc), m theo gio ngha Tnh  th ch c cnh gii ca ch Pht, ca ch Thnh bt thi chuyn nh Cc Lc, th   cc phin no vi t, cc tp kh sinh t mi khng c iu kin sinh khi v dn dn c chuyn ha, hnh gi mi khng ri tr li ci i ng trc (khng cn ti sinh tr li ci Ta b), t  theo s gio ha ca c Pht A Di  m tu tp cho n ngy thnh tu vin mn o qu B .</p>\r\n<p>Nhng li dy trong kinh Nim Pht Ba la mt ni trn cng l cu tr li cho thc mc: Php mn Tnh  ch c nh hay thin Ch m khng c tu qun (thin Qun) th lm sao ph tr cn bn v minh, vi t lu hoc. Mc d cc hnh gi Tnh  cho rng qun ho tng v cng c ca c Pht A Di  v s th thng trang nghim ca cnh gii Cc Lc,  l thin Qun; Hoc cho rng t nh (nht tm bt lon, nim Pht Tam mui) s pht sinh Tu (tu gic, tu qun), nhng cch l gii ny dng nh khng tha ng. Cn c theo kinh in Nguyn thy th thin qun  y l qun v duyn sinh, v ng  chng tu gic v ng (hay tr Bt nh, theo quan im ca Pht gio pht trin). Bi v nu ni t nh m sinh Tu th ti sao ngoi o t ti cnh gii nh rt cao nh Khng v bin x nh, Thc v bin x nh, V s hu x nh v Phi tng phi phi tng x nh m vn khng gic ng, khng xut hin tr tu gii thot. C th ni nguyn nhn l v ngoi o cn chp th cc cnh gii thin nh v khng thy c l Duyn sinh-V ng, ngoi o  khng tu tp tu qun  thy T  (Bn cht ca i sng l v thng, bt toi nguyn, l kh; nguyn nhn ca thc trng  hay nguyn nhn ca kh; An lc hnh phc khi chm dt kh v phng php hay con ng chm dt kh).</p>\r\n<p>Tr li t tng Tnh . Theo bn  ca tng Tnh  th vng sinh l thnh Pht   ngha bt thi chuyn (v sinh, khng cn ti sinh tr li ci ta b), ch vng sinh khng phi l thnh Pht trong  ngha gic ng vin mn, thnh bc phc tr nh nghim, y  tam minh, t tr, thnh tu t gic, gic tha v gic hnh vin mn. Vng sinh cha phi l cui con ng tu tp  t c cu cnh o qu B  hay thnh Pht tht s. iu ny khng ch kinh Nim Pht Ba la mt m cc kinh khc ca Tnh  tng cng c ni r. Mc ch ca tng Tnh  l  c c c hi vng sinh.</p>\r\n<p>S d nhiu ngi tu theo php mn Tnh  l v cho rng php mn ny m bo hn nhng php mn khc  ch bt thoi chuyn, hnh gi c an ton trong cnh gii ca Pht v B tt thng thin nhn, y l hon cnh rt tt lm tng thng duyn cho qu trnh tu tp. Nu khng vng sinh v Cc Lc Tnh , cn ti sinh tr li ci i ng trc th khng ly g m bo hnh gi khng thi tht tm B , lui st cng nng tu hnh, vng vo ng dc lc trn trong qu trnh tip duyn xc cnh nu khng tinh tn tu hnh, khng c nim, nh, tu vng vng.</p>\r\n<p>Tu Vin i s (333-416) i ng Tn (317-420), ngi c xem l S t sng lp Tnh  tng Trung Hoa, vn l mt ngi chuyn nghin cu Thin hc, tu tp Gii, nh, Tu, nhng ngi li lp ra Bch Lin X  L sn, quy t t chng ng tu nim Pht cu sinh Ty phng Cc Lc. Cc bc long tng trong Chnh php nh ngi M Minh, Long Th, Th Thn v.v.. u tn thn php mn Tnh . Trong i Tha Khi Tn lun, ngi M Minh c vit:  Nn mnh m tinh tn, ngy m su thi l bi ch Pht, thnh tm sm hi, khuyn thnh, ty h, hi hng v qu B . Tu tp nh th khng thi ngh th s c khi cc chng, cn lnh thm ln. Li ni: Nh Lai c thng phng tin  nhip h ngi c tn tm. y l dng nhn duyn chuyn nh nim Pht, theo nguyn cu sinh v Tnh , do c thng thy Pht nn vnh vin xa la c o. Nh trong tu a la (kinh) ni: Nu ngi chuyn nim Pht A Di   phng Ty, em nhng cn lnh mnh tu hi hng v ci kia, th c vng sinh. Do thng thy Pht nn khng cn lo thi chuyn. Trong i Tr  lun ca ngi Long Th c ni: Nim Pht tam mui c th tr cc th phin no v ti i trc. Li na, nim Pht tam mui c phc c ln hay  chng sinh. Cho nn cc B tt mun  sinh, nu tu cc php tam mui khc tt khng bng mn nim Pht tam mui, v mn ny c phc c ln, mau dit cc ti. Pht l Php vng, B tt l Php tng, ch B tt tn trng duy ch c Pht. B tt thng kho tu nhn duyn nim Pht, nn thng gp ch Pht, nh kinh Bt Chu ni: B tt vo tam mui ny (nim Pht tam mui) lin hin sinh v ci Pht A Di . Ngi Th Thn dy php tu Ng nim mn trong V Lng Th kinh lun nh sau: Nu tu Ng nim mn thnh tu, kt qu s c sinh v Cc Lc, thy Pht A Di . Ng nim mn l g? L bi mn, tn thn mn, pht nguyn mn, qun tng mn v hi hng mn. L bi l th no? y l dng thn l bi c Pht A Di , t  cung knh, cu Pht nhip th. Tn thn l th no? L dng ming khen ngi sc thn, danh ngha, nh sng, tr tu ca c Pht A Di , mun tu hnh nh tht cho c tng ng. Pht nguyn l th no? y l mt lng chuyn nim vo ni chnh nh, nguyn sinh v Cc Lc. Qun tng l th no? L dng chnh nim qun st cng c trang nghim ca ci Cc Lc, cng c trang nghim ca Pht A Di  v cng c trang nghim ca ch B tt, thnh chng. Hi hng l th no? y l tm t bi khng b nhng chng sinh kh no, nguyn em cn lnh cng c phc bo ca mnh hi hng, cu cho tt c loi hu tnh u c sinh v Cc Lc.Qua s tn dng khen ngi v khuyn khch tu tp theo php mn Tnh  ca cc bc long tng trong Chnh php, chng ta khng th xem thng php mn Tnh , v chc chn php mn y c s th thng vi diu. S th thng vi diu y cng c chng minh sng t hn khi chng ta c s thc hnh, th nghim.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Phan Minh c</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Daophatngaynay</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-29 16:11:04.246129	2016-08-30 16:33:28.511166	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2015-02-08 00:00:00
137	145928765.jpg	Tp Th	<p><strong>c Pht dy: Ny, cc thy t-khu! y l con ng c nht  thanh lc tm (an tnh, thanh tnh) cho chng sanh, vt thot su bi (su bun, bi ai), dit tr u no (u t, phin no), thnh tu chnh tr v chng ng Nit-bn.  l T nim x.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tc l nim thn, nim th, nim tm v nim php.</p>\r\n<p>Trc khi i su vo ni dung tu tp y, chng ta cn phi bit tp th trc. Th n rt quan trng. N l cn bn ca c thin nh v thin tu.</p>\r\n<p>Th c 16 giai on hoc c 16 cch quan st. ng tsallakkheti c ngha l quan st, tc l chng ta bt u tin hnh thin tu t 16 cch th khi qut ny:</p>\r\n<p>C 4 cch th thuc v thn, 4 cch th thuc v th, 4 cch th thuc v tm v 4 cch th thuc v php.</p>\r\n<p>A- Bn Cch Th Thuc V Thn:</p>\r\n<p>Kinh vn nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>1.  Khi th v di (dgha), tu tri (pajnti) ang th v di. Khi th ra di, tu tri ang th ra di.</p>\r\n<p>2. Khi th v ngn (rassa), tu tri (pajnti) ang th v ngn. Khi th ra ngn, tu tri ang th ra ngn.</p>\r\n<p>Mun hiu cch th ny, chng ta phi nm bt cho r ngha hai ch tu tri. Tu tri n khc vi tng tri v thc tri. Tng tri (sajnti) l ci bit ca tng (sa), bit khi qut qua du hiu, hnh dng, mu sc... Thc tri (vijnti) l ci bit ca thc (via), bit qua kin thc, nhn thc, kinh nghim v l tr ch quan. Tng tri v thc tri thng b gii hn, sai lm do v minh v nghip chi phi. Tu tri (pajnti), l ci bit ca tu (pa), l thy r, bit r ng bn cht, ng nh thc tnh. Vy, khi th v th ra di, ta kinh nghim trc tip, cm nhn trn vn hi th v, hi th ra di y, ng din dch, ng lin tng, tng tng g c. N nh th no th cm nhn n nh th y, thy r, bit r n ng nh n l - c gi l tu tri.</p>\r\n<p>- Rt kh hiu, tha thy! Thy c v d no c hnh tng  d nm bt ng ngha ca tu tri y khng?</p>\r\n<p>- C ch, rt d na l ng khc. Ging nh bn s dng ci my nh chp hnh. a hoa, bi trc, ngn ni... i tng cnh nh th no th bn chp nh th y! Nh khi bn i trong m vi cy n pin trn tay, bn ri sng con ng ri xem c bi b gai gc hm h g khng. Bn ch vic nhn, quan st m thi. Cng vy, tu tri l lng nghe, quan st trc tip, kinh nghim trc tip hi th di ngn, vo ra mt cch trn vn, khch quan nh th - ng nh m n l!</p>\r\n<p>- Ngha l ng c gng th su, th di g c - hi th ca mnh nh th no th ghi nhn, quan st n nh th y, ng c dng lc  phnh bng, nn hi xung an in - khc vi cch th ca kh cng hoc Yoga - phi th khng tha thy?</p>\r\n<p>- ng vy! Ngoi ra,  y chng ta cn   ch di (dgha) v ngn (rassa). Thng th di i i vi su, cng c trng hp di m th tho ch khng nh v su; cn ngn th i lin vi cn, nhng cng c trng hp ngn nhng nh nhng, thanh mnh... iu ny, s thc ny mun c bit r, thy r mt cch chnh xc th cn cn s thc nghim ni bn thn ca mi ngi. Trong s thin sinh  y, c nhiu v tu tp thin nh  nhiu nm, c th san s kinh nghim y cho hi chng nghe, c khng?</p>\r\n<p>- Xin vng! Mt ngi ni - Ty theo c a m c ngi c hi th di, su; c ngi c hi th ngn, cn. iu  khng quan trng. Di, su c ghi nhn di, su; ngn, cn th c ghi nhn ngn, cn. Nhng, tht ra, khi mi vo ngi, hi th ca ta n th tho, i khi dn dp v ngn, cn. Lt sau, khi bt c hi th ri, iu thn  yn ri th hi th bt u nh nhng, thanh mnh, t vi hn. Ni tm li, theo con, hi th ngn di, cn su g , n nh th no th nhn ngm, quan st n nh th y, mt cch thanh thn v t nhin!</p>\r\n<p>- , th l ng!</p>\r\n<p>C ngi hi.</p>\r\n<p>- Con c c nhiu sch thin.  ch ny, con nh khng lm, th cc v y u vit nh sau: Chnh nim, v y th vo; chnh nim, v y th ra. Vy th gia tu tri v chnh nim c g ging nhau, c g khc nhau - hay ch khc  ch din t?</p>\r\n<p>- Cu hi ny rt chnh xc. Nhng u tin, trong hi chng ny, ai l ngi hiu ng thc ngha chnh nim l g, xin cho bit?</p>\r\n<p>Mt ngi p:</p>\r\n<p>- Tha, c ngi bo chnh nim l nim tng chn chnh, ghi nh chn chnh, nim tng ng n, ghi nh ng n. C ngi qu quyt l tr nh, ch tm vo ci g  ang xy ra - c ng khng thy?</p>\r\n<p>Ngi khc:</p>\r\n<p>- C v thin s rt ni ting, khi vit mt quyn sch v cuc i c Pht, c mt chng ni v chnh nim - nhng c xong chng y, v con  c rt k, nhng khng h thy mt ch chnh nim no, thay vo  l t tnh thc - c ti thiu trn ba mi ln ch tnh thc c lp i lp li trong chng chnh nim ny. R rng, theo v ny, chnh nim ng ngha vi tnh thc khng hn khng km. Cn na, cng t quyn sch ny, lc ni v tnh thc, i lc nh, lc n tri cam trong tnh thcc th thy c cy cam n hoa, thy nh nng v git ma...; thy c mun vt trong v tr ang tip tay nhau  lm cho tri cam c mt... iu y l ng trong gio php trng trng duyn khi. Tuy nhin, cng chnh iu y lm con khng hiuchnh nim l g na. N c ng ngha vi tnh thc khng? ng ngha vi tu tri - tri nh thc - khng?</p>\r\n<p>- T t , ni hm ca vn , ca nhng cu hi y cn nhng bi hc ring v chnh nim, chnh kin v chnh t duy... C nim  i n nh. C nim tr gip cho t duy v kin. V ngay chnh kin i ni ng ngha vi tnh thc, tnh gic, tu tri, tri nh thc... Ri cn chnh kin hu lu, chnh kin v lu kh phc tp. ng qu tin vo sch. V c im ny, qu v nn lu  cho. L phi phn bit cho tht r, tht k, nhng quyn sch do nh vn vit, hc gi vit; n c khc vi sch do ngi ta dch t cc bn ting Anh ni v s tu tp, v thin nh hay thin tu. Li cng khc xa vi nhng li dy trc tip gia thin s v mn sinh. Nh vn th ngi ta thng c gng vit cho hay, cho bay bng... nhng y khng phi l t liu chnh xc, ng tin cy  tu tp. N ch l mt tc phm vn hc thi. Quyn sch m bn c v trch dn  trn thuc loi ny. Cc nh vn thng cung cp cho chng ta nhng khi nim i khi mng lung ch cha bao gi cung cp nhng khi nim gn vi s thc hoc chuyn ch s thc - nh s yu cu nghim tc, ct li, tinh yu ca thin qun vipassan. Bn  ngh ng, n tri cam nh th khng phi l chnh nim, m chnh l t duy hoc lin tng,  c s tham d ca l tr ch quan - ni chnh xc,  ltng tri v thc tri. Ci lang bang ngh tng, suy tng y cng l mt hnh thi khc ca tht nim y! Do vy, tnh thc  y thng ln ln vi thc tri v tng tri ch khng phi tu tri! Tnh thc rt ro n khc ka! Ri bn s hiu iu  hn v nhng bi thc tp khc, sau ny. Th n, cc nh hc gi vit sch, thng h ch cung cp cho chng ta nhng t liu c gng gn vi s thc, c gng khch quan, khoa hc. Nhng bi vit ca h c chng l, c s liu, c ti liu tham kho cng phu - nhng chc chn h khng phi l nhng hnh gi tu tp ng tin cy. Ngay chnh nhng sch dch v thin, tu tp thin - chng ta cng nn d dt, thn trng. Ti sao vy? Thin qun minh st vipassan - T nim x (satipahna) l kinh nghim t thn ca mi ngi, l cm nhn, l kinh nghim trc tip trn mi hi th, mi cm th... Cm nhn, kinh nghim trc tip y vn l nh thc tnh, l Paramattha - nhng khi din t li, m t li - th phi s dng ngn ng khi nim. S ly cch n nm  y. V thin s dy bng ting Min, trc tip cho hc tr. V thy khng vit li m thng l hc tr vit li - c th l qua bng ging. Thng th vit li bng ting Min sau  dch sang ting Anh. V khi qua mt ngn ng khc th khi nim  b chuyn i hoc c gng tm t tng ng. C phi th khng? Mi ngn ng thng c linh hn v s sng ca n trong dng chy vn ha, tm linh ca dn tc  - khi dch qua mt ngn ng khc th thng nh mt ci linh hn v s sng ca n ri. Ci S Thc, do vy  i xa ri. Th nhng, thi i ny khng dng li  , bng ting Anh li c dch sang ting Vit na th chuyn g xy ra? V nu dch gi khng phi l hnh gi th qu tht l mt i ha! Khng ni th qu v  hiu. Cc dch gi cn trng, lm vic nghim tc, c vn ha tr thc v vn ha tm linh - h  chu kh gi nguyn t Pi, i khi so snh, i chiu vi nguyn c cu k Pi lc gp nhng  ngha i hi s chnh xc ti a. Vic lm  rt ng trn trng. Tuy nhin, cng qu hn na, nu dch gi y l mt hnh gi - cn nu l nh vn hoc hc gi lm vic y th s khng cn ng tin cy na! C nhiu sai lm kh trm trng trong mt s sch dch y. i ch thiu chnh xc, i ch ln ln gia chnh nim v chnh kin, i ch ln ln chnh kin v chnh t duy; ri cn ln ln gia tu tri, tng tri v thc tri nh chng ta  hiu. Hy vng rng,  nhng bi sau, chng ta s tun t i li mt s ng ngha cho chn xc ko nguy him qu... , qu xa ri, lc  ri. Hy tr li bi thc tp hm nay. Chng ta ni n u ri nh?</p>\r\n<p>- Chnh nim, tha thy! Chnh nim, v y th vo, chnh nim v y th ra!</p>\r\n<p>- , vy qu v hy nghe y! Chnh nim nh ngi ng canh ca. N ng canh ci ca thn tm. C ci g i vo cn nh thn tm l ci anh chnh nim phi bit, phi thy. Ti tm dng ch bit v thy nhng nghe ra  khng chnh xc ri,  trt ri. V bit l thuc v tri; v thy l thuc v kin  ni gn l tri kin. Chnh nim khng phi l tri kin ri! Ti s din t cch khc. Th gii bn ngoi c sc thanh hng v xc php thng tm cch i vo mt tai mi li thn . Anh chnh nim ng canh ca, phi ch tm, phi cnh gic  ti ch , th thi. Nhng thy r n, sng sut thy r n, n nh th no th thy r, sng sut thy r n nh th y - th li l chc nng ca anh chnh kin. Ri, ci i tng y, ngi khch y tt xu, trng en nh th no th l bn phn ca anh chnh t duy. N phc tp vy y. Nh vy, chnh nim cha thy, cha bit g c. Ch ai i chnh nim li bit nng ma sng gi! Anh ch vic canh ca, ch tm. Ni cch khc, chnh nim l tr li vi thn tm mnh, l tr li trn vn vi mnh, th thi. Chnh nim, v y th ra, chnh nim, v y th v - c ngha l ch tm, trn vn vi hi th, v y th v; ch tm, trn vn vi hi th, v y th ra - n gin nh vy y. Qu v thc tp th xem.</p>\r\n<p>C ngi hi.</p>\r\n<p>- Con cha th c v con cn thc mc. V khi th t nhin nh th, thy dng ch ch tm - vy th ch tm  u? Phi c ci ch  tm ch vo y ch? C sch ni, c ba giai on, c ba ch  ch tm. Ch th nht l cht mi khi hi th ht vo. Ch th hai  vng ngc v ch th ba l  an in. V khi th ra li t an in, qua ngc, qua mi nh vy - c ng khng thy?</p>\r\n<p>- C ai tr li cho thy cu hi  khng?</p>\r\n<p>- C, con s tr li. Cng c th ch tm nh vy trong giai on mnh tu tp nh. Do tu tp nh l cn ct ci tm. Ban u khi tp thin, ci tm ta n c bung lung, nh kh vn, chy nhy leo tro ch ny, ch kia lung tung - nn ci tm y phi c ct cht  ba ch, ba giai on nh ng bn va ni. Nh mt b ci, ct mt ch th lng lo, nhng ct ba ni th n rt chc chn. Nu c ct mi nh th th ci tm s tm yn, nhng n s khng a n an tnh; ch a n s cng thng, b tiu hao nng lng, c th tot m hi, c th c th s mt mi, r ri. Ti  tng kinh nghim v iu y. Sau giai on ct cht ba ch, khi tm  c v yn ri th ta phi th n ra. Nh trong Thp mc ngu , qua ht giai on gim mi, buc c con tru li n v chung, lc n  thun thc ri, ta ch bung h, sau  ch cn i mt bn trng chng l . Cng vy l hi th. Bn s n giai on theo di, r sot hi th. Nhng y l th ca nh, ch khng phi th ca tu, ca thin qun vipassan - c phi th khng tha thy?</p>\r\n<p>- ng bn  c kinh nghim nh, san s cho mi ngi kinh nghim y th tht l b ch. ng vy, th ca thin nh l nh vy - nn trong kinh vn, c Pht dng t anussati - ty nim, c ngha l theo di, r sot, i theo lun, ch tm lin tc, nim ghi nh lin tc. Cn nim trong thin tu ch trng s t nhin, thanh thn, nh nhng. Nim  tu l sati - nh satipahna (T nim x) l ch tm, l canh ca, ng l l, ng tht nim, ng qun mnh, ng d dui... Nu hi th vo  mi th ch tm  ni cht mi l c ri, v hi th du i ra hoc i vo th n cng phi i qua mi. C ng canh   thi. Thanh tnh oc v d rt hay v iu y. L nh ngi th ca, khi ca mt khc cy, ch cn ch tm ni ch li ca tip gip vi khc cy - ch khng cn phi chy qua chy v theo li ca, lm nh vy s mt lm, c phi th khng qu v?</p>\r\n<p>- ng vy ri! Nhng m tha thy - mt ngi ni - Nu ch tm  ni cht mi, mt im ni cht mi, vy l c khuynh hng nh ri, u c gi l tu?</p>\r\n<p>- ng  y nhng phi canh ca, ch khng phi ng  y ri nh lun!</p>\r\n<p>- Th l sao ?</p>\r\n<p>- Phi canh ca ch sao?</p>\r\n<p>- Th canh ri! Hi th vo ra nh th no cng phi i qua ci cht mi m!</p>\r\n<p>- Rt ng - m cha tht s ng! Hi th thuc v thn. ng bn ch ng canh  y, nhng nu c ngi khch l no i qua cm gic (th), i qua tri gic (tng), i qua cc trng thi tm l (hnh), i qua  thc (thc) - th ng bn khng cn bit hay sao? Hay l c ng nh  y m khng thm bit? nh th khng cn bit, nhng tu th phi bit y, nhng phi l ci bit ca tu tri!</p>\r\n<p>Hi trng im lng.</p>\r\n<p>- Vy th t t  nh! Hi ny gi chng ta mi  cp hai cch th thuc v thn. Qu v hy lng nghe, cn hai cch th cng thuc v thn na, kinh vn nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>3. Cm gic ton thn (sabbakya paisaved) khi th v, v y hc (sikkhati). Cm gic ton thn khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>4. An tnh thn hnh (kyasakhra passambhaya) khi th v, v y hc. An tnh thn hnh khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>Qu v thy l bt u phi ch tm lng nghe ri y. Th no l cm gic ton thn? Th no l an tnh thn hnh? Th no l v y hc? V hc l hc ci g?</p>\r\n<p>Cm gic ton thn - sabbakya paisaved - ny hin c nhiu cch gii thch khc nhau:</p>\r\n<p>- Thn chnh l thn hi th, ton thn chnh l ton thn hi th. Bn phi cm gic ton vn ci thn hi th y.</p>\r\n<p>- Thn cng l thn hi th - nhng ton thn phi c bt u cm nhn  giai on u, giai on gia, giai on cui.</p>\r\n<p>- Cm gic ton thn trong mt hi th t u n chn v t chn n u lc th ra, vo.</p>\r\n<p>Theo ti, chng ta khng cn phn tch phc tp n nh th. V thin s no cng ni rng kinh nghim ca mnh ng, v h  dy ng - nhng ngi lc phin dch b tam sao tht bn. Tp thin, mt s chng nghim c th, ch cn mt ch sai, mt khi nim thiu chnh xc - th s tht  b lch lc mt ri. Nu r sot ton thn hi th hoc cm gic c ba giai on th cng nhm  ct tm - n s nghing v nh, c s xen d ca thc tri. Cn cm gic ton thn m tng tng hi th i t u n chn, t chn n u th n thuc v tng tri. Chng ta lu  y l lnh vc ca tu tri ang quan st hi th, n ch c chc nng thy r, bit r, cm nhn trn vn. Ni cch khc, ton thn phi c cm gic, v cm gic th cm gic nh th no?</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi tu tri hi th vo ra ngn di rt t nhin, rt thanh thn mt thi gian, hi th ca chng ta s khng cn th tho na m tr nn nh, thanh rt l vi t, i khi khng cm nhn c. Theo , ci thn cng tr nn d chu. Cm gic ton thn l cm gic ton b ci  ang hin tn  ni thn - ch khng phi cm gic cc b, khu bit  ni thn hi th hoc  ni thn vt cht! V an tnh thn hnh (kyasakhra passambhaya) cng phi c tu tri nh th! Ci thn n lc ny khng cn th cng, nhc nhch, t au na m n  an n ri. V y th l  iu phc ci thn c ri! C nhiu ngi i hi xa khi phn tch cc cm th, li cn gii thch nhng sinh v dit ca cc cm th na! C ngi li gii thch sakhra - hnh, trong thn hnh - l php hu vi lm cho vn  cng thm phc tp, ri rm thm! Xin tha, y ch mi nim thn, quan st hi th kia m!</p>\r\n<p>By gi, cn ch hc na, hc - sikkhati - l thc tp, l thc hnh. V y phi lng nghe, thc tp, thc hnh... s quan st hi th y, cho d n c vi t cch my cng phi cm nhn cho bng c. Cm gic ton thn v an tnh thn hnh n cng s i n ch vi t hn - cng phi c tu tri nh th. C ai hi g na khng? Khng ! Vy th hy tp th i!</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1472487300.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p>B- Bn Cch Th Thuc V Cm Th:</p>\r\n<p>Trc khi i qua 4 cch th thuc v cm th - cm gic - chng ta nhc li mt vi im quan trng. Gi l thuc v thn, ch c ngha l th vi mc ch l  iu thn, n lc ci thn an tnh c ri mi bt u qua cch th  theo di quan st cccm gic - cm th. Ci thn vn th tho nn ta phi quan st trc, nhng n lc hi th nh nhng, vi t, nu khng c ch tm, tnh nim th ta cng  kh cm nhn c n ri.</p>\r\n<p>4 cch th thuc v cm th l bt u i vo tm. iu thn xong mi qua iu tm.  ni tm th ta phi quan st cc cm gic trc.</p>\r\n<p>Kinh vn nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>5.Cm gic h (pti - paisaved) khi th v, v y hc. Cm gic h khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>6.Cm gic lc (sukha - paisaved) khi th v, v y hc. Cm gic lc khi th ra, v y hc</p>\r\n<p>Mun hiu r ton b kinh vn trn  p dng vo vic tu tp hi th thuc v thin tu, chng ta hy n li mt cht hi th thuc v thin nh. Trong thin nh, khi hnh gi ch tm, r sot hi th, ct tm lin tc vo hi th, n lc tm khng cn chy nhy, phng dt  u na th lc y hi th c khuynh hng cng lc cng nh, thanh, vi t hn. Lc y, i theo vi hi th, do hi th  c an tr, ci thn cng c an theo. Ci thn an ny n khng cn au, nhc, t, nga g na m li c nhng cm gic rt d chu. Cm gic d chu ny c gi l h - l pti - chng c 5 loi h sau y:</p>\r\n<p>- Tiu h (khuddaka-pti): Ni da g, mc c, rn rn c ngi kh d chu.</p>\r\n<p>- Quang h hay st-na h (khanika-pti): Thy c nh chp hay nh sng...</p>\r\n<p>- Khinh h hay thng thng h (ubbega-pti): Nh lng lng nh mun bc ln, bay ln...</p>\r\n<p>- Hi triu h (okkantika-pti): Nh dao ng bi thy triu, nh vng ru m...</p>\r\n<p>- Sung mn h (pharaa-pti): Thm mt, tm mt c ton thn.</p>\r\n<p>Khng phi ai cng pht sanh ng lot 5 loi h ny, c ngi ch mt, hai. Nhng khi m cc h ny pht sanh th chng t thn hnh gi  c d chu, c yn ri. Khng dng li  y, m cng ng qu thch th, m m, chp th ci h y, hnh gi c tip tc theo di hi th vi tm x, nh nhng, thanh thn th hi th kia s cng lc cng ngn li, nh li, thanh li, vi t hn na. Phi tnh nim, ch tm  theo st hi th ko n mt tm dng, ri chng ta s cm nhn c mt trng thi phc lc thm su hn - y c gi l lc, l sukha. Ci lc ny n s thm m trong tm, c gi l php lc - l hnh phc thun ty tinh thn - hnh phc ca lc nh - th gian khng d g c c. n lc ny, hi th cng vi t hn na. C th n nh mt si ch nhch ln, nhch xung. C th n tng t nm bng gn, a hoa cc... Si ch, bng gn, hoa cc - ci tng ca n, tng ca hi th - li bt u t th n t; ngha l t mu xm c, chuyn qua xm sa, qua xm trong... ri ln ln n sng ln, trong ln... t thnh nht tng quang tng. T nht tng quang tng, ch tm vo n vi s nh nhng, thanh thn - hnh gi s ln lt i vo s yn lng, tnh lng thm su. L trnh thin tm c Abhidhamma lit k tun t nh sau: Quang tng, chun b, cn hnh, thun th, chuyn tnh, an ch (nh sc gii, s thin). Tc l hnh gi s chng cn hnh nh, sau  i vo nh s thin. Chng ta cng cn bit thm, lc 5 thin chi ca nh s thin pht sanh th n  ln lt loi tr 5 trin cinh sau:</p>\r\n<p>- Tm (vitakka) - tc l tm kim hi th, nu tinh tn lin tc, nhit tm th n s loi tr hn trm, thy min (thna-middha).</p>\r\n<p>- T (vicra) - tc l r sot hi th, theo di hi th, quan st hi th mt cch lin tc - th n c cng nng loi tr phn vn, lng l, do d, nghi ng, hoi nghi (vicikicch).</p>\r\n<p>- H (pti) - khi c mt trong 5 loi h nh  trn pht sanh th au nhc, t nga, kh chu, nng ny, bc bi s khng cn na - ni cch khc, n  loi b sn (vypda).</p>\r\n<p>- Lc (sukha) - khi hnh phc ni tm  thm su th cc trng thi tm nh lay ng, phng dt, n nn, hi qu s khng c t dung thn; ni cch khc,  loi tr c tro hi, tc l tro c v hi qu (uddhacca-kukkucca).</p>\r\n<p>- Nht tm (ekaggata) - tc l ch cn mt dng tm tri chy, khng cn mt khi nim no dy ln. Nu nht tm s khi, cn, th gi l cn hnh nh, nu trn vn, su hn th gi l an ch nh. C cn hnh v an ch u loi tr c dc lc, mi tham mun, tham dc, tham mun dc lc (kmachanda).</p>\r\n<p>L trnh thin nh l nh th, n xy ra, pht sanh mt cch t nhin, rt khoa hc, khng phi l ci g qu huyn mt, b him. Hi th nh vy th thn nh vy. Thn nh vy th tm nh vy. N rt logic. Cn lu , l hi th trong thin nh c khuynh hng cng lc cng ngn li, gom li, t thnh mt im, mt im quang tng mi i vo nh c. Hi th trong thin tu cng cng lc cng nh, vi t, trong - nhng khng th t li, khng th gom li, m trc sau, u thy bit r rng khi di, khi ngn, lc cn, lc su, lc t vi... i tng ca thin nh, hi th, cui cng l bt ng, tnh; i tng ca thin tu, hi th, trc cng nh sau u di chuyn, ng. V quan trng nht l, nh l do tng kin c m thnh; cn tu l phi do tu tri nh thc m nn.</p>\r\n<p>Li na, nu thin nh c h, c lc - th thin tu cng c h, c lc. n y, chng ta bt u hiu, ti sao, khi thn an tnh ri -an tnh thn hnh - ta bc qua cc cu kinh vn ni v h, ni v lc nh cu 5 cu 6: Cm gic h khi th v, th ra; cm giclc khi th v, th ra; v y hc!</p>\r\n<p>Thin tu bo vi ta rng, th th c th t nhin, nh nhng, thoi mi, ng dng sc, dng cng thi qu; ch ct lun thy r, bit r, lun tu tri n; n nh th no th sng sut, tnh thc thy r, bit r n nh th y, ng xen vo bt c mt tng tri, mt thc tri no. Thin nh loi tr 5 trin ci v lm cho 5 thin chi pht sanh; nhng loi tr  y ch c cng nng l lm cho n lng xung,  n xung nh   c, bao gi cng c tnh cch giai on, tm thi! Thin tu li khc. Thin tu, th ca n l gic, l minh, tng dng ca n l thy r nh thc tnh, soi sng v t chy v minh, phin no. Tuy nhin, ta cha i su vo iu  vi, hy tr li vi cch th vi h v lc. H v lc ca thin tu n nh nhng, tnh yn hn h v lc ca thin nh. Vy khi cc h n, lc n, n nh sao th ta cm gic n nh vy, phi khch quan, v th trc, x.</p>\r\n<p>n y, ta c th thu hiu lun hai cu k cng thuc v cm gic:</p>\r\n<p>7. Cm gic tm hnh (cittasakhra paisaved) khi th v, v y hc. Cm gic tm hnh khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>8. An tnh tm hnh (cittasakhra pasambhaya) khi th v, v y hc. An tnh tm hnh khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>Nu ta  hiu,  thc tp,  quan st  cm gic ton thn ra sao, an tnh thn hnh ra sao - th cm gic tm hnh v an tnh tm hnh cng phi c tu tri nh th. Nu h, cm gic h c tc ng bi thn, t thn  i vo tm - th lc chnh lphp lc ca thin tu. Ci lc ny n s len thm vo tm nh giy thm ht nc, phi cm nhn trn vn chng. V sau  th tm s an lc, an tnh. n y th ci tm  tm thi iu phc c ri... c phi khng qu v?</p>\r\n<p>Mt ngi ci:</p>\r\n<p>- Con tru trong Thp mc ngu , n y n khng cn thm n by la m ca ngi na u.</p>\r\n<p>- N  c thc phm khc, l an lc ni tm!</p>\r\n<p>- Qu v ni ng, nhng nht thit khng hon ton nh th. Nhng cch th ny l nguyn l, l gi  cho chng ta nm bt ton b nim hi th lin quan n T nim x. Chng ta khng th hc, thc tp nhanh n nh vy c. N cn min mt cng phu hn th nhiu. y ch l gi thit. Gi thit rng, tm  tm thi iu phc; nhng ta cn cn phi qun st, i su vo tm y, v ci tm y, ngoi th ra, n cn c tng, hnh v thc na m! Vy th c t t. Hy quan st .</p>\r\n<p>C- Bn Cch Th Thuc V Tm:</p>\r\n<p>Kinh vn nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>9. Cm gic tm (citta paisaved) khi th v, v y hc. Cm gic tm khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>10. Vi tm hn hoan (abhi-pamodayacitta) khi th v, v y hc. Khin tm hn hoan khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>11. Vi tm nh tnh (samdahacitta) khi th v, v y hc. Khin tm nh tnh khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>12. Vi tm gii thot (vimocayacitta) khi th v, v y hc. Khin tm gii thot khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>Khi cm th lc c thm su th ton b tm hnh u c ly lan, nh hng, tc ng lm cho tng, hnh, thc u an lc theo. Nu l trnh ca thin nh l h, lc, nh th l trnh ca thin tu ca tng t vy, l h, lc, an, hn hoan, nh, gii thot (theo tin trnh trn). Khi thc tp, hnh gi ghi nhn, cm nhn trn vn cc trng thi cng lc cng thanh lng hn ca tm. n ch vi tm nh tnh, gii thot th hnh gi  nh nhng v trin ci v phin no ri. Tuy nhin, ti sao li c cm t khin tm hn hoan, khin tm nh tnh v khin tm gii thot? V rng, hn hoan, nh v gii thot - ban u bao gi cng yu t, mui lc - cn c s tr gip ca nim v tn  trng thi y c thm su hn. y l vn  cn thi gian, cn s thun thc v cn s tinh luyn. V khi m trng thi tm gii thot  c n c, hnh gi mi bt u bc qua 4 cch th sau cng  qun php,  t tu tri, bc sang tu gic v tu minh... Vn  cng lc cng vi t, tinh mt, vy qun php s  dnh vo mt hm khc, hy nhn ni mt cht nh!</p>\r\n<p>D- Bn Cch Th V Qun Php:</p>\r\n<p>Kinh vn nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>13. Vi v thng ty qun (aniccnupass hoc aniccnupassan) khi th v, v y hc. Vi v thng ty qun, khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>14.  Vi ly dc ty qun (virgnupass) khi th v, v y hc. Vi ly dc ty qun khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>15. Vi tch dit ty qun (nirodhnupass) khi th v, v y hc. Vi tch dit ty qun khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>16. Vi x ly ty qun (painissaggnupass) khi th v, v y hc. Vi x ly ty qun khi th ra, v y hc.</p>\r\n<p>4 giai on qun php ny rt quan trng, nu thnh tu th tng ng vi 16 tu ca minh st. N chun b cho l trnh tm thnh o, ly thot ci dc, sc v v sc; t b phm phu tnh  thnh thang bc vo min t t do ca gii thot, ca thnh tnh...</p>\r\n<p>- L trnh y n nh th no, tha thy?</p>\r\n<p>- N cng tng t l trnh thin tm vy. Cng chun b, cn hnh, thun th, chuyn tnh, o tm, qu tm... Nhng m thi, chng ta khng cn thit  i su vo , qu v ch cn hc tp ci g cn thit nht, ci nguyn l no  ph qut nht  p dng trong i sng thng nht. Vy, chng ta hy c gng i qua cho ht nhng cch th thuc v qun php ny  nh!</p>\r\n<p>- Tha vng!</p>\r\n<p>- V thng ty qun (aniccnupass). Tht ra, ch v thng - anicca - th ai cng bit ri, nhng ch anupass m kinh sch no cng dch l ty qun, tuy hay y, nhng chng ta phi i su vo t nguyn mt t, s hiu chnh xc hn. Anupass, ng ngha vi anupassaka - c ngha l ngi quan st, ngi ng nhn xem! Vy aniccnupass l ngi quan st v thng! y,  d hiu ri y,  i vo tu qun ri y! Nhng v thng th ci g v thng? Trong qu v, ai bit, ci g v thng?</p>\r\n<p>- Xin tha - mt ngi p - L ton b ci g m chng ta  s dng tu tri  nhn ngm, lng nghe, cm nhn. y l hi th ngn di, l cm gic ton thn, an tnh ton thn, cm gic tm hnh, an tnh tm hnh, l h, l lc, l hn hoan, l nh tnh, l gii thot... Tt c chng, cc trng thi y u n ri i, thay i, bin hoi, i khc nn gi l v thng... Phi nhn ngm ci , quan st ci  ng nh bn cht chng l v thng!</p>\r\n<p>- ng vy!</p>\r\n<p>Cht c ngi hi:</p>\r\n<p>- Bc vo tu qun vipassan, ni no cng ni n danh, sc - sao  y thy khng ni n danh, sc?</p>\r\n<p>- Tht ra, ci g thuc v thn - v d hi th th c gi l sc; ci g thuc v tm nh cm th, tng, cc trng thi tm l, thc - l thuc v danh. Lc chng ta tu tri, nhn ngm, quan st nh thc - th mi danh, sc nh trn u v thng; chng khng th lp nh gia khng gian mt tng no c - nn gi l v tng. Do vy, hnh gi no qun st ci v thng ny - v thng ty qun - th m c cnh ca m Abhidhamma gi l  v tng gii thot - animitta vimokkha.</p>\r\n<p>- Ci gi l v tng, tha thy, kh nm bt lm, xin thy cho nhng v d c th.</p>\r\n<p>- Vng, hy nghe y! V d hi th, hi th l vt cht, mnh hay ni l tng hi th - nhng khi tu tri hi th tht s, mnh thy c mt ln gi nh qua cht mi, sau  n i vo bn trong. Ci ln hi y n khng ngng chuyn bin, thay i ch c tng no u! V d, mt m thanh cng l sc, m thanh n n, n i, tan long, bin hoi, n c tng no u? Cho ch ci thn ca chng ta y - thn sc, nu phn tch cho k th chng ch l tng hp cc t bo. C g trong cc t bo? Chng l s hi t ca cc nng lng vt cht. Khoa hc vt l thi ht nguyn t ny, cho chng ta bit rng, ci n v vt cht nh nht, nh hn cc phn t hng triu ln - th chng chnh l sng hay ht. V ngay cc sng, cc ht y cng khng c thc th, cngkhng c tng - v chng t ri tan rt nhanh, bng mt phn triu, hay mt phn triu triu giy ng h?! c Pht cch nay gn ba th k, khng cn dng c khoa hc, khng cn o c, th nghim - m ngi  thy r sc v tng qua tu gic nhn ngm thng tu nh vy y. Vy, y l h lun i theo, c l l lp ngn rt cao siu nhng d hiu v cng: V sc v thng nn v tng; vy v tng l tht tng ca cc sc - qu v c thy r iu  khng?</p>\r\n<p>Hi trng yn lng giy lt, sau  c ngi ni hiu, c ngi ni cha!</p>\r\n<p>- M thi, cng khng cn phi hiu cch lp ngn c v trit l y. Trit l cng mt lm. Chng ta ch cn quan st hi th, thc hnh, thin tp  thy r bng tu tri cc sc u v thng l  ri.</p>\r\n<p>- Vy cn danh - mt ngi ni - mt cm th, mt t tng, mt thc tri - chng cng c mt ri tan bin  nhng ch cho mt cm th, mt t tng, mt thc tri khc. Chng cng v thng, v tng nh vy?</p>\r\n<p>- ng th, bn  hiu. Nhng ci gi l au nhc, t nga, nng lnh, kh chu, d chu...  ni thn chng c nm hoi,  l, bt ng khng thay i u? Ri nhng ci gi l kh lc, h u  ni tm chng ta cng th. Nh vy chng t g? Chng t mi cm th - danh - u v thng, v v thng nn v tng. T tng v thc tri - danh - cng nm trong nh lut y, s tht y. n y, chc qu v  hiu tt c mi danh php, sc php u v thng ri ch nh?</p>\r\n<p>- Tha vng!</p>\r\n<p>- Nh qun v thng y, cng thin tp i su vo php qun y, hnh gi s thy r cc hnh - thn hnh, tm hnh - u b hn cuc bi sanh dit, chng khng th thot khi sanh dit, cc bn c thy r th khng ?</p>\r\n<p>- Tha, thy r!</p>\r\n<p>- Cha u! Cc bn mi hiu hoc bit trn lnh vc ca thc tri, ca tr nng ch cha thy r u! Thy r thuc lnh vc catu gic,  y cn s thin tp, cn s chng nghim t thn, qua trc gic, qua s thy bit, cm nhn trn vn bng tu qun nh chn, nh thc.</p>\r\n<p>- Tha vng, chng ti s thin tp.</p>\r\n<p>- Cn na, lc thin tp, khng cn thit phi chm chm ch ch ci ny l sc, ci ny l danh; tu tri ca chng ta phi nh ngi quan st khch quan, khng gi tn, khng nh gi, khng phn bit, khng so snh, t gio, khng th, khng x, hon ton trung dung, trung chnh, nh th, nh thc - y c gi l ci nhn, ci thy ca paramattha, ca  nht ngha, ca chn tht ngha... Ni c th hn mt t na, lc ngi th vi v thng ty qun - th ci g tc ng ln thn, thn sc, thn hnh, ci g tc ng ln tm, ln danh, tm hnh... u phi c lng nghe, quan st nh thc... tht l nh nhng, thanh thn, t nhin nh chng l... Ch c th thi! n gin v cng. Cc bn c lm c th khng, ci gi l v thng ty qun y?</p>\r\n<p>- Chng ti nm r ri!</p>\r\n<p>- By gi bc sang cu 14 - ly dc ty qun (virgnupass). Tht ra, virga khng phi l ly dc, m l khng c dc. Sau khi hnh gi thy r mi kh, mi lc, thn hnh, tm hnh, mi danh, mi sc u phi b thay i, bin hoi v bn cht chng ldukkha nn khng cn khi tm bm vu, chp th vo chng na; gi l khng cn dc vi cc hnh, cc php hu vi. Vy nn,ly dc ty qun cn c gi l kh ty qun (dukkhanupassan) - v nh ly dc nn thot khi cc kh. Ch ny hi rc ri, khng bit cc bn c theo kp khng?</p>\r\n<p>- Xin tha, kh phc tp.</p>\r\n<p>- Phc tp th b i, khng cn thit phi hiu lm g cho mt. Ch cn nn nh,  giai on ny, khi th, cc bn c quan st ci g n, ci g i mt cch rng rang, khng dnh mc, vy l c ri.</p>\r\n<p>C ngi hi:</p>\r\n<p>- Tu qun, ngi ta thng ni n v thng, kh, v ng; dng nh thy cha  cp n v ng?</p>\r\n<p>- Vng, tht ra, v v thng nn v ng, v v ng nn v thng, v v thng, v ng nn kh - chng i lin vi nhau, khng th tch ri c. S d ni v thng l do mnh quan st cc danh php v sc php din tin qua thi gian; cn ni v ng l do mnh quan st danh php v sc php din tin qua khng gian. Ni cch khc, qua thi gian, chng v thng, qua khng gian, chng v ng. Cn na, nu tu tri su st, qun chiu thm na th tt c mi php n i, sinh dit, c mt v r tan - mi danh php v sc php y u do duyn khi. V d, khi ta nghe mt li ph bng, m thanh y tc ng vo l tai, nh cn - ri i vo tm lm ta ni gin. Ni cch khc, tm sn (ni gin) s d c mt l do duyn nh cn v li ph bng. Ni cch khc na, nu khng c s giao tip (xc) gia nh cn (cn) v m thanh (trn) th s khng c th (cm gic, kh chu), khng c i (thng ght, tham sn). y chnh l l duyn khi, l thp nh duyn khi. Cng v duyn khi nn chng u v t tnh, khng c ng tnh, chng l khng tnh. Khi thy r duyn khi, v ng - v ng ty qun (anattnupassan), hnh gi s t c ci gi l khng tnh gii thot - sutavimokkha). Ri rm qu phi khng cc bn. Nhng chng ta phi c gng i cho ht nhng cch th c tnh cch kinh in ny,  m nm nguyn l. Ch no  y chng ta cng cn cn tm hiu tr li trong nhng bi thin tp tip theo.</p>\r\n<p>By gi l cu th 15  tch dit ty qun - nirodhnupass. Tch dit l tn gi khc ca Nit-bn, ni vng lng cc hnh, vng lng tham sn, phin no. Ti y, i tng nhn ngm, quan st ca hnh gi  l Nit bn ri. Tht ra, khi thy c s v thng ca mi danh php, sc php l ta  m h cnh ca gii thot th nht l v tng gii thot. Khi chng ta khng cn bm vu, chp th vo cc hnh l  m c cnh ca gii thot th hai  v i (hoc v nguyn) gii thot. Khi thy r cc php d hu vi hay v vi (cc hnh) - chng u l v ng th ta  m h c cnh ca gii thot th ba l khng tnh gii thot . Khng (khng tnh), v tng v v tc (v i) c gi l Tam gii thot mn.</p>\r\n<p>C ting x xo.</p>\r\n<p>- Ch! Sng qu nh?</p>\r\n<p>- Bc u y!</p>\r\n<p>- V lng kip y!</p>\r\n<p>- Khoan bnh phm vi, hy nghe . Cn cu th 16 l x ly ty qun - painissaggnupass, tc l sau khi thy r Nit-bn, hnh gi s khng bm vu, chp th Nit bn, cng c gi l v th trc Nit-bn. Nh th, hnh gi qun st trng thi tch dit mt cch trm nhin, rng khng v chng t trng thi hnh phc siu th...</p>\r\n<p>Ni tm li, 16 cch th  quan st thn, th, tm, php m chng ta va i qua, c xem nh l t s cn cho n ci rt ro. N l bn  l trnh tm linh cho tt thy mi hnh gi. Tuy nhin, khng phi chng ta s thc hnh mt hi t u n cui. y ch l gi  cho chng ta cch th ca tu qun, va nh c ni hi th va quan st c thn th tm php. Ri t t, chng ta s i li T nim x mt cch chi tit v c th hn.</p>\r\n<p>Cc bn c ai thc mc g na khng?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Minh c Triu Tm nh</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Thuvienhoasen</strong></p>	\N	\N	2016-08-29 16:15:11.809061	2016-08-30 16:33:47.41882	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	