158	banner-phat-dan-2561.jpg	Th Mi Tham D i L Pht n PL: 2561 - DL: 2017	<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>TH MI</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>THAM D I L PHT N TI CHA LINH QUANG</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>--------</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>PHT LCH 2561</strong>  <strong>DNG LCH 2017</strong></p>\r\n<p>Nam M Bn S Thch Ca Mu Ni Pht!</p>\r\n<p>Knh tha qu ng Bo Pht T, Thin Nam Tn N xa gn,</p>\r\n<p><span>Nhng tia nng ma xun mang li s m p v sc sng cho mun ngn hoa c sau mt gic di lng thinh trong lng t ma ng lnh gi. Cng vy, nhng tia sng t bi, tr tu, thanh tnh, gii thot v.v...phng ra ca c Th Tn khi Ngi th hin n sinh trong vn Lm T Ni</span>,<span> ph tan bng ti v minh phin no kh au ca chng sinh trong lun hi bt tn</span>,<span> mang li s an lc</span>,<span> hnh phc v bin nu mt ai chm ng vo nhng tia sng y. Tht l mt iu hnh phc cho chng ta khi nhng tia sng kia ca c Pht phng ra vn cn nh hin trong mi lc</span>,<span> mi ni cha tng ln tt.  m mnh vo nhng tia sng t bi tr hu ca c Thch Ca Mu Ni Nh Lai, ng Cng, Chnh Bin Tri th hin n sinh, cng ng tn dng ca tng</span>,<span> cng dng hng hoa tnh thu ca ch thin v long chng</span>. H<span>o vo nim vui h lc v bin ca t tri vn hu</span>, Cha Linh Quang long trng t chc i L Pht n PL 2561 vo lc 08 gi 30 ngy 15 thng 04 nm inh Du (Nhm ngy 10 thng 05 nm 2017).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>CHNG TRNH I L PHT N PL: 2561  DL: 2017</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">04 gi 00: Khai chung trng Bt nh rc Pht n Sanh</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">05 gi 00: GPT lm l n Pht n Sanh</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">06 gi 00: Pht t vn tp</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">08 gi 30: n tip i biu chnh quyn</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">09 gi 00: Khai mc i l Pht n (C chng trnh ring)</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">11 gi 00: Nghi thc tn gio cng dng Pht n Sanh</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">11 gi 30: Dng cm chay thn mt</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">14 gi 00: GPT sinh hot</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;">17 gi 30: Hon mn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Trn trng knh mi ton th qu ng Bo Pht T, Thin Nam Tn N xa gn cng nhau tham d, chn thnh cu nguyn cho i L Pht n c thnh tu vin mn.</p>\r\n<p>Knh chc qu v cng gia quyn phc hu trang nghim, thn tm an lc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Nam M Lm T Ni Vin V u Th H Th Hin n Sanh Bn S Thch Ca Mu Ni Pht</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">CHA LINH QUANG</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">p 1, Ph Ha, nh Qun, ng Nai  061.3629057</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ngy 10 thng 5 nm 2017  Nhm ngy 15 thng 04 nm inh Du</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ban T Chc Trn Trng n Tip Qu V</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Tr Tr Cha Linh Quang</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">i c Thch Hu Tr</p>	\N	\N	2017-05-02 02:07:45.887529	2017-05-02 02:07:55.887568	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	t	2017-05-02 00:00:00
159	nam-hoc-moi-2017-2018-main.jpg	Cha Linh Quang T Chc Trao Hc Bng Cho Hc Sinh Nhn Dp Bc Vo Nm Hc Mi 2017-2018	<p><strong> chun b cho cc em hc sinh c  sch v, qun o v  dng hc tp bc vo nm hc mi 2017  2018, ngy 13/8/2017 cha Linh Quang x Ph Ha  t chc l trao hc bng cho cc em hc sinh ngho, cc em hc sinh c thnh tch hc tp xut sc  cc trng tiu hc Nguyn nh Chiu, THCS Ph Ha, THCS Ph Tn, THCS Trn Hng o, THPT nh Qun, THPT Tn Ph v hc sinh mt s trng khc thuc huyn Tn Ph. </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1509544182.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Thy Thch Hu Tr tng hoa tri n i din Ban bo tr qu hc bng</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Ti bui l, qu hc bng <strong>uc tu</strong> ca cha Linh Quang  trao 151 sut hc bng. Trong  33 sut bcTiu hc, 71 sut bc THCS, 26 sut bc THPT, 7 sut cho bc Cao ng, i hcv 14 sut cho nhng em c nhiu thnh tch xut sc trong hc tp. Mi sut tr gi t 500.000 n 3 triu ng, tng kinh ph trn 80 triu ng.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Trn tinh thn o php ng hnh cng dn tc, ti bui l trao hc bng nm hc 2017-2018, thy Thch Hu Tr tr tr cha Linh Quang  cm n ban iu hnh, ban bo tr  ng hnh cng qu hc bng uc tu trong sut nhng nm qua v mong rng qu v tip tc ng h qu hc bng trong thi gian ti. i vi cc em hc sinh, thy khuyn cc em hy c gng vt kh hc tp tt, rn luyn tt  tr thnh con ngoan, tr gii, ngi cng dn tt.</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Trao i v hot ng khuyn hc ca cha Linh Quang trong nhng nm qua v phng hng cho nhng nm ti, thy Hu Tr cho bit: Qu hc bng uc tu pht trin mt cch rt thun li; t ch ch cp hc bng cho cc em hc sinh ngho  x Ph Ha vi s tin vi chc triu ng th n nay qu  m rng phm vi ra nhiu x nh Ph Tn, La Ng, Gia Canh, Ngc nh v mt s x ln cn khc ca huyn Tn Ph. Ngoi i tng hc sinh, sinh vin ngho th Nh cha cn trao hc bng cho cc em hc sinh, sinh vin c thnh tch hc tp xut sc vi s tin hng nm ln n gn mt trm triu ng. C c kt qu nh vy l nh s ng h ca qu nh ti tr, qu b con Pht t v s tm huyt ca qu thy c gio trong ban iu hnh.  duy tr v pht trin qu hc bng <strong>uc Tu</strong> trong nhng nm ti cn tch cc vn ng mi ngun lc v tinh thn pht tm ca qu pht t, cc mnh thng qun  xy dng qu hc bng.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Vi s tm huyt ca thy tr tr, ban bo tr v tinh thn pht tm ca b con pht t qu hc bng uc Tu ca cha Linh Quang s khng ngng ln mnh nh tm nguyn ca thy i c Thch Hu Tr: <strong><em>uc Tu soi sng vn no ng.</em></strong></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1509544296.jpg" /></strong></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Thy Thch Hu Tr trao hc bng cho cc em hc sinh xut sc nm 2017</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src="/uploads/editor/1509544312.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Cc em hc sinh nhn hc bng nm hc 2017-2018</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><img src="/uploads/editor/1509544327.jpg" /></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Cc em hc sinh vui mng nhn hc bng ra v</em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Thc hin: i Chu</strong></p>	\N	\N	2017-11-01 13:58:45.677557	2017-11-01 13:58:56.019314	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	t	2017-11-01 00:00:00
160	phu_hoa_hb2.jpg	Cha Linh Quang Vi Cng Tc Khuyn Hc, Khuyn Ti	<p><strong>Vi quan nim Lm tt cng tc khuyn hc, khuyn ti l thc hin li dy ca c Pht v ch trng ng li ca ng, trong nhng nm qua, cha Linh Quang (x Ph Ha) lun duy tr v y mnh cng tc khuyn hc, khuyn ti; c vo dp u nm hc mi nh cha li t chc trao hc bng cho hc sinh, sinh vin vt kh hc gii.</strong> <br />Cha Linh Quang ta lc ti p 1 x Ph Ha - huyn nh Qun - tnh ng Nai, ni sinh hot tn ngng tn gio ca b con Pht t cc x Ph Ha huyn nh Qun v x Ph in, Tr C huyn Tn Ph. Tr tr cha Linh Quang i c Thch Hu Tr l ngi rt quan tm n cng tc khuyn hc, khuyn ti. Chnh v vy m ngay khi v tr tr ti cha thy  cho thnh lp qu hc bng nhm tuyn dng khen thng nhng hc sinh, sinh vin c thnh tch cao trong hc tp v ng vin khuyn khch hc sinh, sinh vin vt kh hc gii.</p>\r\n<p>i c Thch Hu Tr cho bit: Qu hc bng ca nh cha chnh thc i vo hot ng c quy c t nm 2012, Ban iu hnh gm c thy Thch Hu Tr tr tr cha Linh Quang, c L Thanh Vn, Nguyn Th Hong Oanh gio vin trng THCS ng Hip, thy L Trn Ph Ha gio vin trng THCS Tr C, thy Nguyn Phi Long gio vin trng THCS Ph Ha, thy Nguyn nh Tun gio vin trng TH Nguyn nh Chiu, c Ng Th Thu Hng, Trn Thy Thanh Bnh gio vin trng TH Ph in, ngoi ra cn c cc thy c gio tm huyt vi cng tc khuyn hc. Kinh ph hot ng c vn ng t cc t chc, c nhn c lng ho tm.</p>\r\n<p>Trong 4 nm, t 2013 n 2016 cha Linh Quang  t chc trao 422 sut hc bng, hn 1.200 phn qu, tng tr gi trn 600 trm triu ng cho cc em hc sinh vt kh hc gii v cc em hc sinh c thnh tch cao trong hc tp. c bit a bn cc x Ph Ho, Ph Tn (huyn nh Qun) v Ph in (huyn Tn Ph) l nhng x vng su vng xa ca tnh ng Nai, i sng nhn dn cn nhiu kh khn; t l h ngho con ng. Nh s hot ng hiu qu ca qu khuyn hc cha Linh Quang  gp phn tch cc trong vic duy tr ph cp TH, THCS, THPT  cc a phng ni trn.</p>\r\n<p> chun b cho nm hc mi 2016  2017, qu  trao 126 sut hc bng, trong  50 sut bc tiu hc, 55 sut bc THCS, 18 sut bc THPT, 7 sut cho bc i hc, cao ng, 14 sut cho nhng em c nhiu thnh tch xut sc trong hc tp. Mi sut tr gi t 400.000 n 1 triu ng, tng kinh ph trn 66 triu ng. Ti bui l trao hc bng nm hc 2016-2017, thy Thch Hu Tr  cm n ban iu hnh, ban bo tr  ng hnh cng qu hc bng cha Linh Quang trong sut nhng nm qua v mong rng qu v tip tc ng h qu hc bng trong thi gian ti. i vi cc em hc sinh, thy khuyn cc em hy c gng vt kh hc tp tt, rn luyn tt  tr thnh con ngoan, tr gii, ngi cng dn tt.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1512265862.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="font-weight: 400;"><span>Trao i v phng hng hot ng khuyn hc ca cha Linh Quang trong nhng nm ti thy Tr cho bit:  y mnh cng tc khuyn hc, khuyn ti cn tch cc huy ng mi ngun lc v tinh thn pht tm ca qu pht t, cc mnh thng qun  xy dng qu hc bng. T chc trao hc bng cho cc em hc sinh vt kh hc tp  u nm, hc k I v cui nm hc, h tr thng xuyn cho nhng em hc sinh c hon cnh c bit kh khn. M rng a bn v i tng cp hc bng, t chc dy ph o cho cc em hc sinh tiu hc, THCS. </span></p>\r\n<p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>Xut pht t li dy ca c Pht<span></span><em>Ti sn ln nht ca i ngi l sc khe v tr tu</em></strong><span>,<span></span><em>Phng s chng sanh l cng dng ch Pht</em><span></span>cng nh trn c s quan im ng li ca ng<span></span><em>Gio dc &amp; o to, Khoa hc &amp; Cng ngh l quc sch hng u</em>,<span></span><em>y mnh cng tc khuyn hc, khuyn ti</em><span></span>v cng vi s tm huyt ca thy tr tr, ban bo tr cng tc khuyn hc, khuyn ti ca cha Linh Quang s khng ngng ln mnh v gp phn y mnh cng tc khuyn hc khuyn ti ca a phng x Ph Ho cng nh ca huyn nh Qun.</span></p>\r\n<p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: right;"><span><strong><i>Nguyn Vn Thu - x Ph Ho</i></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: left;"><span><strong><i>Ngun: <a href="http://dinhquan.dongnai.gov.vn/Pages/noi-dung-tin.aspx?NewsID=1399&amp;TopicID=37" target="_blank" title="http://dinhquan.dongnai.gov.vn/">http://dinhquan.dongnai.gov.vn/</a></i></strong></span></p>	\N	\N	2017-12-03 01:51:52.181811	2017-12-03 02:02:04.838792	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	1	t	\N	f	2017-12-03 00:00:00
162	DSC_0173.jpg	L Hi Hoa ng Va c Pht A Di  2017 - PL.2561	<p>Ti ngy ngy 17/11 inh Du, ha chung khng kh hn hoan cho mng ngy <strong>Khnh n c Pht A Di </strong> trong lng ngi con Pht trn khp mi min t nc, cha Linh Quang long trng t chc l hi Hoa ng Va c T ph A Di . Trong nim tn knh, thing ling, hn 200 Ch tng, Pht t gn xa  quy t v cha tham d m l.</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334847.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Sau phn pht biu tuyn b l do ca<strong> i c Thch Hu Tr</strong>, Ch Tng cng ton th o trng mt lng thnh knh, trang nghim, hng tm v c Pht A Di   tin hnh nghi l cng dng Ly 48 nguyn ca c Pht A Di . c Pht A Di  - v gio ch ci Ty phng Cc Lc l v Pht  pht 48 li th nguyn rng ln  tip dn, cu  chng sinh. Nhng li th nguyn ca Ngi bao trm khp php gii, dung cha chng sinh khp ba ci, bn loi. Vi tnh thng khng hn lng v tr tu v bin, ci Ty phng ca Ngi  tr thnh Lc quc cho chng sinh quay v nng ta, tu tp gii thot. Tip theo l nghi thc Hoa ng  Kinh hnh nim Pht. Ch tng v ton th Pht t truyn hoa ng kinh hnh nim Pht cu cho quc thi, dn an, chng sanh an lc.</p>\r\n<p>Hng nm c vo dp ngy <strong>17/11</strong> m lch, Ch tng, Pht t cha Linh Quang li thit l va A Di , tr thnh mt mt hot ng tm linh tt p ca nhng ngi con Pht.</p>\r\n<p>Di y l mt vi hnh nh ca bui l:</p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334879.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334883.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334886.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334887.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334889.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/uploads/editor/1515334891.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/up