 src="/uploads/editor/1512266247.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Mt s hnh nh tng qu t thin</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Cng trong dp ny, Ban t thin cha Linh Quang cng t chc trao tng mt cn nh Mi m t tm cho gia nh ng Trn Giang i  p 1, x Ph Ha. c bit, gia nh ng Trn Giang i c hon cnh c bit kh khn, phi sng trong mt cn nh dt nat, tm b khng  che ma, che nng; sinh hot ht sc cc kh. Xt thng cnh sng ca gia nh nh tinh thn Pht dy C thng yu v t th s c tt c, Ban t thin cha  vn ng kinh ph xy cn nh cho gia nh ng i vi tng kinh ph l 35 triu, trong  gia nh ch ng Trn Kim Sang  x Ph in l ti tr chnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1512266301.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Cn nh c ca ng i</em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em><img src="/uploads/editor/1512266698.jpg" /></em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Cn nh Mi m t tm</em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong></strong>Chiu ngy 02/12/2017 (rm thng Mi, inh Du), i c Thch Hu Tr tr tr cha Linh Quang  ch tr l bn giao cn nh cho gia nh ng Trn Giang i. ng i v cng vui mng v xc ng khi bc vo cn nh mi, ng chn thnh cm n s gip  ca Thy tr tr, Ban t thin nh cha v gia nh ng Sang. T y, ng  c cn nh m cng   khi tui  v gi; i ng  ht cnh sng nng th nng, ma th t v gi th rt. y thc s l Mi m t tm ca nhng ngi con Pht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Mi ngi mi nc, mi non<br />Khi vo ca Pht, chung con mt nh</em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1512266408.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /><img src="/uploads/editor/1512266409.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><em>Thy tr tr cha Linh Quang, Ban t thin v ch Sang ti l tng nh</em></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong><em>Thc hin: i Chn</em><