174	1.jpg	L Hy K C Thng Ta Thch Tr Tnh PL.2561 - DL.2018	<p>Sng ngy 14/4/2018 (nhm ngy 29/02/Mu Tut) ti cha Linh Quang  x Ph Ha, huyn nh Qun, tnh ng Nai, Ch tng, Pht t  long trng t chc l Hy k ln th 6 c thng ta Thch Tr Tnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em>n gio dng mt i nn Hu mng</em><br /><em>Ngha Tn S mun kip kh p n</em><br /><em>Cng c y snh bng Non Thi</em><br /><em>Mi ngn nm mun kip vn khng qun</em></p>\r\n<p>Thng ta Thch Tr Tnh c cng ln trong vic to lp, khai sng nn cha Linh Quang hin nay. Thun th v thng, Thng ta Thch Tr Tnh  ra i v min lc cnh. Vng theo li Pht dy,  th hin lng tri n, bo n ca ngi con Pht. Ch tng, Pht t cha Linh Quang t chc l Hy k ca Ngi mt cch nghim trang, thnh knh v xc ng, vi nhiu nghi thc quan trng nh:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Pht T Vn Tp.</li>\r\n<li>Cung Nghinh Ch Tn c  Qu Phi on Quan Lm.</li>\r\n<li>Tng Kinh a Tng.</li>\r\n<li>Khai Kinh Bch Pht - Cng Ng</li>\r\n<li>Cung Tin Gic Linh</li>\r\n<li>Cng Dng Trai Tng</li>\r\n<li>Phng sinh</li>\r\n<li>Tng qu t thin</li>\r\n<li>Cung tin Ch Tn c hi quy bn t. Tin qu khch v Pht t ra v.</li>\r\n<li>Hon mn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>V d l Hy k ca Thng ta Thch Tr Tnh c cc on Tng ni, Pht t ca cc a phng huyn nh Qun, huyn Tn Ph, TX Long Khnh tnh ng Nai v mt s on ca TP H Ch Minh. Su mi v Ch tng v hn 600 Pht t c mt trong l Hy k ca Ngi, lm khng kh bui l tr nn trang trng, m cng v chan cha tnh thng yu ca nhng ngi con Pht. <br />Sau bui l Nh cha  trao tng 30 sut qu cho b con ngho  a phng, mi sut tr gi 500.000.<br /><strong><em>Mt s hnh nh ti l:</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1524018465.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1524018470.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1524018472.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1524018474.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1524018476.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="te