176	1.jpg	Bp n T Thin - m Nhng Tm Lng	<p>Mc d bn rt nhiu vic nhng i c Thch Hu Tr tr tr <a href="http://chualinhquang.com.vn/" target="_blank" title="Cha Linh Quang "><strong>cha Linh Quang</strong></a> vn lun quan tm chm lo cho bp n t thin m chnh tay thy gy dng.<br />T nhng khi u v vn kh khn, c lc tng chng nh b tc nhng n nay, bp n t thin ca cha Linh Quang ( x Ph Ha, huyn nh Qun, tnh ng Nai)  i vo hot ng n nh.</p>\r\n<h2>Ba Nm Pht Tm Nhm La Bp n T Thin</h2>\r\n<p>Trao i v c duyn nhm la bp n t thin, i dc Thch Hu Tr tr tr cha Linh Quang cho bit, thy  tng i nhiu ni, chng kin nhiu cnh kh cc nhng khng ai cc kh, o le v ng thng, ng c gip  nh nhng bnh nhn ngho  cc bnh vin; v h  ngho li b bnh him ngho. Nh dn gian vn thng ni Ngho li gp ci eo, xt thng trc nhng cnh i cc kh Thy  quyt tm xy dng bp n t thin ca cha Linh Quang  gip  h.<br />Cha Linh Quang, x Ph Ha thuc a bn vng su vng xa ca huyn nh Qun, tnh ng Nai; l ni sinh hot tn gio ca b con nhn dn cc x Ph in, Tr C (huyn Tn Ph), x Ph Ha (huyn nh Qun) v mt s a phng khc. i sng b con ni y cn gp rt nhiu kh khn. Tuy nhin, vi tm lng t bi, ban vui, cu kh, tng thn tng i ca ngi con Pht; i c Thch Hu Tr cng Ban t thin <strong><a href="http://chualinhquang.com.vn/" target="_blank" title="Cha Linh Quang">cha Linh Quang</a></strong>  xy dng thnh cng bp n t Thin.<br />c s ng  ca Ban gim c bnh vin a khoa huyn nh Qun, cho php cha Linh Quang pht cm, cho t thin phc v bnh nhn ngho. i c Thch Hu Tr khn trng xc tin cng vic v bp n t thin ca cha Linh Quang chnh thc c nhm la vo nm 2015. Bui u i vo hot ng bp n gp v vn kh khn; thiu v lng thc, thc phm, thiu c s vt cht, phng tin vn chuyn, ngi phc v  nhng kh khn tng chng nh khng qua ni. Xt thng trc nhng cnh ngho bnh tt, Thy tr tr cng Ban t thin nh cha  ra sc vn ng mi ngi ng h  duy tr hot ng ca bp n. Nhn c s ng cm v ng h ca cc nh ho tm, b con Pht t gn xa, bp n t thin ca cha Linh Quang  tng bc khc phc kh khn, vt qua th thch v i vo hot ng n nh n nay  c 3 nm. <br />Hin, bp n t thin c hai mi ngi lm vic, c xe  t vn chuyn cm t cha n bnh vin, c bit trong nm va qua, thy tr tr  cho xy dng li khu nh bp mi rng trn 300 mt vung, khang trang sch p, y  tin nghi phc v cho cng vic nh bp. Mi tun bp n pht cm hai ln vo ngy th 7 v ch nht, mi ngy pht t 300 n 400 sut cm, cn cho n sng th pht tt c cc ngy trong tun theo nhu cu ca bnh nhn. Kinh ph hot ng t ngun ng h ca cc nh ho tm, b con Pht t gn xa v mt phn trch t ngn sch ca cha. Bnh qun mi thng kinh hot ng ca bp n t thin l 40.000.000 ng, mi nm l 480.000.000 ng. Nh vy, trong 3 nm qua, Bp n t thin <a href="cha%20Linh Quang" target="_blank" title="Cha Linh Quang"><strong>cha Linh Quang</strong></a>  cung cp hng ngn ba n cho bnh nhn ngho  bnh vin a khoa huyn nh Qun vi s tin ln ti 1.440.000.000 triu ng.<br />Nhn c s ng h ca mi ngi, thy mun pht thm cm chay cho bnh nhn nhng lnh o bnh vin khng ng , v bnh vin lo bnh nhn khng khe mnh, cn phi c ba n mn   dinh dng.</p>\r\n<h2>Nhng Tm Lng y Yu Thng Bp n</h2>\r\n<p>Tham gia cng tc ti bp n t thin cha Linh Quang c hn hai mi ngi, cc c ch u rt nhit tnh v hoan h lm vic. Mi ln vo bp l mi ln c n nhn nhng nim vui v gn nh ai cng u ch n ngy th 7, ch nht hng tun  cng nhau vo bp. Cc c ch trong bp n nh cha; ngi gi c, ngi tr c, mi ngi u say sa lm vic, h nh dn ht tnh cm v kh nng ca mnh vo trong nhng ba cm ca ngi bnh. C nhng b c nm nay  by, tm mi tui ri vn thc khuya dy sm, mit mi lm vic chm lo cho tng ba cm, bt cho ca bnh nhn ngho. Cng vic c thy i c phn cng c th cho tng thnh vin, tng nhm, lch lm vic lun phin nn ai cng c c hi  phc v v ai cng c thi gian  ngh ngi. Nh vy, cng vic  bp n t thin lc no cng din ra nhp nhng, tri chy v kp thi. Cng vic ca mt ba cm t thin c bt u t ba gi ri sng v kt thc lc mi hai gi tra. Sau khi pht cm cho bnh nhn xong v cha thu dn  c, lau ra chn bt, bp nc, mi ngi ai cng mt nhng h u rt vui v h li tip tc lm nhng vic tt. i vi ti, nhng c ch lm vic trong bp n t thin l nhng ngi bnh thng, gin d nhng rt v i; v S v i khng nm trong ti sn, quyn lc, danh vng hay ting tm. N c pht hin trong lng tt, s nhn nhng, s phng s v tnh cch. <br />Cu mong cho bp n t thin <strong><a href="http://chualinhquang.com.vn/" target="_blank" title="Cha Linh Quang">cha Linh Quang</a></strong> tip tc c duy tr v pht trin  phc v c nhiu bnh nhn ngho, chia st bt cho h mt phn kh khn  h nhanh chng phc hi sc khe, xy dng cuc sng.</p>\r\n<h2>Hnh nh Bp n T Thin Cha Linh Quang</h2>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657162.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657166.jpg" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657168.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657171.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657173.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657175.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657177.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657179.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657181.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657184.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657186.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657187.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657190.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657193.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657195.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657197.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657198.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657200.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/uploads/editor/1525657392.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text